title: Tanning Zone
resume: Two best friends working at an LA tanning salon question their life choices as former classmates achieve traditional success. Their dead-end job might just be genius - or the path to nowhere.

title: Quand la marabunta gronde
resume: Charlton Heston est le propriétaire sombre et puissant d'une plantation dans la jungle sud-américaine, sauvage et trompeuse.

title: Superman et les nains de l'enfer
resume: Lorsque des êtres souterrains explorent le monde de la surface depuis un puits de pétrole profond et provoquent par inadvertance une panique, seul Superman peut empêcher une tragédie.

title: Le garçon et le monde
resume: Un petit garçon se lance dans une aventure à la recherche de son père.

title: Le voyage de Ricky
resume: Even though everybody else thinks he's a sparrow - Richard himself holds tight to the conviction that he is in fact a stork.

title: Les magiciens du royaume perdu
resume: When evil screams throughout the world. When all the galaxies converge. When all that's fair and fine seems lost. A Hero will emerge.

title: La malédiction de la pyramide
resume: Une expédition internationale découvre une cité perdue sous une pyramide, où ils doivent empêcher les dieux réveillés de l'Égypte ancienne de déclencher l'Apocalypse.

title: Compañeros
resume: Le film raconte les 12 années d'emprisonnement vécues par trois des figures les plus célèbres de l'Uruguay. Les trois otages mènent une lutte existentielle pour échapper à une terrible réalité qui les condamne à la folie.

title: Les Contrebandiers de Moonfleet
resume: Moonfleet se trouve dans le comté du Dorset, en Angleterre. Le Fleet fait référence à la portion de terre juste à l'ouest de Portland, au sud de l'Angleterre.

title: Appleseed: Ex Machina
resume: With Brialeos convalescing after a mission, Deunan is assigned a new and remarkably familiar partner as a strange wave of terrorist attacks plague Olympus.

title: Carry on Cabby
resume: A taxi company is threatened when an all-female firm sets itself up in business and starts to steal their customers.

title: Le diable à 4 heures
resume: Un prêtre excentrique recrute trois condamnés réticents pour l'aider à sauver une léproserie d'enfants d'une île du Pacifique menacée par un volcan en feu.

title: Kaena: La prophétie
resume: Sur la planète Axis, Kaena, une adolescente rebelle, va défier le grand prêtre et les croyances ancestrales de son peuple pour entreprendre un voyage périlleux et découvrir les sombres secrets qui se cachent au-delà des nuages.

title: Thirst
resume: When a group of wayward teens arrive at a desert boot camp, with no communication, and nowhere to run to, they realize their only chance for survival is to fight for their lives.

title: La Diligence vers l'Ouest
resume: On the stagecoach to Cheyenne, a mixed group of passengers must work together to survive the arduous journey and the Indian attacks.

title: La flamme pourpre
resume: In World War II Burma, a Canadian bomber pilot becomes reckless after losing his bride in a Luftwaffe air raid.

title: Agaguk
resume: In Canada's North during the 1930s, a young Inuit kills a White trader and is pursued by the police but his father is determined to protect his fugitive son at any cost.

title: Zeus et Roxanne
resume: Mary, biologiste marine, a la mauvaise surprise de trouver un chien embarqué clandestinement dans son bateau de recherche. Mais elle est bientôt intriguée de constater que le chien se lie d'amitié avec le dauphin qu'elle y garde captif.

title: Sauvage
resume: Laci comes to live at a run-down gas station with his long-lost father. A van arrives with four prostitutes and their handlers, and we learn that that Laci's father has something to hide. The gang resolves to wait... for what? AKA Primal.

title: Arthur et Merlin
resume: A young Celtic warrior and a hermit wizard must unite to defeat an evil druid.

title: Pokémon : Jirachi, le génie des vœux
resume: A magician attempts to use the power of the Millennium Comet to awaken the legendary Pokémon Groudon.

title: Attrition
resume: When a Thai girl with mythical powers goes missing, Axe and his old team unite in attempts to bring her back.

title: Hurricane
resume: Un marin polynésien, injustement emprisonné après s'être défendu contre un colon tyrannique, est persécuté sans relâche par l'impitoyable gouverneur français de son île.

title: Le masque aux yeux verts
resume: A noblewoman begins to lead a dangerous double life in order to alleviate her boredom.

title: Dragon Ball : Le Château du démon
resume: Goku and Krillin want to be trained in the martial arts by the great Master Roshi. The only way he will agree to train them is if they go to Devil's Castle to find the Sleeping Princess, who is being held prisoner by Count Lucifer, and bring her back to his island.

title: La Source de feu
resume: A group of explorers search for the legendary "flame of life", a mysterious force that bestows immortality.

title: Get on the Bus
resume: A disparate group of African-American men travel by bus to Washington, DC for the Million Man March.

title: Lone Star Shark
resume: A group of virtual hunters unleash a deadly shark in a Texas lake, causing a young couple to fight for their lives during a peaceful fishing trip in a secluded cove.

title: The Sisterhood
resume: In the year 2021, women have been enslaved by men, with their only hope for freedom lying in the hands of a nomadic band of maiden warriors. The maiden warriors Alee and Vera tap Marya and her hawk to help them.

title: 10.0 Earthquake : Menace sur Los Angeles
resume: Los Angeles is about to be hit by a devastating earthquake, and time is running out to save the city from imminent danger.

title: The Nan Movie
resume: Le personnage emblématique de Catherine Tate, Nan, apparaît sur grand écran alors qu'elle part pour un road trip de Londres en Irlande avec son petit-fils Jamie pour faire amende honorable avec sa sœur Nell.

title: 8-ban deguchi
resume: A live-action adaptation of the video game.

title: Eiga Doraemon Shin Nobita to tetsujin heidan: Habatake tenshitachi
resume: Nobita and Doraemon find a giant robot in pieces, which they later assemble and it turns out to be a destructive weapon. A girl comes searching for the robot. Will Nobita and gang be able to save earth from imminent invasion.

title: D-Railed
resume: Passengers on a train that crashes into a river must decide whether to risk waiting for help in the wreckage or take their chances in the murky depths below.

title: Le Château de ma mère
resume: De retour dans ses collines, Marcel découvre l'amour et ses premiers chagrins. Se rendant désormais tous les week-ends à La Treille, la famille emprunte un raccourci traversant des domaines privés.

title: Valley of the Gods
resume: Entwines Navajo lore with a reclusive trillionaire and his would-be biographer, creating a fascinating, mysterious and idiosyncratic vision of America.

title: Roller blade warriors
resume: In the future, a warrior nun on roller skates must rescue a seer, who is to be sacrificed by a band of mutants.

title: Equinox
resume: Four friends are attacked by a demon while on a picnic, due to possession of a tome of mystic information. Told in flashbacks by the sole survivor.

title: Les rebelles viennent de l'enfer
resume: C'est l'histoire d'une amitié et d'une survie quotidienne qui se déroule dans les années 1860. On suit un groupe de fripouilles en cavale qui vivent en suivant leur instinct et en faisant preuve de débrouillardise.

title: Jurassic Shark: Terreur des mers
resume: Retenu dans la glace depuis le Jurassique, un requin préhistorique est libéré après un forage illégal. Les voleurs d'art et les jeunes étudiantes qui sont à proximité se retrouvent soudain en grand danger.

title: Braquage à la suédoise
resume: Charles, un braqueur professionnel spécialiste des voitures de luxe, rassemble une équipe d'experts et conçoit un plan audacieux pour venger le meurtre de son oncle et ruiner la riche industrielle qui en est responsable.

title: Makoo
resume: Eight businessmen decide to go to the location where the Elsalam ship was sunk years ago to make a documentary. There, they face a lot of dangers.

title: Le dernier soldat
resume: Following a deadly viral outbreak, private military soldier Max Gatling leads a handful of survivors and a ragtag band of robots against an army of the infected.

title: Beyond Atlantis
resume: A band of adventurers invade a native island determined to grab a reported fortune in buried treasure. The islanders are just as determined to keep their sacred treasure. Complications ensue.

title: Dinosaures
resume: A scientist's kids are sucked into a TV screen and wind up in the Stone Age with cavemen and dinosaurs.

title: Aventure magique! Un film Wiggles
resume: The Wiggles throw a surprise party for Dorothy the Dinosaur, while she goes after a magician who takes Greg's magic wand to become popular.

title: Odd Squad: Le film
resume: The Odd Squad springs into action when a rival group called Weird Team starts to cover up problems instead of solving them.

title: Batman : Le Retour des justiciers masqués
resume: Batman and Robin of the 1960s live action series are back in action to take down their fiendish foes united once more against them.

title: Vendetta for the Saint
resume: Quelle est la véritable identité d'Alessandro Destamio ? Est-il un membre de l'aristocratie sicilienne ayant émigré aux États-Unis ? Ou Dino Cartelli, un petit banquier véreux, qui aurait frôlé la mort au cours d'un cambriolage ?

title: Game of Death
resume: L'agent spécial Marcus Jones est assigné au chevet d'un diplomate victime d'un attentat. Le garde du corps comprend que les criminels ne vont pas s'arrêter là . Jones s'allie à une infirmière pour mettre hors d'état de nuire les tueurs

title: Joyride
resume: Three teenagers leave Los Angeles and drive north to Alaska, wind up robbing a pipeline and taking one of the employees hostage.

title: Objectif: septième planète
resume: Earth sends a five-man team to explore the frozen planet Uranus, only to find a temperate forest and sultry women from their past on it, courtesy of an alien brain with evil designs.

title: Other Versions of You
resume: Diggsy meets a stranger who gives him a key to parallel universes where another version of the girl of his dreams may not only exist, but where one of them could possibly love him back.

title: The Green Hornet
resume: A newspaper publisher and his Korean servant fight crime as vigilantes who pose as a notorious masked gangster and his aide.

title: Opération Green Ice
resume: A down on his luck engineer gets involved in an adventure with a mysterious woman and an emerald magnate.

title: Est-ce un Tort de Chercher des Rencontres Romantiques dans un Donjon?: Arrow of the Orion
resume: Bell Cranel goes to a festival in the city where he enters a contest to pick up a legendary spear. Pretty soon, he embarks on a quest with the Goddess of the Hunt, to eliminate an ancient threat that lurks outside the city.

title: Beyond the Gates
resume: Two estranged brothers reunite at their missing father's video store and find a VCR board game dubbed 'Beyond The Gates' that holds a connection to their father's disappearance.

title: Camp érotique
resume: A group of women are kidnapped by guerrillas and forced to serve as prostitutes for them in a jungle brothel. The sadistic female warden decapitates uncooperative girls.

title: À l'abordage
resume: Brian Hawke of the Royal Navy versus the pirates of Madagascar.

title: The Adventurers
resume: The world's top thieves join forces to pull off the heist of a lifetime. But when they find themselves pursued across Europe by a legendary French detective, they'll have to take their game to the next level.

title: L'Attaque des Titans : L'Arc et la Flèche écarlates
resume: Dans un monde dystopique, un jeune homme fait voeu d'éliminer les créatures humanoïdes géantes qui menacent les quelques humains survivants.

title: The Wild Women of Wongo
resume: Men, women and apes live together as three different tribes on the tropical island of Wongo. When the tribes discover that they live together on the island, ape-men start planning a raid on the tribe in order to capture mates.

title: Le retour de l'étalon noir
resume: A teenager loses his horse in Morocco and gets him back after various daredevil adventures.

title: Les voyages de Gulliver
resume: After being shipwrecked, a man finds himself on an island inhabited by tiny people, who soon make plans for him.

title: Drôle de singe
resume: Margaret teaches a gorilla sign language etc. When the gorilla owner takes it back to make money from shows, Margaret's rebellious teenage son steals it. They're off on a road trip to the Canadian border.

title: The Buried Giant
resume: The journey of Axl and Beatrice, a couple who set off on a journey to find their son, who they have not seen for some time, and actually do not remember very well.

title: Verano en rojo
resume: Madrid, summer of 2010. Commissioner María Ruiz investigates the sinister crime of a young man. With no visible identity and no clues or apparent motive, María will begin an investigation that will become more and more complicated.

title: Robowar
resume: A special forces unit known as BAM is tasked with a mission: tracking down the rogue Omega-1 cyborg unit in a dense jungle, without being told their exact objective. Soon they find themselves the hunted rather than the hunters.

title: Alcatraz
resume: Un groupe de prisonniers, dirigé par un voleur armé et un gangster, tente de s'échapper de la tristement célèbre île d'Alcatraz.

title: Bienvenue chez les Loud: Le film
resume: Accompagné de ses parents et de ses 10 soeurs, Lincoln Loud se rend en Écosse et apprend que la royauté fait partie de la famille dans ce voyage musical mondial.

title: La corde de sable
resume: A man abused by a sadistic mining company cop before he could tell where on their desert property he'd found diamonds decides to steal them instead.

title: The Rebels of PT-218
resume: En pleine Seconde Guerre mondiale, l'océan Atlantique devient un champ de bataille mortel lorsqu'un torpilleur américain se bat contre le bombardement constant des forces allemandes.

title: Black Is King
resume: Visual album from Beyoncé inspired by 'The Lion King'.

title: Envoyé spécial
resume: Un ex-américain coriace. Un journaliste de la marine se bat contre le temps pour sauver la vie de milliers de personnes innocentes après avoir découvert un complot terroriste complexe.

title: Poséidon Rex
resume: Une petite île au large des côtes du Bélize se retrouve terrorisée par une créature venue des tréfonds du temps lorsqu'un groupe de plongeurs à la recherche d'un ancien trésor espagnol la libèrent accidentellement.

title: Ninja Terminator
resume: Trois étudiants en arts martiaux partent à la recherche du Guerrier Ninja d'Or, une statue réputée avoir des pouvoirs magiques.

title: Objectif lotus
resume: A suspected Western spy steals a secret microfilm from China and hides it in the skeleton of a museum dinosaur, prompting a frantic search for it by various interested parties.

title: La reine des neiges
resume: A young girl embarks on a perilous journey to rescue her friend, who has been taken captive by the Snow Queen and turned cruel by enchanted ice splinters.

title: Ape vs. Monster
resume: Un singe s'écrase sur la Terre, ce qui crée une boue qui lui permet, ainsi qu'à un scorpion, d'atteindre une taille gigantesque, entraînant une lutte pour la domination.

title: Gekijouban Hunter x Hunter: Fantomu rûju
resume: Someone has stolen Kurapika's eyes-and another survivor from his clan whose members were massacred for their Scarlet Eyes! Gon and Killua begin investigating on his behalf, but shortly after they've begun, the Phantom Troupe appears!

title: Revelation
resume: Depuis des millénaires, les forces de l'ombre et de la lumière se livrent un combat sans merci pour s'emparer d'une mystérieuse relique, mais Magnus Martel charge son fils Jake et Mira, une étudiante en alchimie, de la détruire.

title: The Wind & the Reckoning
resume: As an outbreak of leprosy engulfs 19th-century colonial Hawai'i, a small group of infected Native Hawaiians resist government-mandated exile, taking a courageous stand against the provisional government. Inspired by real-life events.

title: Daughters of Joy
resume: A count tasks seductive Susan and her friends to stop an assassination plot against Napoleon in this historical sex comedy that's part of "Frau Wirtin..." movie franchise.

title: Beretta's Island
resume: An Interpol agent fights drug dealers in his homeland, the beautiful island of Sardinia and in America.

title: Starbright
resume: A woman finds the secret to making wishes come true.

title: Le barbare et la geisha
resume: In 1856, the first U.S. Consul General to Japan encounters the hostility of the local authorities and the love of a young geisha.

title: Vikram
resume: Vikram, un flic qui pleure la mort de sa femme, est chargé de récupérer un missile. Il est aidé par un ingénieur hautement qualifié, Preethi, qui détient les connaissances nécessaires pour désarmer la bombe nucléaire, dans sa mission.

title: La piste des éléphants
resume: Une épidémie de choléra sévit, la terre souffre de la sécheresse et des troupeaux d'éléphants rendus fous par la soif dévastent la plantation dans une ruée tonitruante.

title: Darwin Awards
resume: To investigate bizarre insurance claims that transpired in either accidents, death or both, a former cop and an insurance investigator travel throughout the country to look at the cases up close.

title: Capitaine Sindbad
resume: To marry Princess Jana, Captain Sindbad must battle deadly obstacles and fight El Kerim, the evil ruler who also wants to marry the princess.

title: L'étranger au paradis
resume: A roguish poet is given the run of the scheming Wazir's harem while pretending to help him usurp the young caliph.

title: Le Tombeau hindou
resume: Henri et Seetha fuient Eschnapur afin de vivre leur amour. Rattrapés par le frère du maharadjah, qui souhaite s'emparer du trône, la jeune danseuse est contrainte d'épouser Chandra pour que son bienaimé puisse continuer de vivre.

title: Maximum Ride
resume: Six enfants génétiquement modifiés (ils sont 98% humains, 2% oiseaux) parviennet à échapper à leurs créateurs. Des hommes-loups sont lancés sur leurs traces pour les éliminer.

title: Les oies sauvages II
resume: A group of mercenaries is hired to spring Rudolf Hess from Spandau Prison in Berlin.

title: L'homme au masque de fer
resume: Despotic King Louis XIV discovers he has a twin brother who has grown up under the tutelage of his foster father, the patriotic musketeer D'Artagnan.

title: Lego Marvel Avengers: Code Rouge
resume: The Avengers meet a dangerous new foe quite unlike anything they've ever encountered before.

title: The Polar Express 2
resume: 20 ans après la sortie du film de Noël de Robert Zemeckis, The Polar Express, il a été confirmé que Polar Express 2 était en cours de développement.

title: Destination: planète Hydra
resume: A spaceship from Hydra crashes on Sardinia. Aliens take a scientist, his daughter, technicians and spies hostage to fix their ship. After repairs, aliens abduct the humans but they rebel, sending the ship into deep space.

title: Captain Planet
resume: A story centered around an environmentally friendly superhero.

title: Le Dernier Dinosaure
resume: A wealthy big game hunter and his group become trapped in prehistoric times where they are stalked by a ferocious dinosaur.

title: Le vieux qui ne voulait pas payer l'addition
resume: The 101 year old man Allan Karlsson goes through Europe in search for a Russian soda recipe he lost during the early 70s. Unfortunately, he is not the only one who is looking for it.

title: Doug, le film
resume: Suivez les mésaventures de Doug Fripon, qui se retrouve pris entre la volonté de sauver le "monstre" du lac pollué Dakodac et l'envie d'emmener Patti Mayonnaise au bal de l'école.

title: Tarzan chez les singes
resume: Élevé par un singe sans petit, l'héritier orphelin des Greystokes devient l'un des leurs. Le Dr Porter organise une expédition de sauvetage et sa belle fille Jane attire son attention. Tarzan des singes a-t-il trouvé la compagne idéale ?

title: Dora and the Search for Sol Dorado
resume: Dora, Diego, and their new friends brave the treacherous Amazonian jungle, racing to uncover the legendary Sol Dorado treasure before villainous forces claim its immense power.

title: Le Grand Attentat
resume: A New York City detective, traveling by train between New York and Baltimore, tries to foil an on-board plot to assassinate President-elect Abraham Lincoln before he reaches Baltimore to give a major pre-Inauguration speech in 1861.

title: Les gens de la nuit
resume: During the Cold War, an American soldier is abducted in West Berlin, sparking a recovery effort led by Colonel Steve Van Dyke.

title: La Phalène d'argent
resume: A famous female flier and a member of Parliament drift into a potentially disastrous affair.

title: The Royal Hunt of the Sun
resume: In 1532, Spanish conquistador Francisco Pizarro leads an expedition into the heart of the Inca Empire and captures the Incan Emperor Atahualpa and claims Peru for Spain.

title: Off Ramp
resume: A couple of lovable, degenerate Juggalos must sojourn through America's hellish underbelly to The Gathering of the Juggalos, the one place on earth they feel accepted.

title: Pinocchio et l'Empereur de la nuit
resume: Pinocchio and his friends, a glow worm and a marionette, search for a magic music box. However, so is the evil Scalawag and the Emperor of the Night.

title: Ayalaan
resume: Un extraterrestre perdu cherche de l'aide pour rentrer chez lui, mais tout devient plus difficile après que l'extraterrestre tente de rentrer chez lui.

title: Drôles de pirates 2
resume: Three vegetable friends seek the roots of true heroism during a 17th-century adventure.

title: Alien Predator
resume: Lorsqu'une équipe d'opérations secrètes est envoyée pour enquêter sur le crash d'un objet non identifié, ils se retrouvent bientôt traqués par ses anciens occupants.

title: Coeur de lion
resume: A young knight intent on joining King Richard's crusaders pledges to lead a group of orphans to safety and to protect them from a notorious slaver.

title: Fantastic Voyage
resume: Un scientifique atteint d'une maladie potentiellement mortelle risque sa seule chance de survie : cinq de ses collègues sont miniaturisés dans un vaisseau et injectés dans son système sanguin.

title: Ass Backwards
resume: Two best friends (Kate and Chloe) embark on a cross country trip back to their hometown to attempt to win a pageant that eluded them as children.

title: Against a Crooked Sky
resume: When Charlotte Sutter is kidnapped by Apaches, her brother Sam, aided by an old drunk prospector, goes searching for her.

title: Course à mort : l'ultime solution
resume: A former race car driver's car is confiscated. He rebuilds it and drives to Free California with a teen's help. Agents dispatch a jet pilot to stop him, fearing his autonomy threatens their control.

title: Sumuru
resume: Basé sur les romans cultes de Sax Rohmer, ce fantasme futuriste vous emmène dans une colonie terrestre dans un futur lointain, où les femmes gouvernent et les hommes sont utilisés pour propager la race et travailler dans les mines.

title: Ground Control
resume: A disgraced former air traffic controller is called back into service when the airport's traffic control system malfunctions.

title: Le Colosse de Hong Kong
resume: Ah Wei est une belle femme, considérée comme la reine de la jungle grâce à la protection d'un singe géant. Un homme d'affaires sans scrupules parvient à capturer la créature pour l'utiliser comme attraction touristique.

title: Le brise-glace
resume: Un énorme iceberg se dirige vers le brise-glace "Mikhail Gromov". Voulant éviter la collision, le navire est pris dans les glaces et entame une dérive forcée au large de l'Antarctique.

title: Vikingdom: L'Eclipse de sang
resume: Basé sur la mythologie Viking, le film raconte l'histoire du roi Eirick, guerrier légendaire, qui défia le Dieu Thor dans un combat titanesque pour récupérer la corne d'Odin

title: Le roi de la montagne
resume: A group of friends race their high-powered cars up and down a dangerous and deadly mountain road known as Mulholland Drive to see who can claim the title of "King of the Mountain."

title: Sam l'intrépide
resume: Travis, Arliss, and Lisbeth are captured by Apaches while their dog, Sam, tracks their trail.

title: Les Monstres du continent perdu
resume: An Interpol investigation uncovers a shunned biologist, his cyborg daughter, and their monstrous dinosaur, entwined in a alien plot to resurrect Mechagodzilla and construct a new utopia from the ashes of humanity.

title: Les aventures galantes de Robin des Bois
resume: The Erotic Adventures of Robin Hood, his Lusty Men and Bawdy Wenches.

title: Ni no Kuni
resume: High school peers Yuu and Haru travel between the real world and a parallel fantasy universe to help their friend Kotona, whose life is in danger.

title: Lettre à Momo
resume: 11-year-old Momo moves with her mother to a small island town after her father dies. When she arrives, she encounters three goblins that others cannot see who try to help her to cope with the loss of her father and the changes in her life.

title: Fat Pizza
resume: The life at a suburban Sydney pizzeria.

title: Broad Peak
resume: Après avoir gravi le Broad Peak, Maciej Berbeka apprend que son ascension vers le sommet est incomplète. Vingt-cinq ans plus tard, il entend bien finir ce qu'il a commencé.

title: PS 2 - Ponniyin Selvan Partie 2
resume: Arulmozhi Varman poursuit son voyage pour devenir Rajaraja I, le plus grand souverain de l'empire historique Chola, dans le sud de l'Inde.

title: Les aventuriers du timbre perdu
resume: When the joker Tommy Tricker plays some practical jokes on some of his friends, his best friend Ralph, a stamp collector, discovers the secret of "stamp travel" to make him travel around the world on a stamp to bring back the mysterious Charles Merriweather, who never returned on a stamp for 75 years.

title: La vida precoz y breve de Sabina Rivas
resume: At the Mexican-Guatemalan border, young teenage lovers Sabina and Jovany, both Hondurans, accidentally meet again after some years apart. She plans to get to the United States and dreams about being a great singer; he commits all the required atrocities to be accepted by the gang La Mara Salvatrucha. Sabina and Jovany clash with the most adverse conditions at the border, including white slavery, Mexican and American migratory agents Burrona and Patrick, brothel matron Doña Lita, Don Nico the Mexican Consul in Tecún Umán, the drug-trafficking networks, the army, and La Mara Salvatrucha.

title: Barbe-Noire le pirate
resume: Honest Edward Maynard finds himself serving as ship's surgeon under the infamous pirate Blackbeard.

title: The Last Warrior: Root of Evil
resume: Lorsqu'un mal ancien surgit et que l'existence du monde magique est mise en danger, Ivan doit faire équipe avec ses nouveaux rivaux. Ils entreprendront un long voyage pour trouver un moyen de ramener la paix à Belogorie.

title: Lost Soul - The Doomed Journey Of Richard Stanley's Island of Dr. Morea
resume: A behind the scenes chronicle of how clash of vision, bad creative decisions, lack of interest and really bad weather plagued the disastrous production of the infamous L'Île du Dr. Moreau (1996).

title: L'oiseau de paradis
resume: A native girl falls for a visitor to her island, but she's chosen to be sacrificed to the volcano god.

title: Turma da Mônica: Laços
resume: Jimmy Five gathers his friends Monica, Maggy and Smudge to find his kidnapped dog Fluffy.

title: The Saga of the Viking Women and Their Voyage to the Waters of the Great Sea Serpent
resume: A group of lonely Viking women build a ship and set off across the sea to locate their missing menfolk, only to fall into the clutches of the barbarians that also hold their men captive. There is a cameo appearance by the sea serpent.

title: Bender. Nachalo
resume: 1919 year. Fate confronts the young idealist Osya with the Turkish swindler Ibrahim Bender. And the honest Osya would never have contacted such a shameless and cunning swindler if they had not been united by an incredibly dangerous adventure - a hunt for a royal relic, a precious rod, which local bandits and white officers would also like to get. In a series of dizzying adventures, Osya is forced to learn from Ibrahim charming flattery, delicate deception, captivating blackmail and - brute force. And all this - being in love with the purest girl in the city. And, it seems, into one more - a fatal foreign beauty. This is how the portrait of the legendary great schemer and favorite of women, Ostap Bender-Zadunaisky, begins to take shape.

title: The Curious Incident of the Dog in the Night-Time
resume: An autistic 15-year-old replicates the methods of Sherlock Holmes to discover who killed his neighbor's dog with a garden tool.

title: Heavenly Sword
resume: A power-hungry ruler known as King Bohan seeks to obtain the long-protected "Heavenly Sword" in order to use its devastating power for evil. Why doesn't anyone ever use immensely powerful swords for good anymore?

title: Naruto Shippuden, le film : The Lost Tower
resume: Our hero Naruto is caught in special chakra that propels him into the past. He finds himself in the City of Loran. As he encounters strange things, can he save the future with the past?

title: Groupe d'élite
resume: Séville, années 1980. Une escouade de policiers appelée Groupe 7. Rien ne peut leur résister et leurs moyens ne sont pas toujours dans les limites de la loi: la violence, la coercition et les mensonges.

title: Shamshera
resume: Une tribu de guerriers est emprisonnée, réduite en esclavage et torturée par un Shudh Singh autoritaire et impitoyable. Shamshera est une légende pour sa tribu qui se bat sans relâche pour la liberté et la dignité de sa tribu.

title: Dragon Ball Z : Le Robot des glaces
resume: The Z-Fighters must stop a mad scientist out to take over the world.

title: The Seven Deadly Sins: Prisoners of the Sky
resume: The Seven Deadly Sins travel to the Sky Temple in search of an elusive ingredient.

title: Ram Setu
resume: Un archéologue athée devenu croyant doit mener une course contre la montre pour prouver l'existence réelle du légendaire Ram Setu avant que des forces maléfiques ne détruisent ce pilier du patrimoine indien.

title: Opération Marrakech
resume: One of six travelers who catch the bus from Casablanca airport to Marrakesh is carrying $2 million to pay a local operator to fix United Nations votes. But which one?

title: Le dernier missile
resume: After a nuclear war, Phillip Hammer and Marlowe Chandler have spent fifteen years on their own in a bunker, stuffed with junk from the 40s and old detective novels. Now, nineteen-years-old, they leave their shelter to find a world full of mutants, freaks, and cannibals. They become famous detectives in the struggle for the two keys that could fire the last nuclear weapon.

title: L'aventure vient de la mer
resume: En Angleterre, à l'époque de la Restauration, une femme aisée tombe amoureuse d'un beau pirate français, cultivé et même philosophe, et quitte son mari pour vivre toutes sortes d'aventures avec son bien-aimé.

title: La patrouille perdue
resume: Durant la Première Guerre mondiale, une patrouille de militaires traverse le désert de Mésopotamie lorsque leur commandant, le seul à connaître leur destination, est abattu par des bandits cachés.

title: Squanto: A Warrior's Tale
resume: Chronique fictive de la vie de Squanto avant et pendant l'arrivée du "Mayflower" en 1620.

title: The Bay of Silence
resume: Will pense que sa femme Rosalind est innocente du meurtre présumé de leur fils, mais découvre que son passé la lie à un autre crime non résolu.

title: Arachnid
resume: A scientific expedition investigating the outbreak of an unknown viral epidemic on an island in the south Pacific battles with a giant alien spider in the jungle.

title: Les Sables du Kalahari
resume: After a small aircraft crashes in the Kalahari Desert, one of the seven passengers decides that his survival chances would increase if he eliminates the other men in the group.

title: Le trésor de San Lucas
resume: When a levelheaded waitress decides to help her shady friend against her better judgment, she becomes a target of a deadly international gang of thieves who are after a priceless San Lucas' relic. A bumbling stranger helps her.

title: Astérix le Gaulois
resume: Asterix, the most cunning warrior of a Gaulish village resisting Roman occupation, must save their magic potion-brewing druid Getafix when he is kidnapped by an ambitious Centurion.

title: Beau Geste le baroudeur
resume: In 1906, two American brothers join the French Foreign Legion and, led by a sadistic Sergeant-Major, they defend a fort against Berber and Tuareg attack.

title: Bienvenue chez les Loud: Espionner peut attendre
resume: Lincoln and the Louds are ecstatic to welcome their new Gran-Gran, Myrtle, into the family with a tropical wedding celebration, but the festivities are cut short when an old nemesis from Myrtle's secret agent past appears on the island.

title: Apocalypse of Ice
resume: Un vortex polaire menace de recouvrir de glace la Terre. La seule chance de survie est une zone tempérée de 160 km près de l'équateur. Un virologue, avec le seul remède contre la pandémie, doit atteindre la zone dans les 24 heures.

title: Guerrier
resume: Dans un pays déchiré par la guerre où les tribus vivent dans la peur de leur propre disparition, un guerrier mène une guerre destructrice. Quand il est trahi par les siens et laissé pour mort, il est guéri par une mystérieuse princesse.

title: Connected
resume: A man receives a distressing phone call from a woman who has been kidnapped.

title: Bienvenue à Woop Woop
resume: A con artist escapes a deal gone wrong in New York and winds up in the Aussie outback in a strange town whose inhabitants are an oddball collection of misfits.

title: Tracker
resume: An Afrikaner Boer War veteran immigrates to New Zealand. Hired to track a fugitive accused of killing a soldier, he captures him but learns he's innocent. Faced with turning him in or freeing him, only one will survive.

title: Night Hunters
resume: Nick Moon, P.I. (Paranormal Investigator), delves into a hidden world of monsters and creatures of the night as he takes on a case to retrieve an ancient artifact with astonishing power.

title: På rymmen med Pippi Långstrump
resume: Fed up with their strict parents, Tommy and Annika run away from home, with their friend Pippi Longstocking to look after them in their long trek.

title: Remise de peine
resume: Après son veuvage, Frank Fogle s'embarque à contrecœur dans un voyage pour honorer la dernière volonté de sa femme, à savoir répandre ses cendres dans un lac isolé de son Irlande natale, et promettre d'emmener son fils Sean.

title: Are You Being Served?
resume: Le personnel de Grace Bros. se rend à Costa Plonka pendant les travaux de rénovation du département.

title: Fort Ti
resume: Set against the backdrop of the French and Indian war in colonial America, the British soldiers attempt to root out the French Army from Fort Ticonderoga.

title: The Dinosaur Project
resume: A British expedition formed by the lead researcher Jonathan Marchant, his assistant, a doctor and a TV crew, travels to Congo to seek evidence of a dinosaur.

title: Jonas et les Végétaloufs
resume: When the singing Veggies encounter some car trouble, they are stranded at an old rundown seafood joint, where nothing is quite as it seems.

title: Mojin: La légende perdue
resume: En 1969, deux hommes survivent à une tombe surnaturelle. Ils deviennent plus tard des pilleurs de tombes avec Shirley/Shu Qi. Vingt ans plus tard à New York, l'un est engagé pour retrouver cette tombe et les deux amis suivent plus tard.

title: M. Mecanik et les Templiers
resume: Lorsqu'un historien de l'art trouve une ancienne croix templière, il doit s'associer à un groupe d'aventuriers improbables pour tenter de percer les secrets de cette relique.

title: Dans les bras de l'enfer
resume: Col. Cooper leads a group of American P.O.W.s, battling their way to freedom as Saigon falls to the Viet Cong.

title: Mission à Alger
resume: Sherlock Holmes est chargé d'assurer la protection d'un jeune prince héritier jusqu'à son pays d'origine après l'assassinat de son père lors d'un voyage à bord d'un paquebot sur lequel les comploteurs ne manquent pas..

title: Mabok, l'éléphant du diable
resume: A circus lion tamer, his girlfriend, a publicist and a professor travel to the Malayan jungle to find proof to the claim that a beautiful woman raised there might be the rightful heiress to an American family's fortune.

title: Fanfan la Tulipe
resume: France, XVIIIᵉ siècle. Les aventures de Fanfan la Tulipe, jeune recrue de l'armée du roi Louis XV.

title: Her Composition
resume: A talented, artistically stuck composition student starts seeing escort clients after failing to secure her scholarship. Struck with unexpected sounds during her sexual encounters, she turns them into music and the clients into her muse.

title: Hannibal
resume: Lors de la seconde guerre punique en 218 av. J.-C., le général carthaginois Hannibal attaque la République romaine en traversant les Pyrénées et les Alpes avec sa vaste armée.

title: Les Green à Big City le film : Vacances dans l'espace
resume: Après avoir gâché les vacances de sa famille avant même qu'elles ne commencent, Cricket tente de réparer ses erreurs en proposant à sa famille de participer à une mission agricole expérimentale - dans l'espace.

title: Eiga Doraemon: Nobita no getsumen tansaki
resume: Nobita saw a moon turned yellow last night and told his class about it but they think it's funny. Doraemon gives him the "History Explorers Club Badge" and discovers there's life on the moon. Until a new student changed him forever.

title: Le mystère des sables
resume: In 1901, two British yachtsmen visiting Germany's Frisian Islands accidentally discover a German plot to invade England.

title: Survival Quest
resume: A group on an Outward Bound-type adventure runs across a paramilitary team with a sadistic leader who has harmful intentions towards anyone who may find themselves in their path.

title: Kureyon Shinchan: Arashi o Yobu Janguru!
resume: Shin-chan, with her family and friends, travel to island for watch The new movie of his favourite hero. But in this place found a secret organization with a malevolent ideas.

title: Legend Has It
resume: A misfit teenager travels through a magical portal to the Hidden Kingdom, where he discovers his destiny is to become a prophesied warrior, who is said will destroy an ancient evil curse.

title: Samsara
resume: A spiritual love-story set in the majestic landscape of Ladakh, Himalayas. Samsara is a quest; one man's struggle to find spiritual Enlightenment by renouncing the world. And one woman's struggle to keep her enlightened love and life in the world. But their destiny turns, twists and comes to a surprise ending...

title: Petit panda en Afrique
resume: A panda travels from China to Africa, facing hippos, hyenas, gorillas. He rescues his kidnapped dragon friend, makes new friends, and protects their jungle home.

title: Orky : Le Petit Dragon du lac
resume: Two siblings find out about a mythical aquatic monster and try to a save a remote Canadian lake from being used as a dump site for toxic waste.

title: La tente rouge
resume: Déchiré par une culpabilité personnelle, le général italien Umberto Nobile se souvient de son expédition arctique ratée de 1928 à bord du dirigeable Italia.

title: La vengeance aux tripes
resume: A crooked sheriff in a small Southern town frames an ex-convict in a drug bust and takes his girlfriend.

title: Panique à bord
resume: After a boiler explosion aboard an aging ocean liner, a man struggles to free his injured wife from the wreckage of their cabin and ensure the safety of their four-year-old daughter as the ship begins to sink.

title: Boggy Creek II: And the Legend Continues
resume: A professor and three of his students camp out in the wilderness to find a Bigfoot-type creature.

title: Fall 2
resume: Les meilleures amies Grace Caroline Currey et Virginia Gardner reprennent leurs rôles. Leur expertise en escalade et leur détermination à survivre sont mises à l'épreuve par des scénarios risqués au sommet d'une tour de radio.

title: L'île des braves
resume: During WW2, a platoon of Marines crash-lands on a tiny Pacific island occupied by a small Japanese unit.

title: Les rois du soleil
resume: On the coast of the Gulf of Mexico, the Native American tribe of chief Black Eagle clashes with the Mayan tribe of king Balam.

title: Sexmission
resume: Deux scientifiques sont placés en hibernation et censés être réveillés au bout de trois ans. Pourtant lorsqu'ils se réveillent, cinquante ans ont passé et ils sont les deux seuls hommes dans une société nouvelle souterraine composée exclusivement de femmes.

title: Thugs de l'Hindostan
resume: Un voyou envoyé par Lord Clive pour espionner une bande de pirates révolutionnaires indiens les rejoint à l'improviste, ce qui aboutit, entre 1790 et 1805, à une saga épique de révolte et de guerre pour la liberté.

title: Anbe Sivam
resume: Deux hommes, l'un jeune et arrogant, l'autre meurtri - physiquement mais pas psychologiquement - par la vie, sont réunis par les circonstances, et découvrent qu'ils sont en quelque sorte liés par le destin.

title: Tiger Zinda Hai
resume: L'agent Tiger de RAW s'associe à Zoya pour sauver un groupe d'infirmières retenues en otage par une organisation terroriste.

title: Le Tigre du Bengale
resume: Henri Mercier, architecte, est convié à Eschnapur, par le maharadjah Chandra, afin de construire un hôpital. En chemin, il s'énamoure, d'une danseuse dont il a sauvé la vie. Mais, cette dernière est également convoitée par le souverain.

title: Le bras de diamant
resume: An ordinary Soviet citizen accidentally intervenes into a huge operation of international criminal group that trades illegally obtained jewelry.

title: Persephone
resume: The giant ark-ship Odyssey and its ten thousand hibernating settlers have left behind a dying Earth--journeying for fifty years to the nearest star and its lone habitable planet, Proxima b.

title: Dragon Ball Z : Le Combat fratricide
resume: A group of aliens visit Earth to plant the Tree of Might, a plant that grants cosmic power by draining the Earth's life force.

title: Il était une fois en Chine 2 : La Secte du lotus blanc
resume: Wong Fei-Hung, Leung Fu et tante Yee vont à Canton pour assister à une conférence scientifique. Ils trouvent la ville à feu et à sang, victime des assauts terroristes de la secte du Lotus Blanc, un groupe de fanatiques nationalistes.

title: La Légende de Fong Sai-Yuk 2
resume: Le héros cantonais Fong Sai Yuk s'implique dans la confrérie secrète "La Fleur Rouge", qui tente de renverser l'empereur de Mandchourie et de rétablir la dynastie Ming.

title: Frankenstein et les faux-monnayeurs
resume: La famille des Munsters se rend en Angleterre après que Herman découvre qu'il est le nouveau Lord of the Munster Hall.

title: Untitled VeggieTales Project
resume: The third VeggieTales feature film starring LarryBoy.

title: L'Aventure sans retour - L'Odyssée du capitaine Scott
resume: The story of British explorer Robert Falcon Scott's 1912 expedition and his quest to be the first to reach the South Pole.

title: Godzilla, Mothra, Mechagodzilla: Tokyo S.O.S.
resume: Mothra and her fairies return to Japan to warn mankind that they must return Kiryu to the sea, for the dead must not be disturbed. However Godzilla has survived to menace Japan leaving Kiryu as the nation's only defense.

title: Bienvenue chez les Casagrandes: Le film
resume: En voyage au Mexique pour ses 12 ans, Ronnie Anne libère par mégarde une demi-déesse transformée en montagne et compte sur sa famille pour l'aider à arranger les choses.

title: Nebo zovyot
resume: Two countries race to have the first successful landing on Mars.

title: Le Jaguar
resume: Deux Français doivent se rendre en Amérique du Sud pour sauver l'âme du chaman local des forces du mal.

title: La Guerre des yokai
resume: A young boy is chosen as the defender of good and must team up with Japan's ancient spirits and creatures of lore to attempt to destroy the forces of evil.

title: Scarygirl
resume: As her world is shrouded in darkness, a young girl must overcome her fears and travel to a mysterious city of light, save her father from a dangerous scientist and prevent the destruction of her planet.

title: 50 degrés Fahrenheit
resume: A new biological chemical weapon that explodes up to temperatures over fifty degrees Fahrenheit, falls into the hands of two men who try to make sure that it doesn't get stolen by a terrorist.

title: Xiu chun dao II: xiu luo zhan chang
resume: In the Ming dynasty of China, Shen Lian (starring Chang Chen), a secret police of corrupt government, is trapped by the conspiracy on a mission. To prove the innocence, he seeks the truth with a girl called Bei Zhai (starring Yang Mi).

title: Scott, le film
resume: Spot (Lane) is a dog who can talk and read. Posing as a human, he sneaks into school with his master Leonard (Flemming). Educational adventures ensue.

title: Chhota Bheem Master of Shaolin
resume: Bheem and his friends accompany Ming, a monk, to the Shaolin temple to fight against a dangerous Kaifu who wants to take control of the Shaolin temple.

title: AmeriGeddon
resume: A family of dedicated patriots living in the United States decide to defend their country against a terrorist organization that shuts down electricity in America and tries to take over the nation.

title: Skullduggery
resume: A female anthropologist goes on an expedition to a remote location in Papua New Guinea searching for ancient human remains, accompanied by a fortune seeker looking to mine a rare mineral. There, they encounter a new species of ape.

title: Wheels of Fire
resume: In a postapocalyptic future, a ruthless vehicular gang called the Highway Warriors is conquering the wasteland through murder and plunder. During a raid, they kidnap the sister of a road warrior named Trace. He brings hell down upon them.

title: Aventure en Floride
resume: Sandy is distraught when, having saved Flipper by pulling out a spear, his father insists the dolphin be released. A grateful Flipper, however, returns the favor when Sandy is threatened by Sharks.

title: Les aventures de Billy Stone: le médaillon sacré
resume: L'archéologue Michael Stone a passé sa vie à rechercher un médaillon magique. Son fils Billy parvient à le retrouver. Mais une mauvaise manipulation libère son pouvoir. L'adolescent et son amie Allie se retrouvent projetés dans le temps.

title: The Epidemic
resume: Après qu'un météore se soit écrasé sur la croûte terrestre, une épidémie inexpliquée décime la population d'une ville en transformant les gens en zombies.

title: Nukie et Miko
resume: An alien called Nukie searches for his brother Miko, who has been captured by the U.S. government.

title: Caravans
resume: In 1948, at the U.S. embassy in Zadestan, a young diplomat is ordered to find the missing daughter of an influential U.S. Senator.

title: Les Aventuriers du Bout du Monde
resume: Tout en recherchant un trésor perdu, les pirates voyageant dans le temps se retrouvent dans les temps modernes et se battent avec des ennemis improbables: un groupe d'enfants avec les derniers gadgets technologiques.

title: Chasseur de monstres
resume: Human and monsters have lived in their separate worlds, but after the birth of Wuba, the last of the monster kings, begins the adventure to bring the two races together.

title: Détective Conan: Le Fantôme de Baker Street
resume: Conan and his friends were invited to the premier of an new virtual computer game. But someone programmed the game, that if they can't answer the riddle in the game, they all have to die.

title: Van Diemen's Land
resume: Il raconte l'histoire d'Alexander Pearce, le bagnard le plus célèbre d'Australie. En 1822, Pearce et sept de ses compagnons se sont échappés de Macquarie Harbour, un lieu de bannissement et de punition extrêmes.

title: L'ange noir
resume: When Kirk Bennett is convicted of a singer's murder, his wife tries to prove him innocent...aided by the victim's ex-husband.

title: Les Évadés de l'espace
resume: La planète Jillucia a été colonisée par l'empire Gavanas. Le chef des Jilluciens disperse huit noix divines à travers l'univers qui seront capables de découvrir les huit guerriers qui uniront leurs forces pour libérer la planète occupée..

title: Le prince et le pauvre
resume: A poor boy named Tom Canty and the Prince of Wales exchange identities but events force the pair to experience each other's lives as well.

title: The Trip to Spain
resume: Actors Steve Coogan and Rob Brydon embark on a six-part episodic road trip through Europe. This time they're in Spain, sampling the restaurants, eateries, and sights along the way.

title: L'enlèvement de David Balfour
resume: En Écosse, en 1751, le jeune David Balfour est embarqué à bord d'un navire où il rencontre le rebelle jacobite Alan Breck Stewart avec qui il s'échappe vers les Highlands écossais en évitant les tuniques rouges.

title: One Piece: L'Aventure sans issue
resume: Luffy and his gang finds out about and joins the death race DeadEnd and the ex-marine Gasparde and the bounty hunter Shuraiya clash as the conspiracy of the race unfolds.

title: Godzilla vs. Mothra
resume: Japan is caught in the middle of a three way battle between Godzilla, the divine Mothra, and her dark counterpart Battra.

title: Félix le chat, le film
resume: In another dimension, the villainous scientist Duke of Zill, with the help of his mechanical, geometric army, takes over the Land of Oriana, prompting Felix the Cat to save its princess and restore order once again.

title: Der Prank
resume: A 12-year-old boy and his Chinese exchange student's April Fool's prank escalates into mayhem, entangling them with gangsters and inept police officers.

title: Vanished
resume: When millions of people begin to disappear, Gabby, her sister, and their other companions will have to stick together for survival and to figure out what happened behind an indescribable occurrence.

title: Il était une fois en Chine : Dr Wong en Amérique
resume: Wong Fei-Hung part rendre visite à l'un de ses disciples, qui habite en Amérique. Au cours d'une attaque indienne, il est frappé à la tête et perd la mémoire.

title: The City of Gold
resume: An anguished media magnate, Jonathan Davenport, accompanies his estranged lover to the Peruvian Amazon in pursuit of a reclusive artist living in rebel occupation. Despite their philanthropic intentions, the mission proves to be the harbinger of something dark and ominous rooted deep within Jonathan.

title: Le froussard héroïque
resume: Harry Flashman est contraint par Otto von Bismark de se faire passer pour un prince. Bismarck tente d'assassiner Flashman et le prince afin de réaliser l'unification des États allemands.

title: Bolt from the Blue
resume: An overlooked engineer is sent to Alaska to scope out an eccentric scientist's claim that capturing lightning can be a new source of renewable energy.

title: Le Roi cerf
resume: Une meute de loups, transportant une étrange maladie, laisse Van, un guerrier réduit en esclavage, et une petite fille du nom de Yuna, seuls survivants de l'attaque d'une mine de sel. Leur survie intéresse alors les puissants du royaume.

title: Minor Details
resume: Four best friends at a boarding school try to solve the brewing mystery.

title: 749 Ju
resume: A traumatized young man with physical abnormalities is forced to join a mysterious bureau to confront a disaster spreading across the earth caused by an unknown creature. He embarks on an adventure uncovering mysteries about his life.

title: Les dents du diable
resume: Un Esquimau qui a eu peu de contacts avec des hommes blancs se rend dans un poste de traite où il tue accidentellement un missionnaire et se retrouve poursuivi par la police.

title: Le banni des îles
resume: Après s'être livré à des malversations financières, un Britannique décide de fuir son pays. Avec la complicité d'un vieil ami, la capitaine Lindgard, il embarque sur un bateau en direction de l'Orient.

title: La chevauchée terrible
resume: After selling his cattle in town, ranch owner Morgan unexpectedly dies, and his foreman Pike has to deliver the payroll to Sonora, despite the perilous journey during which he's followed by many shady characters who want the money.

title: Küss mich, Monster
resume: KISS ME, MONSTER finds The Red Lips moonlighting on a striptease world tour - but no sooner do they hit the stage than the girls are up to their pasties in stiffs, Satanists and Sapphic sadists, all after a secret formula for human clones!

title: Dasavatharam
resume: Dans ce film où Kamal Haasan interprète 10 rôles, un scientifique découvre un virus qui peut détruire le monde. La suite du film est une course poursuite entre lui et Fletcher, un homme engagé pour l'arrêter et reprendre le virus.

title: Dolce pelle di Angela
resume: Naive, orphaned maiden Angela leaves her small town for 19th- century London, where she quickly learns the ways of the world. She begins work at a brothel, where she gets a quick education in life. On her first "job," she is rescued by Rocco, a traveling thief who happens to be going from room to room, robbing the patrons. Rocco and Angela fall in love, but Rocco must flee the inn at which they have taken residence, when the police arrive at the door...

title: La Main de la momie
resume: Des archéologues profanent la tombe du momifié Kharis, qui a été enterré vivant pour être tombé amoureux d'une princesse égyptienne.

title: Les 12 Travaux d'Astérix
resume: César lance un défi aux irréductible Gaulois: ils devront réaliser 12 travaux, impossibles mais différents de ceux d'Hercule. S'ils réussissent, César quittera le pouvoir. Sinon, ils devront se soumettre. Astérix et Obélix s'y collent.

title: Posljednji Srbin u Hrvatskoj
resume: Croatia, seven years after bankruptcy. There is a fight going on in the world - water has become more precious than oil. In order to get hold of it, the powerful are ready to start wars, conquer, destroy, and even plant a zombie-virus. Mico, a bon viveur from Zagreb, whose daily routine includes massage parlours, restaurants and cinemas, where he watches a movie series featuring his favorite actress Franka Anic, is caught completely off guard by the zombie-epidemics. Nevertheless, he boldly embarks on an Odyssey accompanied by his movie heroine, with one highly unattainable, goal: to survive.

title: Panther Squad
resume: Une escouade de mercenaires féminins prend le contrôle d'une organisation appelée Space Clean, qui se consacre à l'arrêt de l'exploration spatiale.

title: L'empreinte du loup solitaire
resume: Ex-safecracker Michael Lanyard now works legally, but an old rival frames him for stealing secret documents. He's caught between seductive Karen and loyal girlfriend Val Carson.

title: Sahara
resume: Un jeune cobra et son meilleur ami scorpion partent en voyage à travers le désert du Sahara afin de sauver un nouvel amour.

title: Daveed
resume: A middle-aged bouncer named Ashiq Abu enters a fierce rivalry with Turkish boxer Sainul Akhmadov, leading him through a personal journey of redemption and determination.

title: Les Bisounours II - Une nouvelle génération
resume: The Care Bears try to help a young girl at summer camp who, in an effort to revamp her dorky social status to agility and skill, enters into a sinister bargain with a shape-shifting demon posing as a young boy.

title: The Wizard Hunter: The Hunt for Evangelion Crowley
resume: A bounty hunter of lost masterpieces is at the end of his tasks. But one last assignment by a mysterious Countess will force him to discover his dark legacy.

title: Les chiens à l'opéra
resume: Moscow, early 20th century. The stray dog Samson, running away from animal catchers, finds himself in the Bolshoy Theater. So the main character gets acquainted with the dog of the prima ballerina, after which he helps to return the stolen decoration of the hostess.

title: Irish Dog
resume: A London nightclub bouncer reluctantly agrees to chaperone an old friend on a trip to Spain, only to find himself navigating a dangerous reunion of criminal power players, testing his resolve to leave his violent past behind.

title: Gekijouban Ano hi mita hana no namae wo bokutachi wa mada shiranai.
resume: A group of friends were separated when one of them died in an accident. Later on she comes back as a ghost trying to get into heaven but to do that her friends must grant her a wish.

title: Astérix et les Indiens
resume: Sent out to prevent Getafix from being thrown off the edge of the Earth by the Romans, Asterix and Obelix find themselves in America, encountering a Native tribe and a greedy medicine man.

title: Le prisonnier de Zenda
resume: In order to save King Rudolph of Ruritania from assassins and murderous usurpers, the kingdom hires a look-a-like London cabby to impersonate the Monarch.

title: Mutant Year Zero
resume: A four quadrant action adventure, based on the popular video game of the same name.

title: 13 Frightened Girls
resume: While attending a school for diplomats' daughters, the teen-aged daughter of the American ambassador uses her access to various embassies to engage in espionage.

title: Cuando los ángeles duermen
resume: Un PDG vit la pire nuit de sa vie après un accident de voiture

title: Minions & More 2
resume: Catch animated shorts like "Phil's Dance Party" and "Binky Nelson Unpacified" in this compilation from the company behind the "Despicable Me" franchise.

title: Kis Vuk
resume: Little Jack is a young fox living happily with his family in the woods, but everything changes when his father is captured by a circus troupe in order to be part of their show. The rest of the animals from the wood will share the same destiny. With the help from a nature-loving disabled boy in a wheelchair and a young acrobat girl, Little Jack will try to rescue the animals.

title: Les évadées
resume: Abused female prisoners at an all-women's prison camp in the tropics plot revenge against their sadistic overseers.

title: Und nächstes Jahr am Balaton
resume: A true road movie. Set in the 1970-s, in Communist Central Europe. An East German guy with a Dutch girl -- hitchhiking their way, with all sorts of adventures. This movie feels like you're on a holiday yourself.

title: Crayon Shin-chan: Unkokusai no Yabou
resume: A Time Patrol agent stranded in modern Japan enlists the Nohara family's help. Their journey to feudal Japan leads to an unexpected encounter with a samurai seeking allies against a mysterious foe.

title: Les aventures de Yogi le nounours
resume: In the end, Ranger Smith on the helicopter take Yogi, Boo Boo and Cindy home from the tallest building.

title: The Art of Flight
resume: Two years in the making, this film gives snowboarder Travis Rice and friends the opportunity to redefine what is possible in the mountains.

title: El valiente vive... hasta que el cobarde quiere
resume: L'arrivée d'une nouvelle institutrice dans une petite ville provoque divers bouleversements.

title: Wolfboy
resume: Suit un jeune garçon qui s'enfuit de chez lui à la recherche de sa mère, dont il est séparé.

title: Les Rebelles de la forêt 4
resume: Elliot, Boog and all of the beloved woodland creatures are back in a brand-new comedy adventure.

title: Dragon Inn
resume: Lorsque les enfants d'un général exécuté sont pourchassés en 1457 en Chine, d'héroïques experts de l'épée et des arts martiaux interviennent pour les sauver.

title: La panthère des neiges
resume: En haut du plateau tibétain, au milieu de vallées inexplorées et inaccessibles, se trouve l'un des derniers sanctuaires du monde sauvage, où vit une faune rare et inconnue: le léopard des neiges.

title: Le dernier loup
resume: Pendant la révolution culturelle chinoise, un jeune étudiant urbain est envoyé vivre avec des bergers mongols, où il adopte un louveteau.

title: En route pour le Maroc
resume: Two carefree castaways on a desert shore find an Arabian Nights city, where they compete for the luscious Princess Shalmar.

title: Doraemon: Nobita to midori no kyojinden
resume: Nobita finds a small plant still in a container at an abandoned area and decides to take it home. His mother asks him not to put it on their garden because it won't have space to properly grow. Therefore he asks Doraemon for help. The robot cat then uses a special plant converter from the future that will allow the plant to move freely without the need to form roots attached to the ground. Named "Kibou" (Hope), the small green creature gleefully plays with Nobita and his friends. The group is taken by surprise when they are suddenly transported to another planet governed by a society of plant beings. Doraemon and his friends then discover that due to mankind's mistreatment of nature, the green population is planning to remove all plants from Earth. They must now return home and find a way to save the world.

title: Boys Club
resume: In Ontario, Canada, three fourteen-year-old boys, Kyle, Brad and Eric are forced to perform an ordeal when they find a wounded mysterious fugitive named Luke, who has a gun and claiming to be a cop, has taken a hiding in their clubhouse.

title: Sindbad le marin
resume: In medieval Persia, during the rule of Caliph Harun-Al-Rashid, Sinbad the Sailor boasts about his latest adventures to his friends.

title: Gridman Universe
resume: Follows Yuta who repeatedly drew and then erased Gridman in his notebook, which he vaguely remembers. Then he decided to confess his feelings to Rikka, and their life in such a peaceful world begins to crumble with a roar.

title: Les Nibelungen : La Vengeance de Kriemhild
resume: Princess Kriemhild vows to avenge her husband's murder but must overcome her brothers who swore allegiance to Hagen. She marries Etzel, King of the Huns, and persuades his army to attack Hagen, but she loses more than she bargained for.

title: Posledniy bogatyr. Poslannik tmy
resume: Now that Ivan is about to turn 21, he is now grown up and finally old enough to marry the beautiful Vasilisa. But when Vasilisa is kidnapped and trapped in modern Moscow, Ivan and his friends must travel to the present day to rescue her.

title: Le petit chaperon rouge
resume: The faithful little girl must brave the forest and the big, bad wolf to bring her grandmother a basket of goodies in this musical version of the classic fairytale.

title: Doraemon: Nobita no Nihon tanjô
resume: Nobita and his friends ran away from home, went to Japan of a primitive era by Doraemon's time machine and created their own paradise in there. However, there was the Spirit King Giga-Zombie which manipulated the frightening power freely. They Help a primitive boy and confront Giga-Zombie.

title: Ahl Al Kahf
resume: The film deals with a fictional framework, the story of three people who wake up from their sleep after three centuries, and find themselves in a time other than the time in which they lived before, and they live in a struggle with time.

title: Les chats au musée
resume: The cat Vincent and mouse friend escape a flood in a harpsichord, arriving at the Hermitage. Elite guard cats protect the art from mice. When the Mona Lisa arrives, Vincent must stop it being stolen and win over Cleopatra cat.

title: Shaan
resume: Two brothers go after the international mafia kingpin who murdered their cop brother. They are later joined by another man who wants revenge against the gangster.

title: Majo no takkyûbin
resume: A young witch, on her mandatory year of independent life, finds fitting into a new community difficult while she supports herself by running an air courier service.

title: Rainbow Brite and the Star Stealer
resume: Rainbow Brite must stop an evil princess and her underlings from taking over the planet Spectra.

title: La Croisée des destins
resume: Peu de temps avant l'indépendance de l'Inde, Victoria Jones, une métisse, est victime d'une tentative de viol. Elle tue son agresseur, un soldat anglais, et trouve refuge auprès d'activistes indiens.

title: La prophétie des ténèbres
resume: SPOILER: A rabbi in Jerusalem develops software that can unlock prophecies in the Torah. He's murdered and the software stolen. A powerful man uses it to gain world domination.

title: Maya l'abeille 2: Les jeux du miel
resume: Lorsque Maya, trop enthousiaste, embarrasse l'Impératrice de Buzztropolis, elle est obligée de faire équipe avec des insectes marginaux et de participer aux Jeux du Miel pour tenter de sauver sa ruche.

title: L'extraordinaire évasion
resume: A British prisoner of war working at a zoo gets the chance to escape from the Germans, so he does and takes with him the elephant that he's been caring for. Together, they head for the Swiss border and freedom.

title: Détective Conan: Le Sniper Dimensionnel
resume: Un tireur d'élite cible Shuichi Akai et tire sur Masumi Sera. Les citoyens de Tokyo paniquent. On ne sait rien du mystérieux tireur d'élite. Personne ne sait pourquoi Masumi a été ciblé.

title: Burn Your Maps
resume: A family in emotional turmoil is taken by surprise in this quirky adventure where an eccentric 8-year-old American boy, Wes, has an existential epiphany - He believes that he is in fact a Mongolian goat herder.

title: Le premier rebelle
resume: In 1759, in Pennsylvania's Allegheny Valley, local settlers and Indian fighters try to persuade the British authorities to ban the trading of alcohol and arms with the marauding Indians.

title: Powwow Highway
resume: Two Northern Cheyenne men take a road trip from Montana to New Mexico to bail out the sister of one of them who has been framed and arrested in Santa Fe. On the way, they begin to reconnect to their spiritual heritage.

title: Four Men and a Prayer
resume: The sons of a disgraced British officer try to clear his name.

title: Sasquatch: The Legend of Bigfoot
resume: Scientists mount an expedition to find a Bigfoot-type creature.

title: Napoléon en Australie
resume: Les aventures du chiot Golden Retriever Napoléon et de son ami, le perroquet Birdo Lucci.

title: Kill Buljo: Ze Film
resume: Une parodie norvégienne de Kill Bill.

title: Le prince et le pauvre
resume: Two boys, one a prince and one a poor boy, change places.

title: La maîtresse de fer
resume: The exploits of nineteenth-century pioneer Jim Bowie after settling in New Orleans.

title: Percy Jackson and the Titan's Curse
resume: This is a fan-made film based on the Percy Jackson series by Rick Riordan. This third adventure in the series finds Percy faced with his most dangerous challenge yet: The chilling prophecy of The Titan's Curse.

title: Tsarevna-lyagushka
resume: In a pond in a city park there lived a frog who really loved watching films in the summer cinema. And then one day she saw a cartoon about how someone like her caught an arrow and turned into a beautiful girl. The frog also decided to catch the arrow, however, instead of it she caught... a golf ball, but still turned into a beautiful girl.

title: La valise
resume: Sentant sa vie menacée au cours d'une mission, l'espion israélien Bloch doit être rapatrié en France. Le capitaine Augier est chargé de le faire sortir clandestinement du pays. Pour cela, il doit être enfermé dans une valise diplomatique.

title: Le roi des singes
resume: Sun Wukong, the King of the Monkeys, sets off on his first adventure to gain a worthy weapon. This earns the attention of the Jade Emperor of Heaven.

title: Smile
resume: High school student Katie signs up for a trip to China, where she meets Lin, who has a facial deformity that discourages her from ever showing her face, but her friendship with Katie helps her start to see life in a new way.

title: Jue ji
resume: An orphan becomes the disciple of a powerful sorcerer and is drawn into a larger conflict among the world's magical elite.

title: Anthony Adverse
resume: In 18th-century Italy, an orphan's debt to the man who raised him threatens to separate him forever from the woman he loves.

title: Eiga Doraemon: Shin Nobita no Nippon tanjou
resume: Doraemon and friends trying to save a boy name Kukuru and his tribe from Gigazombie who want to change history for his own sake in the ancient times.

title: The Last Island
resume: Cinq hommes et deux femmes, survivants d'un accident d'avion, découvrent qu'ils sont peut-être les seuls survivants d'une catastrophe mondiale.

title: Land Shark
resume: Lucinda Regis, Director of Development at MALCO Oceanic Research, becomes the target of a dangerous killer after unraveling a sinister plot to inject sharks with human DNA.

title: Dauntless: L'Enfer de Midway
resume: En juin 1942, la marine japonaise a balayé le Pacifique. Pour changer le cours de la guerre, un groupe de transporteurs américain est positionné au large de Midway prêt à piéger leur ennemi.

title: Opération Pingouins
resume: Inspiré d'une histoire vraie. Un grand-père, sa petite fille et un gros toutou tout à fait craquant unissent leurs efforts pour sauver une réserve de pingouins.

title: Deti protiv volshebnikov
resume: Magic is slowly corrupting the world. In order to save Russia from the same fate, Ivan Tsaritsin with some help from his friends, will try to put an end to this.

title: Alice in Wonderland
resume: Musical under wraps.

title: Cabo Blanco
resume: Un tenant de bar intrépide aide une jeune et belle femme à retrouver son ancien amant et sa fortune disparue.

title: El hombre del saco
resume: Explores the Spanish origins of the character's story, where he is a tuberculosis patient from Almeria who will do anything to get well, even consuming the blood of the kids he kidnaps in a sack.

title: Super Mario Bros. : La Grande Mission pour sauver la princesse Peach !
resume: The Mario Bros.Mario and Luigi go to another dimension, and must now rescue Princess Peach from King Bowser Koopa.

title: Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them 5
resume: The fifth installment of the 'Fantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them' series which follows the adventures of Newt Scamander.

title: Dünya Varmis
resume: Dunya Varmis begins 24 hours before a deadly pandemic threatens to wipe out all life on Earth. A secret organization known as "The Ancients," possessing knowledge of future events, constructs a hidden sanctuary for a select group of individuals to survive the impending apocalypse. As the chosen ones gather in the sanctuary, disguised as a luxurious hotel, they face days filled with suspense, intrigue, and unexpected revelations.

title: Theeb: La naissance d'un chef
resume: Dans la province ottomane d'Hijaz pendant la Première Guerre mondiale, un jeune Bédouin s'embarque dans une dangereuse aventure initiatique à travers le désert pour guider un officier britannique vers sa destination secrète.

title: Les Aventuriers de l'univers perdu
resume: Trois personnes sont transportées dans une réalité parallèle, où elles découvrent qu'elles doivent utiliser la technologie moderne, mais des armes médiévales, afin de sauver les citoyens d'un seigneur de guerre meurtrier.

title: Rice Girl
resume: Windy Yee is a dimwitted actress desperately tries to land a big role in Director Martini's new movie, Hooker X.

title: Bing feng: Yong heng zhi men
resume: La garde impériale et ses trois amis d'enfance traîtres ordonnés de le traquer sont accidentellement enterrés et restent figés dans le temps. Quatre cents ans plus tard, ils sont décongelés et continuent la bataille qu'ils ont laissée derrière eux.

title: Doubles masques et agents doubles
resume: The British secret service hire a WWII veteran to voluntarily kidnap and smuggle a 13-year-old Arab prince into Spain. Once there, a gullible American mercenary is hired to protect him, but greed threatens to spoil the operation.

title: Made in Abyss: Hôrô Suru Tasogare
resume: After departing from Ozen's camp, Riko and Reg continue their journey, encountering more dangers as they descend further into the Abyss.

title: Easy Rider: the Ride Back
resume: Family drama spanning decades follows the Williams clan connected through motorcycle passion. No analysis, just their struggle to bond amid internal conflicts from the 1940s to present.

title: Kureyon Shinchan: Bakumori! Kanfe Boizu Ramen Tairan
resume: Shin-chan and the Kasukabe Defense Group are planning to perform an absolutely no-stunt Kung Fu challenge on the stage in Aiya Town, also known as the Chinatown of Kasukabe city.

title: Les mille et une nuits
resume: Le calife de Bagdad doit se cacher avec un groupe d'artistes ambulants lorsque son frère usurpe le trône. Les deux frères désirent une belle danseuse, qui est déchirée entre le pouvoir et le véritable amour.

title: The Boxcar Children
resume: Four children set out on a journey to find a new home.

title: L'île au trésor
resume: Le jeune Jim Hawkins est déchiré entre sa loyauté envers ses bienfaiteurs et son affection pour l'aimable pirate John Silver dans leur combat pour retrouver un trésor de pirate enfoui.

title: Les aventures fantastiques du Baron Munchhausen
resume: This lavish, impudent, adult fairy tale takes the viewer from 18th-century Braunschweig to St. Petersburg, Constantinople, Venice, and then to the moon using ingenious special effects, stunning location shooting.

title: Los verduleros 4
resume: A police commander fails to drag in a dangerous drug cartel, despite using all the (limited) equipment at his disposal, and his best detectives as infiltrated agents. It's then that old cops must come out of retirement and do the job - helped by a number of sexy young girls.

title: Miniforce: Deeno the King of Dinosaurs
resume: A boy named Yang revives and befriends an injured T-Rex, forming an alliance with Miniforce to defeat an invading army of dinosaurs.

title: L'année de la comète
resume: An auctioneer's daughter and a rich buyer's emissary fall for each other while trying to keep a rare wine out of the hands of evil doers.

title: Shôjo kakumei Utena: Adolescence mokushiroku
resume: Utena Tenjou, a mysterious transfer student, gets drawn into duels at Ohtori Academy to win the hand of the Rose Bride and the power to bring on a revolution in this retelling of the surrealist Shoujo classic.

title: Galaxy Express 999
resume: Les aventures d'un jeune garçon courageux qui voyage de planète en planète dans une quête déterminée pour venger la mort de sa mère.

title: El cuarto pasajero
resume: 50-year-old Julian, divorced and with a cash problem, offers a car-sharing service from Bilbao to Madrid. Having fallen in love with his constant passenger Lorena, his troubles start with the two strangers joining in for the ride.

title: Carry on Columbus
resume: History is only slightly rewritten: instead of experienced sailors, there are only convicts whose last and only meeting with H2O was their prison diet of bread and water. And Columbus doesn't have his own map.

title: Le chevalier du dragon
resume: Princess Alba is abducted by a dragon, and it's up to Klever to save her. But, it turns out that this dragon is an alien spacecraft, and Alba falls in love with the human-alien inside it.

title: Elli and the Ghostly Ghost Train
resume: All Elli wanted was a family to love. But finding one turns out to be a ghostly affair.

title: Cetvrti covek
resume: A man awakens from a two-month-long coma with total amnesia and sets out to discover the truth about his identity.

title: Exodos 1826
resume: Captain Mihos Floros returns to Samarina to gather more men and lead them to the besieged by the Ottomans, Missolonghi, in order to assist the fight of the resistance at General Makris' bastion.

title: Hero Dog: The Journey Home
resume: Chinook the Alaskan Malamute must lead a shipwrecked blind man out of the wilderness, while the man's children launch a rescue mission of their own.

title: Poliorkia
resume: Inspired by the story of the battle of Dovra monastery in 1822 in Veria, Greece, the love story of two young Greeks unfolds as they prepare to secretly get married in a church that is surrounded by Turkish troops.

title: M. Smith agent secret
resume: Le professeur Horatio Smith, même s'il semble très modeste, sauve les victimes des persécutions nazies pendant la Seconde Guerre mondiale.

title: Félins: Le royaume du courage
resume: Un documentaire sur la nature centré sur deux familles de félins et la manière dont elles enseignent à leurs petits les dangers de la vie sauvage.

title: Ang panday
resume: A young blacksmith realizes his destiny when a malevolent demon bent on ruling the world unleashes an army of creatures on humanity.

title: Les débiles de l'espace
resume: A trio of moronic aliens crash-land on Earth and become celebrities, while a fourth alien, who arrives separately, finds himself ignored.

title: Ironmaster, la guerre du fer
resume: Un homme violent est expulsé de sa tribu après avoir tué deux de ses aînés. Il découvre un moyen de fabriquer des armes en fer et commence à faire la guerre aux tribus de la région. Son rival parvient à s'échapper et jure de l'arrêter.

title: L'Odyssée sous la mer
resume: When an underwater ocean lab is lost in a earthquake, an advanced submarine is sent down to find it and encounters terrible danger.

title: Manina, la fille sans voiles
resume: Gérard, a young student, discovers a fragment from a Phoenician amphora in Corsica. Several years later he sets off on a smuggling boat, looking for the treasure he thinks he has found. When he get back to island, he falls in love.

title: Le vol du corbeau
resume: An Irish man seeks vengeance against the vikings who killed his parents.

title: Satu - Year of the Rabbit
resume: When a bomb endangers the Pha Tang temple, 'Satu' an orphan child laborer decides to head north through the rich and feral landscape of Laos in search of his long lost mother with his new photojournalist friend 'Bo'.

title: Les échappés du néant
resume: Lorsqu'un avion commercial atterrit de force dans une jungle sud-américaine, les passagers et les pilotes doivent réparer les moteurs et fuir la zone infestée de cannibales.

title: Go Goa Gone
resume: A group of friends, just looking to have a good time in a rave party on a remote island in Goa, find out that the island is infested with Zombies.

title: Le corps et le fouet
resume: Une bande de délinquantes est envoyée dans une prison dirigée par la directrice sadique Carla. Contraintes à des situations de perversion sexuelle, de violence et de torture, elles tentent de renverser Carla et s'échapper de prison.

title: Salut l'ami, adieu le trésor !
resume: Sur une petite île du Pacifique, Alan et Charlie tentent de trouver un trésor de guerre laissé par l'armée japonaise pendant la Seconde Guerre mondiale.

title: L'ornithologue
resume: Fernando, un ornithologue solitaire, recherche des cigognes noires lorsqu'il est emporté par les rapides. Secouru par deux jeunes Chinoises en pèlerinage, il s'engouffre dans une forêt sombre et mystérieuse pour retrouver son chemin.

title: Why me? Un plan d'enfer
resume: A jewel thief steals a sacred ruby which sets off a chase by the police, the Turkish government, nutty American terrorists, and the C.I.A.

title: Spy School
