resume: Doubting Thomas is the story of a twelve year old boy known for telling tall tales who overhears a plot to kidnap the President's daughter. When he goes public with his story, no one believes him, and he is forced to save her on his own.

title: Hangmen
resume: Rob Greene has information about an undercover terror team inside the CIA led by Joe Connelly. To stay alive with the knowledge, he is advised to stay undercover by his supervisor Andrews. Connelly's men try to kill Greene, but he can escape and warns his son Danny that he also may be in danger and that he should look for Dog Thompson, an old military friend of Greene's. Together with Thompson and Bone Conn, another ex-soldier, Danny tries to escape Connelly's henchmen. Meanwhile, Connelly figures that Danny's friend Lisa would make a good target in order to get Danny and also his father.

title: La lance brisée
resume: Un éleveur de l'Arizona dirige son ranch et élève ses enfants de manière tyrannique. Alors qu'il est sur le point de mourir, son fils aîné se rebelle contre lui et reprend le ranch.

title: The Crimson Ghost
resume: A criminal mastermind known as the Crimson Ghost is out to steal a device called the Cyclotrode, which can short-circuit every electrical current on the planet.

title: Raavan
resume: A bandit leader kidnaps the wife of the policeman who killed his sister, but later falls in love with her.

title: Severnyy polyus
resume: The beginning of the 1960s, a period of aggravation of the confrontation between the USSR and the USA. In the most difficult weather conditions and with malfunctions on board, the first Soviet nuclear submarine K-3 sets off for a hike under the ice of the Arctic Ocean in order to surface exactly at the North Pole.

title: Les Vikings
resume: Vikings compete for power and the love of a woman.

title: Tyrannosaurus Azteca
resume: A band of 16th century conquistadors must fight for their lives when they realize they're going to be served as sacrifices to a god-like T-Rex.

title: Persona 3 the Movie: #1 Spring of Birth
resume: In the spring, male student Makoto Yuki transfers to Gekkoukan High School. However, as he heads to his new dormitory, listening to the music on his headphones, he is stopped. More precisely, time has stopped, and the people who were around him turn into coffins. Makoto learns that this period of time hidden between the minute of midnight is called the Dark Hour, a time when monsters called Shadows appear. Suddenly made the leader of his fellow classmates Yukari and Junpei by his upperclassmen Mitsuru and Akihiko, Makoto must learn empathy, his connection to his comrades, and the meaning of death. With the power of his Evoker aimed at his head, Makoto fights against the Shadows threatening to attack his world from the mysterious tower of Tartarus.

title: Tini: La nouvelle vie de Violetta
resume: Violetta returns from a worldwide tour to unexpected news. Finding herself at a crossroads, she is forced to question everything.

title: Jojo Bizarre Adventure Diamond Is Unbreakable Chapitre 1
resume: Un adolescent doué de pouvoirs surnaturels découvre la vérité de son lignage bizarre et maudit, et le mal qui se cache dans sa ville.

title: Wild Men
resume: Dans une tentative désespérée de guérir sa crise de la quarantaine, Martin a fui sa famille pour vivre dans les montagnes norvégiennes afin de chasser et cueillir comme ses ancêtres le faisaient il y a des milliers d'années.

title: Saladin
resume: After Saladin's victory over the King of Jerusalem, a peace treaty is signed between them, but the commander of the Crusader army, Renaud de Chatillon, slaughters a group of pilgrims going to Mecca. Saladin then decides to take revenge.

title: What's My Name?
resume: Lorsqu'un homme se réveille du coma, il doit reconstruire son identité et son sens en affrontant des adversaires emblématiques de sa carrière, jusqu'à l'affrontement final.

title: Railroad Tigers
resume: Un groupe de guerilleros travaille sur la voie ferrée pendant la guerre du Pacifique. Ils volent les effets des soldats japonais pour stopper le transport des armes japonaises. . .

title: Crystal Fairy y el cactus mágico
resume: As Jamie travels in Chile, he invites an eccentric woman to join his group's quest to score a fabled hallucinogen, a move that finds him at odds with his new companion, until they drink the magic brew on a beach at the edge of the desert.

title: Le mystère de la troisième planète
resume: Zoologist professor Steel, his small daughter Christine and captain Green leave Earth in search for rare space animals. The journey turns into adventurous and dangerous mission involving space pirates and a missing captain of a ship.

title: Le livre érotique de la jungle
resume: A private detective journeys to Africa to find a legenday white gorilla. The gorilla turns out to be an escaped Nazi war criminal.

title: Crayon Shin-chan: Mononoke Ninja Chinpuden
resume: The film features Shinnosuke as a ninja, and will reveal if Shinnosuke is the real son of Hiroshi and Misae.

title: Huckleberry Finn
resume: In 1840s Missouri, young Huckleberry Finn, wanting to escape his violent drunkard father, joins Black runaway slave Jim on a quest for freedom down the Mississippi River on a raft.

title: Le Souffle sauvage
resume: In South America, after Jeff Dawson and Dutch Peterson's oil rigs are dynamited by local bandits, the two partners resort to risky transportation of nitroglycerin to raise money.

title: Baba Yaga: La forêt des damnés
resume: Lorsque la mère d'Egor meurt, il a une belle-mère, puis une petite demi-soeur. Les choses deviennent sérieusement tordues lorsque son père obtient une nounou sexy, qui est la sorcière Baba Yaga.

title: À cor et à cri
resume: Joe Kirby découvre par hasard une bande de trafiquants dont le chef mystérieux utilise le "Trump", un journal pour enfants, pour transmettre ses ordres. Joe et ses copains mènent l'enquête..

title: La grande aventure de Maya l'abeille
resume: Maya est une petite abeille au grand coeur? Rejoignez-la dans son aventure épique.

title: Fuga scabrosamente pericolosa
resume: The daughter of a rich farmer is kidnapped by a fugitive. She is raped and brutalized but finally gets her revenge.

title: Thorvald le Viking
resume: An eleventh century Viking Prince sails to America to find his father, who on a previous voyage had been captured by Indians.

title: Iron Warrior
resume: Ator and his brother are separated as children by the evil witch Phoedra. 18 years later, she takes over the kingdom with the help of a masked warrior. Ator rescues the rightful heir princess Janna, and they struggle to topple the witch.

title: Zhang chao
resume: Khepri Cockroach Tide is a biological disaster online movie. It tells the story of the super cockroach, which was originally developed to deal with environmental problems, but during transportation it's starting attack humans

title: Doraemon Nobita no Takarajima
resume: Upon hearing about the story of Treasure Island, Nobita dreams of discovering and exploring his own treasure island, despite the fact all of the Earth has been mapped already.

title: Snezhnaya Koroleva. Razmorozka
resume: Kai and Gerda live in a cozy quiet town, suddenly the Icy Spirits come there to freeze everyone. However, Ila, a little wizardess, comes up to help the heroes. Together they go to the magic world of Mirrorland to get the Icy Spirits back.

title: Les chevaliers du futur
resume: In the future, a kickboxer and a robot lead a revolution against ruling cyborgs.

title: Babes with Blades
resume: Situé sur la planète Draiga, ce film d'action steampunk met en scène des femmes artistes martiales de classe mondiale et suit Azura qui tente de sauver sa race mourante.

title: Zatôichi, le masseur aveugle
resume: The adventures of a blind, gambling masseur who also happens to be a master swordsman.

title: La petite sirène
resume: A mermaid falls in love with a human prince, which leads to tragedy.

title: 5 cm
resume: Five best friends try to find out what true friendship is by climbing Mount Semeru, the highest peak in Java.

title: Les agents 007 1/2
resume: Duncan Jax is facing his most challenging mission ever, to save the world from evil terrorists!

title: La brigade héroïque
resume: Dans l'ouest canadien de 1877, un inspecteur de police se révolte contre son commandant inepte, empruntant une route plus sûre vers la frontière américaine afin d'arrêter l'invasion d'Indiens hostiles.

title: L'enfer blanc du Piz Palu
resume: Un homme escalade une montagne de 3600 mètres à la recherche de sa femme, perdue lors de leur lune de miel. Un autre couple grimpe avec lui.

title: Z Experiments - Les Origines de la monstruosité
resume: Une mission de sauvetage du jour J tourne mal lorsqu'un groupe de soldats alliés se bat contre des expériences horribles créées par les nazis.

title: Boulevard du Rhum
resume: In the prohibition years, the 'rumrunners' travel through the Caribbean Sea with the forbidden liquor barely escaping the ship patrols. While on the run, one of the bootleggers falls in love with an actress on a movie set.

title: America 3000
resume: In a post-apocalyptic wasteland where a tribe of women rule and all men are either ferals or slaves, one men rises up to free the men. Can they coexist in peace or will they die in war?

title: One Piece: Strong World
resume: Straw Hat Pirates must save their navigator and stop the legendary Pirate, Shiki the Golden Lion from conquering East Blue.

title: Cat City
resume: An agent delivers plans to save mice from a feline syndicate dedicated to eradicating rodents.

title: Le grand méchant renard et autres contes...
resume: Un groupe d'animaux particulièrement agités, un Renard qui se prend pour une poule, un Lapin qui se comporte comme une cigogne, et un Canard qui veut remplacer le Père Noël. Si vous voulez prendre des vacances, passez devant cet endroit.

title: One Piece: Le Baron Omatsuri et l'Île aux secrets
resume: The Straw Hat Pirates received an advertisement on a recreational island. The offers all looked promising, so they sailed to the island for an opportunity to kick back and relax from their journey across the Grand Line. The site of the resort looks like a dream come true. Only our heroes find themselves greeted by the head of the island: Baron Omatsuri. He asks all 7 of them to compete in a series of contests for their granted relaxation. Luffy accepts the challenge, and they all find this island to be not so average. There is however a mystery shrouded on the recreational paradise. Such as why are the Straw Hat Pirates the only tourists around? And why is Baron hold the only flower of the island?

title: Lady Gun Fighter
resume: The story of a woman who must find her kidnapped son, navigating a world she doesn't know, on the edge of danger with every heartbeat.

title: L'Odyssée du docteur Wassell
resume: Lorsque les forces américaines se retirent de Java, avant l'invasion japonaise, le médecin de la marine américaine Corydon M. Wassell conduit les derniers militaires blessés en sécurité vers les derniers points d'évacuation alliés.

title: À la poursuite du manuscrit sacré : La Quête de la vérité
resume: A Jewish-American doctor and a Muslim State Department employee find themselves in the center of a conspiracy that could bring about the end of days. With time ticking away, they take on a mission to unravel the mystery and save the world.

title: El arracadas
resume: A young man arrives home to an assassinated father. His mother makes him promise to take vengeance upon the murderer of his father giving him an earring of which he is nicknamed "el arracadas". Upon swearing to take revenge, he goes out in the hunt for his father's killer taking anyone down in his way.

title: Tempête sous la mer
resume: Fierce competition among sponge fishermen forces a Greek-American family to fish in the dangerous 12-mile reef area off the western coast of Florida.

title: Hamilton
resume: A nuclear armed SS20 will be smuggled from Russia via Finland to Sweden unless Swedish agent Hamilton +5 stop them with "no loose ends". What about the other stolen SS20?

title: Tarzan trouve un fils
resume: Tarzan finds a boy from a crashed plane and raises him with Jane in the jungle. A search party comes looking for the plane.

title: Gears of War
resume: On the planet Sera, a former P.O.W. is civilization's best hope in their fight against the Locust Horde, a race of creatures who emerged from underneath the planet's surface, intent on eliminating humankind.

title: Tarzana, sexe sauvage
resume: The granddaughter of Sir Donovan is believed dead in the African jungle. Fifteen years later, vague reports arrive in Europe, and he wants to believe that he has found her.

title: I Am Patrick: The Patron Saint of Ireland
resume: I AM PATRICK peels back centuries of legend and myth to tell the true story of Saint Patrick. Through historical re-enactments, expert interviews and Patrick's own writings, experience the journey from man to saint.

title: Kûkai
resume: When a demon cat appears and breaks the peace of Chang'an City, causing a series of strange events, poet Bai Letian and monk Kukai join hands to investigate the death of the emperor's concubine by following the trail left by the cat.

title: Les tribulations d'un Chinois en Chine
resume: Les aventures farfelues du malheureux milliardaire suicidaire Arthur Lempereur.

title: Fantômas contre Scotland Yard
resume: Les célèbres, mais malchanceux poursuivants français de Fantomas se rendent en Écosse pour une ultime tentative visant à traduire l'impudent criminel en justice.

title: StarCrash II - les évadés de la galaxie III
resume: The crew of a space ship confronts an evil galactic ruler out to rule the universe.

title: Lucky Luke
resume: L'intrépide pistolero Lucky Luke reçoit l'ordre du Président de ramener la paix à Daisy Town.

title: Agent Vinod
resume: A series of seemingly unconnected events across the world leads to Agent Vinod undertaking a globe-trotting mission to discover why his colleague was murdered.

title: Boo
resume: There are rumors that a long shut down and neglected hospital is haunted by the inhabitants that died there in a fire. Four college students are about to discover that the myths might just be true.

title: La princesse des glaces 3
resume: Gerda, la Princesse des Glaces, rêve de revoir ses parents, enlevés autrefois par le Vent du Nord et de vivre de nouveau en famille, accompagnée de son frère Kai. C'est ainsi que Gerda et ses amis embarquent dans un voyage exaltant, plein de rebondissements, faisant face à de nouveaux challenges qui ne vont pas lui rendre la vie facile.

title: Origine
resume: In 24th century Earth, Agito, a young boy, meets Toola, a girl from the past. Together they fight to preserve the balance between humanity and nature and to prevent the destruction of both.

title: Stryker's War
resume: Jack Stryker took two bullets in the leg in Vietnam and was carried back by one of his men. When he returns, he tries to live a quiet life in his cabin and go back out with his girlfriend, Sally.

title: Echanges
resume: An attractive but conservative mid-30's housewife stays at the house of her sexually open daughter and soon becomes involved in her daughter's swinger lifestyle.

title: Butterfly Tale
resume: A pair of rival butterflies form an unlikely friendship.

title: Sphinx
resume: Lors de son voyage au pays des pharaons, l'égyptologue Erica Baron y découvre bien plus que ce qu'elle avait prévu, à savoir le meurtre, le vol, la trahison, l'amour et la malédiction d'une momie.

title: Le big-Bang
resume: Sex farce about Fred, an inept post WWIII superhero garbageman, who must prevent WW4 by disarming the continents of Virginia, where mutated feminists live, and USSSR, where mutated buttless men live. Beautiful Liberty is his only ally.

title: L'Admirable Crichton
resume: In 1905, Lord Henry Loam and his family and servants are shipwrecked on a deserted island where the survival of the fittest renders the rigid class system irrelevant.

title: Détective Dee: la légende des rois célestes
resume: Le détective Dee est obligé de se défendre des accusations de l'Impératrice Wu alors qu'il enquête sur une vague de crimes.

title: Le sang de Fu Manchu
resume: Fu Manchu poisons and hypnotizes ten women to bring down his enemies, including Nayland Smith, with kisses of death.

title: Chosen Survivors
resume: A group of diverse individuals are suddenly taken from their homes and flown via helicopter to a futuristic bomb shelter in the desert, one-third of a mile below the surface of the Earth. There, they learn that a nuclear holocaust is taking place and that they've been "chosen" by computer to survive in the shelter in order to continue the human race. The shelter is designed to allow the people to exist underground comfortably for years, but they are faced with a threat nobody could have predicted: a colony of thousands of bloodthirsty vampire bats finds a way into the shelter and launches a series of vicious attacks where they claim the humans one by one.

title: Romulus et Remus
resume: Twin brothers revolt against tyranny in pre-Roman Italy and then come to a parting of the ways as they lead their people toward the founding of a new city.

title: Il giardino delle fate
resume: Marquess Elena Baraldi Contini hides a secret in her enchanted garden. Her Grandchildren, shocked by the death of their parents, will uncover the truth and will find a way back to life and joy thanks to Friendship and Magic.

title: Le papillon
resume: This is the story of a young girl named Elsa who was raised by a single mother (Isabelle) in the city. Isabelle and Elsa begin the film moving in next door to an elderly man who collects butterflies (Julien). Isabelle who "spends a lot of time with her friends" does not pay much attention to her daughter who walks home because her mother forgot to pick her up from school. After meeting her new neighbor, Elsa finds out about the butterflies and in short annoys Julien for a while. Julien receives a mystery package from a fellow entomologist. Julien sets out on his annual attempt to find a rare species of butterfly that he had once promised his son he would find (son dead) in the French country side, specifically a region known as Vercors. Elsa stows away in his car. After being discovered she convinces him to let her come to Vercors with him. They bond while hiking and camping until Julien, who is initially annoyed by Elsa, near the end of the film seems to have a grandfather-granddaughter relationship with her. Elsa falls in a well. The police arrest Julien. Elsa tells everyone it is cool. Isabelle starts paying attention to her child. Julien and Elsa are friends. The mystery package contained a caterpillar which turned out to become the rare species of butterfly Julien set out to find. The species is called Isabelle. So Elsa finds her mother (Isabelle) and Julien finds the butterfly (Isabelle). Surprisingly happy feel for a french film.

title: Valatty
resume: A heartwarming love story of two dogs, Tomy and Amalu, whose owners are in disapproval because of their religious differences. The dogs decide to elope, embarking on an adventurous journey replete with many challenges.

title: Primal
resume: A group of friends travel into the Australian wilds to view ancient cave paintings but soon find a horrible sickness gripping one of their own, which leaves them with nothing in their mind but a primal blood lust.

title: Men with Guns
resume: Humberto Fuentes est un riche médecin dont la femme est décédée récemment. Malgré les conseils de ses enfants, il part en voyage pour rendre visite à ses anciens élèves qui travaillent désormais dans des villages défavorisés.

title: La princesse du Nil
resume: In 1249, an Egyptian princess allies herself with the son of the Caliph of Baghdad in order to rid Egypt of its Bedouin invaders.

title: Le mur du son
resume: Fictionalized story of British aerospace engineers solving the problem of supersonic flight.

title: Feed the Gods
resume: Two brothers return to a small mountain town in search of their long lost parents only to discover that the place has a monstrous taste for tourists.

title: La Revanche de Godzilla
resume: Un enfant qui vit dans la ville industrielle de Kawasaki affronte sa solitude à travers ses rêves d'évasion sur l'île des monstres et son amitié avec Minilla.

title: Witch Hunter
resume: A medieval town plagued by demonic beasts, once innocent woodland creatures twisted by a powerful witch. A fearless hunter and his warriors must confront her dark magic to restore peace.

title: La garde noire
resume: Captain Donald King of the British Army goes to India just as World War I breaks out, convincing his comrades that he is a coward. In reality, he is on a secret mission to rescue British soldiers held prisoner there.

title: Odio el verano
resume: Comedy about three couples who unknowingly book the same house for their family vacation, turning summer into a comical exercise in tolerance.

title: Windwalker
resume: En 1797, dans l'Utah, un vieux patriarche Cheyenne aide ses proches à combattre un groupe de guerriers Crow rivaux et il raconte à ses petits-enfants l'histoire de leur famille.

title: Douma et ses amis
resume: A "born free" type story set in Kenya about an orphaned cheetah cub that is adopted and raised by an American family.

title: Eiga Doraemon: Shin Nobita no uchû kaitakushi
resume: The twist of hyperspace had been brought about by an accident when Nobita's room connected to Roppuru's spaceship door. Nobita who made friendship with Roppuru helps him to cultivate the wild planet where he is settled. On the planet that has far less gravity than the Earth, Nobita is like Superman. He confronts the company that hunts down resources of the planet with his toy guns.

title: The Mothership
resume: Un an après la disparition mystérieuse de son mari, Sara Morse découvre un étrange objet extraterrestre sous leur maison. Elle et ses enfants se lancent dans une course pour retrouver leur mari, leur père et la vérité.

title: Le hussard sur le toit
resume: Flamboyante cavalcade dans la Provence stupéfiée par le choléra, sous la Restauration. Angelo, un colonel italien de 25 ans et rebelle patriote, croise la route dune Pauline inattendue, calme et lumineuse. Épure damour nu sous l'oeil pointu dun corbeau. [255]

title: Savage Harvest
resume: A family in Africa finds itself under attack by a pride of lions.

title: Godzilla : Le Dévoreur de planètes
resume: L'humanité, ses alliés extraterrestres et Godzilla entrent tous dans leur phase ultime lorsque la puissante entité destructrice connue sous le nom de Ghidorah arrive sur Terre.

title: L'honorable Griffin
resume: Adventurous Bostonian Jack Flagg heads west to join the California gold rush with the hopes of restoring his family fortune, but his dedicated butler Bullwhip Griffin sets out to find Flagg and bring him back home.

title: Kincsem
resume: Ernõ Blaskovich a tout perdu après la révolution hongroise de 1848. Kincsem, un magnifique cheval, donne un sens à sa vie insignifiante et autodestructrice. Il a une chance de tout regagner: la vengeance, l'amour et la gloire.

title: Les Dieux du jeu
resume: A master gambler loses his memory and is befriended by a street hustler who discovers his supernatural gambling abilities.

title: La légende de l'étalon noir
resume: Lorsque Neera découvre que sa famille est sur le point de tout perdre, elle met au point un plan pour la sauver, quitte à mettre en danger ce qu'elle a de plus cher au monde : son étalon noir.

title: Gekijouban Fairy Tail: Houou no miko
resume: Follow Fairy Tail's dream team as they lend a helping hand to a girl with little memory and a grudge against wizards.

title: Deck of Cards
resume: The king of hearts has disappeared from the Kingdom of Cards, and the Joker and his friends set out on a quest to locate him, but there are other forces at play in the Kingdom, and someone might have an ace up their sleeve.

title: The Champagne Gang
resume: A group of female criminals use their smarts and their sex appeal to pull off a series of heists that help fund their lavish lifestyle.

title: La grande croisade
resume: Utilisant la machine à remonter le temps construite par sa mère, Dolf se retrouve coincé en l'an 1212. Il se retrouve dans une croisade où il confronte ses nouveaux amis aux techniques modernes.

title: Snoopy Come Home
resume: When Snoopy receives a letter from a girl named Lila, who's in a hospital, he goes on a journey with Woodstock to see her.

title: Bora Bora
resume: A Frenchman finds his runaway wife on an island in the Pacific.

title: Beneath
resume: A crew of coal miners becomes trapped 600 feet below ground after a disastrous collapse. As the air grows more toxic and time runs out, they slowly descend into madness and begin to turn on one another.

title: Camp Beaverton: Meet the Beavers
resume: At Burning Man's Beaverton Camp, queer women and trans people create a safe haven to explore boundaries and forge lasting friendships within the radical self-expression art festival.

title: Mon chat et moi, la grande aventure de Rroû
resume: Le voyage de Clémence et de son chaton, Rroû, qui quittent Paris pour passer les vacances à la campagne. Rroû profite de la vie sauvage et se lie d'amitié avec Câline, un chaton blanc qui rôde dans les bois.

title: BoBoiBoy Movie 2
resume: BoBoiBoy and his friends have been attacked by a villain named Retak'ka who is the original user of BoBoiBoy's powers. He seeks to take back his powers from him to become the most powerful person and dominate the galaxy.

title: Robin des Bois
resume: A nobleman becomes the vigilante Robin Hood who protects the oppressed English people from the tyrannical Prince John.

title: Yatterman
resume: A toy shop owner/hero and his assistant/heroine battle a leather-clad vixen and her minions to prevent them from acquiring the pieces of a mystical skull.

title: Détective Dee II : La Légende du dragon des mers
resume: Arrivant à la capitale, le détective Dee empêche la courtisane Yin de se faire enlever. Celle-ci, également pourchassée par une créature marine, est maintenant protégée par son sauveur, qui flaire un complot visant à renverser la dynastie.

title: L'esprit de la forêt
resume: A shape-shifting mountain man and a group of children team up to protect an enchanted forest from evil lumberjacks.

title: Doraemon: Nobita no shin makai daibôken 'Shichinin no mahô tsukai'
resume: When Nobita turned the world into a world with magic with the what-if-telephone-booth-gadget, He and his world needed to defeat the threat that became reality in this world.

title: Dhamaal
resume: Four lazy slacker conmen buddies learn about the secret of a hidden treasure from a dying thief and set out to find and claim it while being pursued by a determined police inspector who is hellbent to get the treasure all by himself.

title: Astérix et les Vikings
resume: While tutoring the Gallic chief Vitalstatistix's rebellious nephew Justforkix, Asterix and Obelix must rescue him from Vikings who wish to learn the meaning of fear to become invincible.

title: Shéhérazade
resume: Sheherazade is promised to a powerful Sultan as a gift in exchange for free passage to the Holy Land. When the Sultan's underling saves her from certain death, she falls madly in love with her hero.

title: Point of No Return
resume: Peter, a young aircraft engineer is deceived by his manager Jason into substituting faulty aircraft parts. When a part explodes killing a passenger, Air accident investigation find Peter responsible. Jason is found murdered.

title: Sampo
resume: The evil witch Louhi kidnaps Lemminkäinen's sister to build for her a Sampo, a device that creates salt, grain, and gold. When Lemminkäinen fails to recover the Sampo, Louhi steals the sun, plunging the world into frozen darkness.

title: Femmes gangsters
resume: An undercover policewoman helps three female convicts escape from prison so that they can lead her to a stash of stolen diamonds hidden in a swamp.

title: The Visual Bible: Matthew
resume: The plot follows the birth, preaching, teaching and miracles of Jesus. He preached and lived a radical message of God's Love and was able to heal people of lifelong disabilities and illnesses and was able to command natural phenomena.

title: Benji la malice
resume: Après avoir survécu à un accident en mer, Benji se retrouve confronté à la nature sauvage et doit faire face à de nombreux dangers.

title: Our Drawings
resume: Paige Foster, discovers a mysterious intruder inside her artwork where she travels. Her beatboxing puppy sidekick helps search within her imaginative realms drawings that enable Foster to become anything desired.

title: Bang Bang
resume: A young bank receptionist gets mixed up with Rajveer Nanda, a man who has a mysterious background.

title: Appel inconnu
resume: Petit déjeuner, embrasser sa femme avant de partir, emmener les enfants à l'école, une bombe sous la voiture, une journée sans fin se profile.

title: Salaami
resume: An honest army cadet discovers evidence of police corruption, leading to a dangerous confrontation between military and law enforcement when he attempts to expose a corrupt superintendent.

title: Blue Exorcist: le film
resume: Rin and his friends, along with the rest of True Cross Academy Town, are in the midst of preparing for a festival that is celebrated only once every 11 years. While the barriers protecting the city from demon intrusions are being repaired, Rin and his twin brother Yukio are sent to the scene of an exorcism as reinforcements. Things take a turn for the worse and as they attempt to salvage their mission, they meet a mysterious young boy that may threaten everything that they know. Meanwhile, Cheng-Long Liu, a First Class Senior Exorcist from the Taiwan Branch, joins the 'simple' repair operation that forces his fate to cross with 'Satan's spawn', Rin.

title: Zanna: Whisper of Volcano Isle
resume: Zanna, a girl separated from her family suddenly enters a world full of wonders that she never imagined.

title: Le Sang des Templiers 2
resume: A survivor of the Great Siege of Rochester Castle fights to save his clan from Celtic raiders. A sequel to the 2011 film, "Ironclad."

title: Dans les griffes du loup garou
resume: Daninsky joins a Yeti expedition in the Himalayas but gets captured by cannibalistic nymphs guarding a Buddhist temple. They turn him into a werewolf where he encounters a sadistic bandit while roaming the mountains.

title: King Rising 3
resume: Un assassin est embauché pour un dernier travail: kidnapper les enfants d'un homme d'affaires. Les choses se compliquent quand il s'avère qu'il a choisi de retourner au Moyen Âge et de ramener l'ordre dans un royaume en proie au chaos.

title: Daku Ramkali
resume: A tale of twin brothers divided by fate - one joins law enforcement while the other turns to crime. Their daughters' lives intertwine through love and vengeance.

title: Dead Sea
resume: A Marine Biologist is assigned to investigate the mysterious deaths of marine life in an inland salt water lake that have been attributed to a creature thought to have been the stuff of legend.

title: Memes & Nightmares
resume: NBA Twitter king's quest unravels the fleeting nature of online content and human bonds in the digital era, shaping our ephemeral connections.

title: Au coeur de l'apocalypse
resume: Tandis que des tempêtes solaires provoquent des tsunamis, des éruptions volcaniques et des inondations, une famille tente de fuir vers des grottes situées à quelques kilomètres.

title: Les Monstres de l'île en feu
resume: After undersea explosions near a Caribbean island, prehistoric creatures are unleashed on the population. A boy teams up with a Neanderthal and an irritated dinosaur try to stop the dinosaurs.

title: Ek Chalis Ki Last Local
resume: A comic thriller about two people who miss the last local train at 1:40 am and how missing of their train changes their course of life forever.

title: Smelliville
resume: À la recherche d'une nouvelle maison, les Ogglies se retrouvent dans le beau et paisible village de Smelliville. Malheureusement, Smelliville a un problème d'odeur nauséabonde : le dépôt d'ordures est en train d'abîmer l'endroit.

title: Voyage au centre de la terre
resume: Young people exploring a cave in Hawaii fall into a hole, and wind up in the lost city of Atlantis.

title: The Aristocats
resume: Based on the 1970 animated film, follows a family of Parisian felines who must team up with a smooth-talking tomcat to try to make it back home after their owner's jealous butler kidnaps them and leaves them in the country.

title: Tobot Movie: Attack of Robot Force
resume: Doctor Franklin and his 2 sons, Ryan, and Kory go over to Jeju Island on their holidays. When a robot army comes to Jeju Island and starts to attack humans, it's up to the Tobots to stop them.

title: Fly Me to the Moon
resume: En 1969, la Nasa s'apprête à envoyer trois astronautes sur la Lune. Résidant tout à côté du centre, trois mouches, Nat et ses copains Scooter et I.Q., décident d'embarquer clandestinement dans la navette.

title: Azumi
resume: Raised to deal in cold blooded death, the teenage assassin girl Azumi must defeat three evil warlords while also battling her own heart.

title: Ozzy, la grande évasion
resume: When his family goes on vacation, a young dog finds himself at a dog prison where he must escape with the help of his new friends.

title: Angélique
resume: En France, avant que Louis XIV ne monte sur le trône, une jeune baronne est forcée de se marier contre sa volonté et doit lutter contre la trahison et le meurtre qui la menacent ainsi que son mari, qu'elle a appris à aimer profondément.

title: Big Fish & Begonia
resume: Une jeune fille de 16 ans voyage dans le monde humain sous la forme d'un dauphin et établit un lien avec un garçon humain.

title: Vildheks
resume: "Wild Witch" is a fantasy film for the whole family based on the popular book series by Lene Kaaberbøl.

title: Barney
resume: A twelve year old boy and a common criminal are being transported in the same ship from England to Australia in the last century. When the ship wrecked they happen to be the only survivors of the catastrophe. Now they have to get along with each other and finally become friends.

title: Air Force the Movie: Selagi Bernyawa
resume: Zafran, a grounded SUKHOI pilot, fights for the opportunity to save them. Nine of the passengers managed to make their jump before the plane crashes. Back in Malaysia, upon discovery of the news, the air force makes preparation for rescue.

title: Le chaînon manquant
resume: C'est l'histoire d'Oh, un homme préhistorique pas comme les autres et, par conséquent, rejeté par ses congénères, même sa mère. Dans ces circonstances, ce seront finalement un brontosaure et un ptérodactyle qui prendront soin de lui.

title: War-Gods of the Deep
resume: En 1903, en Cornouailles, un groupe d'habitants découvre une cité sous-marine datant de 1803, qui cache une société de contrebandiers et de créatures aquatiques.

title: Hirokin
resume: Hirokin, un héros réticent marqué par un sombre passé, doit accomplir son destin lorsqu'il est contraint de choisir entre venger le meurtre de sa famille ou lutter pour la liberté d'un peuple longtemps maltraité.

title: Tom Sawyer
resume: A la mort de ses parents, le jeune Tom Sawyer part vivre chez sa tante Polly, dans le Mississippi. Avec son meilleur ami Huckleberry Finn, il fait les quatre cents coups, jusqu'au jour où les deux garnements sont les témoins d'un violent règlement de comptes.

title: Blood: The Last Vampire
resume: Une vampire nommée Saya qui chasse et détruit les démons dans un Japon d'après-guerre, est insérée dans une école militaire pour découvrir lequel de ses camarades de classe est un démon déguisé.

title: Solo
resume: Après être tombé près d'une falaise sur une plage déserte, un surfeur grièvement blessé entame une lutte solitaire pour survivre contre la nature sans merci.

title: Montevideo, vidimo se!
resume: A football team from Belgrade, in the former Yugoslavia, gets a chance to go to the First World Football Championship, but things get complicated along the way.

title: Le Château des Carpathes
resume: In 1897, in a castle near the town of Werewolfville in the Carpathians, a slightly deranged Professor Orfanik experiments with his new inventions which include, even at this early date, television and a film camera.

title: Le Maître du monde
resume: Un savant fou prénommé Robur entreprend un terrifiant plan: détruire les armées du monde entier afin de régner sur la planète. L'un de ses quatre otages, membre du gouvernement, parviendra à empêcher ce funeste objectif.

title: Doraemon: Nobita to Ryû no kishi
resume: Origin of species that have evolved differently from human beings.

title: Kureyon Shin-chan ankoku tamatama daitsuiseki
resume: The Nohara family gets involved in a dispute between two clans who are fighting to possess a sphere claimed to be able to bring back to life a powerful evil spirit.

title: Kidnapped
resume: In eighteenth century Scotland, during the Jacobite Rebellion, David Balfour claims his inheritance from his uncle who has him shanghaied on a ship where David meets fugitive Jacobite rebel Alan Breck.

title: L'expédition du fort King
resume: Lorsqu'il apprend le projet d'extermination d'une tribu amérindienne en Floride, le lieutenant Caldwell tente de convaincre son supérieur de la cruauté de cet acte.

title: A Few Less Men
resume: Travel plans for three men in ill-fitting wedding tuxedos goes horribly wrong. A follow-up to the 2011 comedy 'A Few Best Men'.

title: William
resume: Julian Reed et Barbara Sullivan créent un bébé en utilisant l'ancien ADN d'un corps de Néandertal. William doit apprendre à exister dans un monde où il est le seul homme de Néandertal de la planète.

title: Dead Water
resume: A relaxing getaway turns deadly for a former marine, who must risk his life to save his wife and best friend from a modern day pirate.

title: Sou jiu
resume: A man loses his son while travelling in the snowy mountains.

title: A Mermaid's Tale
resume: A twelve-year-old girl befriends a quirky teenage mermaid who's anything but mythical, and their friendship could heal an age-old feud.

title: Le Cheik
resume: Un charmant cheik arabe s'entiche d'une anglaise aventureuse et moderne et l'enlève pour l'emmener chez lui, dans le désert saharien.

title: Rock Dog 3: Battle the Beat
resume: When the young performers on a music contest show admit they have never heard of Angus Scattergood, Bodi is compelled to join the show to restore the Rock Legend's good name.

title: Robby
resume: Shipwrecked on a tropical island, a young boy befriends an abandoned native youth, forcing him to reevaluate societal prejudice about race, religion and nudity.

title: Docteur Cyclope
resume: Un savant fou travaillant dans la jungle sud-américaine fait des miniatures de ses collègues quand il ressent que sa mégalomanie est en danger.

title: Qayamat: City Under Threat
resume: CBI officer Akram seeks to nab three terrorists, Ali, Abbas and Laila, who have held 213 tourists as hostage in Elphinstone Jail. For this, he seeks help from Rachit, a former associate of the trio.

title: Mr Zoo Keeper
resume: A zookeeper and his relationship with the animals and birds that remain in the zoo.

title: The Proposition
resume: In Wales, around 1800, Catherine Morgan is widowed young, her husband a war casualty whose unpaid gambling debts threaten both the loss of home and farm and destitution for her and her daughters Elen and Emily. Catherine hopes to save them by selling their cattle at a distant market. She must overcome the hardships of the cattle drive across the craggy Welsh countryside as an obsessively infatuated sheriff, whom she does not love, attempts to thwart the drive; and she must work out her insecurities in her relationship to his half-brother, an experienced drover, who helps her on the drive.

title: Were the World Mine
resume: A bullied and demoralized gay student at an all-boys school uses a magical flower derived from Shakespeare's "A Midsummer Night's Dream' to turn many in his community gay, including a comely rugby player for himself.

title: Racing Extinction
resume: A documentary that follows undercover activists trying to stave off a man-made mass extinction.

title: The Stormriders
resume: An evil warlord takes in 2 students (Wind & Cloud) in an effort to become invincible so he can take over the world.

title: Black Butler: Book of Murder
resume: Ciel Phantomhive hosts a banquet attended by several nonpareil upper-crusters of polite society, as well as one struggling writer, Arthur Conan Doyle. All is merry until the guest of honor, Georg von Siemens, is found murdered.

title: Adam Green's Aladdin
resume: Adam Green's "Aladdin" is a hyper-sensory, poetic, and humorously modern take on the Arabian Nights classic tale. Revolving around Aladdin's dysfunctional family, who live in an "average" American city ruled by a corrupt Sultan with a decadent socialite daughter, the film explores themes of technology, government repression, greed, and true love.

title: Wolf Warrior 2
resume: L'agent le plus redoutable des forces spéciales chinoises s'installe paisiblement au bord de la mer. Lorsque des mercenaires sadiques se mettent à viser les civils alentour, il doit laisser derrière lui sa tranquillité retrouvée et reprendre du service comme soldat et protecteur.

title: Mobile Suit Gundam SEED Freedom
resume: Lacus Clyne becomes president of a peace monitoring organization, but things are not quite what they seem.

title: The Phantom Warrior
resume: L'histoire du justicier masqué et de l'âme immortelle, Nemesis Knight.

title: Teddy
resume: Un jeune atteint de TOC entreprend de sauver une fille des griffes d'un groupe criminel médical international à l'aide d'un ours en peluche qui se comporte comme un humain.

title: 7 Days to Vegas
resume: Inspired by a true story about Hollywood big shots who will bet on anything.

title: Sparkle: A Unicorn Tale
resume: Annabelle runs away from an orphanage with two other kids to rescue the animals on her family's farm. The orphans discover a magical unicorn has taken up residence, and they try to determine the mythical beast's purpose.

title: Le port des passions
resume: Shrimpers and oilmen clash after an ambitious wildcatter begins constructing an off-shore oil rig.

title: Patagonia
resume: A young Welsh couple travel to Argentina to work on their relationship.

title: Shrek 5: The Contract - A Fan Made Film
resume: In this film, when all 4 of Shrek's old nemesis come back from the dead and kill Fiona, he must find a way to bring Fiona back from the dead via magical contract, all with the help of Donkey, Puss, and some new faces.

title: La ronde de l'aube
resume: Pendant la Dépression, en plein carnaval de la Nouvelle-Orléans, un journaliste s'immisce dans la vie d'un couple d'aviateurs acrobates.

title: Le Dernier Voyage
resume: Une lune rouge menace l'intégrité de la Terre. Le seul espoir de l'humanité est l'énigmatique Paul W.R, l'astronaute le plus talentueux de sa génération. Mais quelques heures avant le début de la mission, Paul disparait.

title: Le trésor de Tarzan
resume: Tarzan's jungle home, and his family, Jane and Boy, are threatened by men greedy for gold.

title: The Thirsty Dead
resume: De belles jeunes filles sont enlevées dans les rues de Manille par un culte de la mort qui a besoin de leur sang pour rester immortelles

title: Tigresse
resume: Alors qu'elle traverse une crise émotionnelle, Vera, vétérinaire du zoo d'une petite ville, provoque l'évasion d'un tigre.

title: The Upper World
resume: Esso est pris dans une querelle mortelle et sur le point d'être expulsé lorsqu'il se rend compte qu'il a un don inattendu : l'accès à un monde où il peut voir des aperçus du passé et de l'avenir.

title: Make Me Feel
resume: An adventurous Love Story about a young mother who travels into the coma dreams of her ex-husband in order to become a family again.

title: Sword Art Online: Ordinal Scale
resume: Kirito uncovers a conspiracy within Ordinal Scale, a popular AR game developed for a new system called The Augma.

title: Zombies of the Stratosphere
resume: The invaders come to Earth to create an H-bomb to blast Earth out of orbit so that Mars can take its place.

title: Journey to the West
resume: Tang Zhijun, an editor of a science fiction magazine, tries to find signs of alien civilization.

title: La totale !
resume: François, simple fonctionnaire aux yeux de tous, travaille en réalité depuis 20 ans comme agent secret. Il découvre alors que son fils sèche les cours et que sa femme le trompe. Il va tout tenter pour remettre les choses en ordre.

title: It Came from the Desert
resume: Hommage aux films de créatures des années 1950, le film met en scène des héros de motocross rivaux, des soirées dans le désert, des bases militaires souterraines secrètes, des incertitudes romantiques et bien sûr des fourmis géantes.
Intense tale of the young gunsmith named Isaiah who's in a race to save the lives of the endangered youth.

title: Les Trois Jeunes Détectives : Le Secret de l'île aux fantômes
resume: Three kid detectives go on an epic journey to eerie Skeleton Island. Once home to pirates, it's now plagued by a mysterious beast.

title: Python Island
resume: A group of people searching for a magical tree in a mysterious jungle, find they are not alone. Something is watching them, waiting for the perfect moment to strike.

title: Bright: Samurai Soul
resume: Izo le rōnin et Raiden l'orque s'allient pour escorter une jeune elfe et sa baguette magique jusqu'au territoire des elfes dans le nord…

title: Dancing in the Rain
resume: An autism spectrum boy starts a beautiful friendship with each other. When they all grew up, a tragic event occurs, putting their friendship on the edge of destruction.

title: Condorito: La película
resume: Condorito embarks in a hilarious adventure to save the planet and his loved ones from an evil alien.

title: La planète des tempêtes
resume: Cosmonauts land on the planet Venus. However, they find themselves in danger from the voracious monsters they find on it.

title: RDX: Robert Dony Xavier
resume: Trois jeunes hommes voient leur vie bouleversée lorsqu'ils se heurtent à un gang impitoyable.

title: L'homme qui rétrécit
resume: Shipbuilder inexplicably shrinks, gets trapped in basement, few inches tall. Must fight for survival in now-hostile ordinary household environment. Sci-fi premise, no explanation given for shrinking phenomenon.

title: Du sable et des diamants
resume: A former British Naval Officer now makes his living by smuggling goods around the Mediterranean. After being forced to dump his cargo after nearly being caught by the authorities in Malta, he is eager to recoup his losses. When a former colleague appears and tells a wild story about smuggling diamonds out of South West Africa, he sees his chance to make a lot of money. Accompanied by the wife of a diamond prospector and a few shady characters he embarks on a quest to retrieve the diamonds. The only problem is that nobody trusts anybody else and the only way to retrieve the diamonds is to navigate the dangerous waters of the skeleton coast, a place where few ships have ever survived. To complicate things further, he has some very good reasons for not going there related to a mission he undertook there during the war.

title: Rodeo Princess
resume: A group of rodeo trick-riders recruits a young girl to join them.

title: La bataille de San Sebastian
resume: En 1743, le hors-la-loi Leon Alastray est traqué par l'armée espagnole, mais un prêtre lui donne asile dans un village terrorisé par les Indiens Yaqui en maraude.

title: Conan, le fils du futur
resume: In the aftermath of a war fought by magnetic weapons which caused massive earthquakes, a young and spunky boy named Conan gets involved in a grand adventure. A condensed version of the TV series.

title: Insiders
resume: À la suite d'une crise bancaire, quatre amis de la classe moyenne organisent un hold-up "en gants blancs", mais découvrent que leur banque a déjà fait faillite.

title: Seven Swords
resume: Malgré son passé de bourreau, deux villageois décident d'écouter les dires d'un homme, les mettant en garde de la venue de mercenaires. Ensemble, ils vont obtenir des sabres légendaires et l'aide de quatre guerriers pour sauver le village.

title: Bekas
resume: The story is about two brothers want to travel to america and the adventures that they face in the journey.

title: My Side of the Mountain
resume: As young Sam Gribley runs away he learns about nature.

title: L'infernale poursuite
resume: During the Civil War Union spy Andrews and his men volunteer to steal a Confederate train and drive it to Union territory while destroying the Confederate railway system along the way.

title: Latitude zéro
resume: A journalist is saved by a giant submarine captained by a 200-year-old man who takes him to an underwater paradise city where no one ages. That's when monsters and mutants sent by the captain's rival, a 200-year-old scientist, attack.

title: Legacy Peak
resume: De son côté, Jason se lance dans une quête pour gagner le cœur des enfants de Noëlle avant qu'ils ne se marient.

title: Dragon Age: Dawn of the Seeker
resume: In the land of Orlais, where battles are fought with swords and magic, a young heroine rises as templars, mages, and dragons clash. Cassandra, a brash and beautiful Seeker, must stop a conspiracy that threatens the realm's most powerful religious order, the Chantry of Andraste. Accused of treasonous crimes and hunted by friend and foe, Cassandra must clear her name and overcome her raging emotions in order to save the day and take her place in legend.

title: Jauja
resume: Un père et sa fille voyagent du Danemark vers un désert inconnu qui existe dans un royaume au-delà des limites de la civilisation.

title: Guardians of Time
resume: Quatre cousins découvrent un passage menant à un monde mystérieux. Pris au piège dans ce pays, le Royaume de Keoherus, ils doivent affronter le Gardien du temps, affronter des forces et des bêtes sombres pour espérer rentrer chez eux.

title: Le Secret des 7 volcans
resume: Teenage twins Rachel and Theo travel to Auckland to stay with relatives after their mother suddenly dies. They find an alien environment and overhear Mr. Wilberforce talking about something stirring beneath the ground - the fire-raiser.

title: Ali Baba et les 40 Voleurs
resume: A boy prince, raised by forty thieves, takes revenge on the Mongol invaders who murdered his father and stole his kingdom.

title: Traffic
resume: Plusieurs histoires s'entrecroisent lorsqu'une jeune femme a un besoin urgent de transplantation cardiaque, l'unique donneur résidant à des kilomètres.

title: Mega Time Squad
resume: John steals money and a bracelet/temporal dislocator from a Chinese antiques shop. Fleeing, he triggers the device and goes minutes back in time. The time travels result in new Johns and they form the Mega Time Squad.

title: Chasseurs de dragons
resume: A fantastic tale telling the adventures of two dragon hunters!

title: El Niño
resume: Le trafic de drogue à travers le détroit de Gibraltar est tenu par des caïds que deux jeunes d'une vingtaine d'années, El Niño et El Compi, décident de défier pour y prendre leur part.

title: Super Flics en jupons
resume: Squad of beautiful government agents tries to catch saboteurs.

title: The Gamers: Dorkness Rising
resume: Lodge, a gaming geek, takes his playing very seriously, unlike his babyish friends who'd rather be immature. He decides to shake things up by introducing two unconventional people to their group.

title: Les Grandes Vacances
resume: Un directeur français strict envoie son fils frivole en Angleterre pour apprendre l'anglais. Mais l'étudiant a une meilleure idée de comment passer ses vacances d'été.

title: Saucisses à tout prix
resume: A road trip comedy about three friends who travel across the country in a Wiener Wagon to beat up a popular daytime talk show therapist.

title: Delhi Safari
resume: A group of animals plan a trip to Delhi in order to ask the parliament why the forest they live in is on the verge of destruction.

title: Biru Unjárga
resume: Set in Norway's northern reaches, the story centers on Elvira, a Sami teen. Convinced her mother conceived at a Danish clinic, her life shifts when her true father emerges, forever altering her world.

title: Signé Zorro
resume: A masked vigilante battles a corrupt commandant by night while masquerading as an aristocrat by day.

title: Bilal: La naissance d'une légende
resume: Il y a mille ans, un garçon rêvant de devenir grand guerrier est kidnappé avec sa soeur et emmené dans un pays loin de sa famille. Jeté dans un monde où gourmandise et injustice sont les maîtres mots, Bilal trouve le courage d'élever la voix et de faire avancer les choses. Inspiré par des événements réels, c'est l'histoire d'un véritable héros qui a mérité son souvenir dans le temps et l'histoire.

title: Le trésor de Matacumba
resume: En 1869, dans le Kentucky, un jeune garçon et ses amis partent à la recherche d'un coffre au trésor caché par son défunt père dans les Everglades de Floride pendant la guerre de Sécession.

title: Les combattants
resume: Entre ses amis et l'entreprise familiale, l'été d'Arnaud s'annonce paisible. Tranquille jusqu'à sa rencontre avec Madeleine, aussi belle que cassante, bloc de muscles tendus et de prophéties catastrophiques.

title: Quand la jungle s'éveille
resume: A doctor and an adventurer journey to the Amazon, where they encounter a man in a bizarre bird costume terrorizing the local indigenous population.

title: Love on the Rock
resume: Colton Riggs, a burned-out former tough cop from the Midwest, has his boring new Maltese charter-boating lifestyle turned upside-down when he suddenly finds himself catapulted into a web of high-stakes international espionage.

title: Alpha and Omega: Family Vacation
resume: Pack up for a howling fun movie adventure filled with action, laughs, and tender moments as Kate and Humphrey take their pups on their first family vacation!

title: Draug
resume: A missionary disappears with soldiers in Sweden's northern forest during the late Viking age. A search party enters the woods, where an ancient darkness lurks.

title: Wolf Hound
resume: Inspiré de l'unité d'opérations spéciales allemande KG 200 qui a abattu, réparé et piloté des avions alliés en tant que chevaux de Troie, "Wolf Hound" se déroule en 1944 en France occupée et suit les exploits du Capitaine David Holden.

title: 25 km/h
resume: Deux frères très différents se réunissent et partent pour un voyage très spécial, une virée en moto qu'ils avaient imaginée dans leur enfance.

title: Deathstroke Knights & Dragons: The Movie
resume: Slade Wilson, maître assassin, mène une double vie : père de famille, et tueur impitoyable connu sous le nom de Deathstroke. Saura-t-il expier ses péchés pour sauver ses proches ?

title: Tomb Raider Ascension
resume: Lara Croft explores an English mine seeking clues about a Mayan artifact, the Ascension Stone. She discovers her uncle's involvement and her father's secrets, leading her on a quest to become the famed Tomb Raider.

title: Gus, petit oiseau, grand voyage
resume: Un voyage de héros avec un héros des plus improbables. Yellowbird est un minuscule oiseau orphelin qui n'a jamais quitté le nid, n'a pas de famille, mais en cherche désespérément une - jusqu'à ce qu'il se retrouve à mener une volée d'oiseaux migrateurs vers l'Afrique.

title: Griffes jaunes
resume: En décembre 1941, l'ancien capitaine Rick Leland monte à bord d'un navire japonais qui se dirige vers l'Asie via le canal de Panama. Ses hôtes japonais se montrent intéressés par les plans de défense américains pour la zone du canal.

title: Deathstalker
resume: A reboot of the cult classic 1983 sword and sorcery film.

title: Ghost Book Obakezukan
resume: The forbidden book "The Haunted Book" can make any wish come true, but in order to make your wish come true, you have to go through a life-threatening ordeal. What is the ordeal...!?

title: Finnik 2
resume: Careless Finnick loses his invisibility after awakening an ancient staff's magic. Now, all finns are in danger. He and Christine must embark on an adventure to restore his invisibility and save the finns.

title: Le magicien d'Oz
resume: Animated version of the classic story of a young farmgirl who is transported to the magic land of Oz.

title: All the Little Animals
resume: Bobby Platt is a mentally slow young man who escapes an abusive, hateful stepfather who has killed his pets one by one. To save himself, Bobby runs away and meets a strange old man who wanders the highways to bury roadkill animals. Bobby becomes the old man's apprentice and learns to see the world of nature in a strange idyllic way. But soon the shadow of his stepfather catches up to him and Bobby's world explodes into a grotesque nightmare.

title: Maugli
resume: A boy raised by animals learns to live by the laws of the jungle. Full-length version of the Soviet animated series.

title: Heroes of the Golden Mask
resume: Charlie, a wise-cracking, homeless, American orphan is magically transported to the ancient Chinese kingdom of Sanxingdui, where a colorful team of superheroes need his help to defend the city from a brutal conqueror.

title: Dieu pardonne, elles jamais!
resume: A series of inexplicable accidents befall the people and companies responsible for developing the world's first supersonic airliner (SST1). A British agent is sent to investigate and with the help of another agent uncovers a plot masterminded by Carl Petersen who stands to gain eight million pounds if the aircraft is not ready by a certain date. The evil Petersen has developed a number of "robots" (actually rather beautiful girls with "electronic brains") to help him sabotage the SST1 project by means of "infrasound" (extreme low frequency sound waves) which can be directed at people or objects with devastating results.

title: Les cinglés partent en safari
resume: Lady Evelyn Bagley mounts an expedition to find her long-lost baby. Bill Boosey is the fearless hunter and guide. Prof. Tinkle is searching for the rare Oozalum bird. Everything is going swimmingly until a gorilla enters the camp.

title: Avis de tempête
resume: L'Amérique du Nord se voit frapper par d'innombrables ouragans suite à une expérience scientifique ayant échouée. Un chercheur tente alors de mettre sa famille en sécurité avant que la situation n'empire.

title: Georges le petit curieux 3: Retour dans la jungle
resume: Curious George goes on an epic adventure to space that crash lands in the jungles of Africa leading to an unforgettable journey with some new animal friends.

title: Vercingétorix, la légende du druide roi
resume: Le destin de toute une nation est entre les mains d'un seul homme.

title: L'Ile de Nim 2
resume: Avec l'aide d'un jeune fugueur, une courageuse adolescente de 14 ans se bat pour préserver sa maison sur une île idyllique des griffes des promoteurs immobiliers.

title: Lost Continent
resume: Major Joe Nolan heads a rescue mission in the South Pacific to recover a downed atomic rocket. The crew crash lands on a mysterious island, and spends much time rock-climbing.

title: Santa Jaws
resume: Trying to survive his family Christmas, Cody makes a wish to be alone, which ends up backfiring when a shark manifests and kills his entire family.

title: Le survivant des monts lointains
resume: A fired railroad man is re-hired and entrusted to carry a ten thousand dollar payroll in secret, even though he is suspected of being connected to outlaws.

title: Naruto, le film : La Légende de la pierre de Guelel
resume: Naruto, Shikamaru and Sakura are on a mission to deliver a lost pet to a village when a mysterious knight appear to confront them.

title: Laskar Pelangi
resume: In the 1970s, a group of 10 students struggles with poverty and develop hopes for the future in Gantong Village on the farming and tin mining island of Belitung off the east coast of Sumatra.

title: The Sin of Nora Moran
resume: A young woman with a difficult past is sentenced for a murder she didn't commit, but revealing the truth could hurt people she loves.

title: Pokémon : Zoroark, le maître des illusions
resume: A greedy, manipulative media mogul seeks to capture Celebi for nefarious purposes, using the shape-shifting Pokémon Zoroark to hunt it down.

title: Refroidi à 99%
resume: Uncle Frank Kelly calls on Harry Crown to help him in a gang war. The war becomes personal when Harry's new girlfriend is kidnapped by Uncle Frank's enemy, Big Eddie.

title: Dagmar: L'âme des vikings
resume: Signe, spared from death to produce a child, befriends a little girl, Frigg, and escapes from the camp.

title: Qu'il était bon, mon petit Français!
resume: In 1594 in Brazil, the Tupinambás Indians are friends of the French and their enemies are the Tupiniquins, friends of the Portuguese. A Frenchman (Arduíno Colassanti) is captured by the Tupinambás and, in spite of his trial to convince them that he is French, they believe he is Portuguese. The Frenchman becomes their slave, and maritally lives with Seboipepe (Ana Maria Magalhães). *Contains Spoilers* Later, he uses powder in the cannons that the Portuguese left behind to defeat the Tupiniquins in a battle. In order to celebrate the victory, the Indians decide to eat him.

title: Savana - Sesso e diamanti
resume: The film about diamonds contraband in one South American country.

title: Time Pirates
resume: Le groupe SM6 est en tête d'affiche de son premier concert, lorsque la découverte d'une demi-carte au trésor les renvoie dans le passé. Pour rentrer chez eux, ils devront trouver la moitié manquante de la carte et le trésor caché.

title: Lissi und der wilde Kaiser
resume: A send-up of the Sissi trilogy.

title: Kureyon Shinchan: Buriburi Ôkoku no hihô
resume: Shinchan and his lookalike embarks on a journey to defeat forces of a ruthless leader Mr. Anaconda and his forces.

title: King Kong revient
resume: A newly discovered 36-foot gorilla escapes from a freighter off the coast of Korea. At the same time an American actress is filming a movie in the country. Chaos ensues as the ape kidnaps her and rampages through Seoul.

title: Les enfants de l'eau
resume: This children's fantasy tells the story of a 12-year-old boy who discovers a complex underwater world where young children are held prisoner by an evil shark and an eel.

title: Raavanan
resume: A bandit leader kidnaps the wife of the policeman who killed his sister, but later falls in love with her.

title: Bouboulina
resume: Captain Lascarina decides to organize the revolution in Spetses despite her double widowhood. In the struggle for the liberation of Greece, she gives all her property, fighting along with her lads.

title: Empire Queen: The Golden Age of Magic
resume: Dans un royaume où la magie est interdite, un charmant trio d'aventuriers se lance dans une quête dangereuse à la recherche de la légendaire baguette souveraine, nécessaire pour renverser une reine maléfique et restaurer la magie pour tous

title: Due gocce d'acqua salata
resume: After an airplane crash, two young passengers, a male and a female are left stranded on a tropical desert island.

title: La communale
resume: Année 1945. Un groupe d'écoliers fréquente une école de la banlieue de Prague. Le mauvais comportement des enfants oblige un enseignant ayant une expérience militaire, un héros de la résistance pendant la guerre, à incorporer l'école.

title: Orage au paradis
resume: On a small Mediterranean island live Costanza, her father Urbano, and beachcomber Moore, whom she plans to marry. Into this Eden come two plane crash survivors, supermodel Laura and her playboy friend Wally. The shapely, worldly Laura becomes a bad influence, especially when triangles start to develop. But beyond this, little mysteries lead Laura and Wally to wonder what's going on and who Moore really is.

title: Loophole
resume: When architect Stephen Booker loses his partnership, he finds jobs hard to come by, and with money in short supply, he unwittingly becomes involved in a daring scheme to rob one of London's biggest bank vaults.

title: Atoman
resume: A mystical Astrolabe with the power to destroy the world is stolen from the lost city of Atlantis in the Atlas Mountains. One man discovers he is one of the last descendants of the Atlanteans and must prevent the impending cataclysm.

title: Delta Force 3: L'enjeu mortel
resume: A terrorist places an atomic bomb somewhere in an American metropolis. The U.S. president has no choice but to call in the Delta Force.

title: Attack on Titan: The Weight of Pain
resume: It is the fourth film in the compilation saga. That collects from chapters 38 to 42 of the third season, and includes the óvulos of Levi ackerman

title: Le tableau
resume: Trois personnages de différentes classes sociales échappent à leur tableau inachevé à la recherche du peintre, dans l'espoir de le compléter.

title: Arthur & Merlin: Knights of Camelot
resume: Le roi Arthur rentre chez lui après avoir combattu l'empire romain. Son fils illégitime a corrompu le trône de Camelot. Arthur doit maintenant retrouver Merlin et les chevaliers de la table ronde et se battre pour récupérer sa couronne.

title: Gorilas a todo ritmo
resume: An enterprising woman reporter enlists the help of a hardened African explorer to try to locate a missing showbiz man who disappeared some time ago.

title: Between Two Worlds
resume: Passengers on an ocean liner can't recall how they got on board or where they are going yet, oddly enough, it soon becomes apparent that they all have something in common.

title: Maara
resume: Quand Paaru voit un conte de fées qu'elle a entendu d'un inconnu alors qu'elle était enfant peint sur les murs d'une ville côtière, elle part à la recherche de l'homme qui l'a peint: Maara.

title: La Voie de la lumière
resume: Kojiro Sasaki, un talentueux samouraï, lance un duel à Musashi. Ce dernier se retire alors un an à la campagne en attendant le moment de la confrontation. Là, il est rejoint par Otsu et Akemi qui se disputent la place auprès de leur aimé.

title: Rachel et l'étranger
resume: A widowed farmer takes an indentured servant as his new wife, but the arrival of his old friend threatens their burgeoning relationship.

title: Rakuen Tsuiho: Expelled from Paradise
resume: With Earth in ruins, humanity no longer takes corporeal form and exists in a virtual society known as 'DEVA'. When a hacker infiltrates the cyber universe, Officer Angela Balzac is dispatched to the surface to track him down.

title: Le Roi des ronces
resume: A virus begins to grip the Earth's population and a group of hopeful survivors are cryogenically frozen in attempt to find a cure. But when the group awakens they are flung into a horrifying situation.

title: Les magiciens du royaume perdu II
resume: Three kingdoms have been overtaken by three evil lords and only a teenage boy with magical powers can restore peace to the land.

title: Le Mystère de l'île des monstres
resume: A young man and his traveling buddy embark on a global journey onboard their ship, only to be shipwrecked on a desolate island teeming with prehistoric creatures and gold-hunting bandits.

title: La nouvelle guerre des boutons
resume: Dans la France occupée, la bande d'enfants que dirige Lebrac joue à la guerre contre un clan rival, mais la fille qu'il aime, une juive, est sur le point d'être démasquée par les collabos du coin. Lebrac et le village doivent maintenant faire face à la réalité des choses.

title: Winx Club: le secret du royaume perdu
resume: At Alfea College, Stella, Aisha, Flora, Musa, and Tecna all graduate and become fairy guardians of their home planets. But, Bloom must watch graduation from the sidelines. The Winx try to save Bloom's parents and the planet.

title: Le club des ravisseurs
resume: A group of Irish noblemen kidnap girls in order to marry into their fortune and avoid becoming priests or soldiers.

title: L'envol de Ploé
resume: Un jeune pluvier n'a pas appris à voler lorsque sa famille migre à l'automne. Il doit surmonter l'hiver arctique, ses adversaires vicieux et lui-même afin d'être réuni avec son bien-aimé au printemps prochain.

title: Tonde Saitama
resume: In a world where people are discriminated based on their birthplace, a resident of the much-reviled Saitama Prefecture embarks on a revolutionary campaign to improve things for his home.

title: Tant que soufflera la tempête
resume: In 1847, the Irish potato famine forces Katie O'Neill and her husband to emigrate to a troubled South Africa where Katie runs into an old flame.

title: Las últimas de Filipinas
resume: Two young sisters are shipwrecked on a deserted island with their teacher Ms. Muro.

title: The Flight That Disappeared
resume: A cross-country airliner, whose passengers include a nuclear physicist, a rocket expert, and a mathematical genius, is drawn beyond radar range by an unknown, unbreakable force.

title: Rupan sansei
resume: Le petit-fils d'un gentleman cambrioleur légendaire rassemble une équipe de cambrioleurs pour dérober un collier de Cléopâtre à deux partis: un allié devenu rival et un magnat de la pègre.

title: Un duo d'enfer!
resume: A prostitute and a drifter find themselves bound together as they make their way through the rural South, doing what they have to do to survive.

title: Les bas-fonds d'Hawaï
resume: An American woman goes to Hawaii to search for her husband, MIA since the war, but he's a fugitive from the law and involved in a private feud against his former crime syndicate partners.

title: Salvando al Soldado Pérez
resume: A Mexican crime lord is forced by his mother to plan a suicidal rescue mission to find his lost brother in the most unexpected place on Earth...

title: Le Roi des dinosaures
resume: A new planet moves into the Solar system and four scientists (two couples) are sent to explore planet Nova. In between romantic interludes, the cast faces an iguana masquerading as a Tyrannosaurus rex.

title: Detention of the Dead
resume: A group of oddball high school students find themselves trapped in detention with their classmates having turned into a horde of Zombies.

title: Flight of the Lost Balloon
resume: Un professeur est engagé pour naviguer à travers l'Afrique dans une montgolfière pour sauver un explorateur perdu, mais un mystérieux méchant local nommé "Le Hindou" réquisitionne le ballon à ses propres fins néfastes.

title: Le voyage en ballon
resume: A young boy sneaks onto his grandfather's hot-air balloon and together they travel over France.

title: Le soleil blanc du désert
resume: At the end of the Russian Civil War, Red Army soldier Fyodor Sukhov is ordered to guard the harem of a Caspian Sea guerrilla leader.

title: Big Fat Liar 2
resume: When a scheming producer steals his idea for a new video game, Kevin Shepard and his best friend Becca, declare "GAME ON" and stop at nothing to set the record straight.

title: Le maître du monde
resume: Primitive humans had to adapt to their brutal and savage environment or disappear into oblivion. For Bog, a great warrior, this struggle means conquering the land and gaining supremacy over his rivals.

title: L'homme de Rio
resume: Un jeune homme vient au secours de sa petite amie kidnappée par des voleurs et emmenée à Rio. Une aventure extravagante se poursuit.

title: Sky High: Un été d'enfer!
resume: Three American college students traveling in Greece find themselves accidentally thrust into the world of international espionage when an experimental mind control device falls into their hands.

title: Sous le signe de Rome
resume: Zenobia, Queen of Palmyra, revolts against Rome and defeats the Roman troops - but she makes a big mistake when she falls in love with enemy officer Marco Valerio.

title: Conversations with God
resume: Chronicles the dramatic true journey of a struggling man turned homeless, who inadvertently becomes a spiritual messenger and bestselling author.

title: Fei Ying
resume: Lulu Wong mène une double vie - à la fois bête sociale urbaine et super-héros justicier.

title: Viking Destiny
resume: A Viking Princess is forced to flee her kingdom after being framed for the murder of her father, the King. Under the guidance of the God Odin, she travels the world gaining wisdom and building the army she needs to win back her throne.

title: The Man Who Wasn't There
resume: On his wedding day, a State Department employee is given an egg-shaped device by a dying man with blue vials inside, which can turn people invisible. He finds himself being chased by various parties who want the substance.

title: Joey
resume: Croyant pouvoir communiquer avec son père décédé, un jeune garçon développe des pouvoirs psychiques dont il se sert pour tenter d'arrêter les forces surnaturelles qui menacent sa famille, notamment une poupée ventriloque possédée.

title: Mikaela
resume: Epiphany Eve. An unprecedented snowstorm ravages Spain. Amidst the chaos of a collapsed highway, a group of robbers takes the opportunity to assault an armored van.

title: Le Lac des Cygnes
resume: Un prince tombe amoureux d'une princesse maudite pour se changer en cygne le jour.

title: Le Troisième Homme sur la montagne
resume: Au XIXe siècle, John Winter, alpiniste britannique, veut vaincre un sommet invaincu en Suisse. Aucun guide du village ne veut l'accompagner, sauf Rudi, dont le père est mort quinze ans plus tôt durant une tentative d'ascension de ce sommet

title: Unbranded
resume: Unbranded follows four men and sixteen mustangs on an epic 3,000-mile journey from Mexico to Canada through the American West to inspire adoptions for the 50,000 wild horses and burros in government captivity.

title: Capitaine Fuoco
resume: Baron Oddo de Serra who is cruel to his subjects, is neighbor of the Count Gualtiero of Roccalta. The servants of the baron cross the lands of Count to escape his abuses. Baron hatches a plot to assassinate the earl.

title: The Climb
resume: Two professional solo climbers form an uneasy partnership after a successful rescue mission grants them the gift of a lifetime.

title: L'arche de Noë
resume: Noah is building a whale of a boat in order to save two of every species from a flood that will cover the entire world. Pretty soon, animals are lining up to board the Ark two by two.

title: Saga of Tanya the Evil Movie
resume: Tanya Degurechaff continues her misadventures, avoiding death and being sent to hell, while battling the forces of the Republic Army.

title: Dante's Inferni
resume: Dante goes on a journey through the first and worst part of the afterlife, Hell. Virgil guides and protects Dante on his dark journey descending circle-by-circle to the center of the Earth, and out into Purgatory (sequel).

title: L'ange de Broadway
resume: A cuckolded embezzler on the verge of suicide is helped by a tout, an alcoholic playwright, and a pick-up girl to reimburse the money with a gambling sting.

title: Le Club des crocodiles
resume: Hannes wants to be a member of the Crocodiles, but he must do something dangerous to be part of them. When he is finally a member, they have dangerous adventures together.

title: Bigfoot
resume: Is Bigfoot alive? A hoax? Some claim to have seen him while others think it is a myth.

title: Le Cristal magique
resume: Il existe un cristal magique, qui a le pouvoir de faire revenir l'eau dans la forêt. Mais il a été volé par Bantour, le roi des ours. Seul un héros courageux pourra le rapporter et éviter la sécheresse.

title: La jeune fille et son aigle
resume: Thirteen-year-old Aisholpan trains to become the first female in twelve generations of her nomad family to become an eagle huntress.

title: Les aventuriers du fleuve
resume: Mark Twain's 1851 story about two runaway friends, a fostered white boy and an escaped black slave, who sailed on a raft down the Mississippi River in search of freedom and adventure.

title: The Honor List
resume: A story of four friends and a bucket list.

title: Deep
resume: In 2100, when humanity has abandoned the Earth, a colony of extravagant creatures still thrives in the deepest abyss of the ocean. Deep, an adventurous "dumbo" octopus and the last one of his kind lives there with his two unconditional friends: Evo, a nerdy and clumsy angler fish, and Alice, a neurotic deep-sea shrimp. When an accident destroys their home, the guardian of the abyss, The Kraken, will send Deep and his friends on a perilous journey to find a new home. In their mission, they will be joined by Maura -a voracious moray eel- and together they will travel to amazing places like the submerged city of New York, the Titanic or the Arctic, facing formidable enemies and hilarious situations. Will they be able to bring the oceans back to their former glory?

title: L'homme de Hong Kong
resume: While on dispatch in Australia to extradite a drug courier, a tough Hong Kong cop wages a one-man war against Sydney's most powerful kingpin.

title: Le bateau qui mourut de honte
resume: A trio of ex-servicemen begin smuggling innocuous black market items into post-war Britain, but through greed they graduate to more sinister cargo.

title: Menino Maluquinho: O Filme
resume: The adventures of a nutty little boy of unique personality traits who finds comfort at his grandfather's farm after his parents are divorced.

title: Fais leur vivre l'Enfer Malone
resume: Un détective privé coriace (Malone) s'oppose aux gangsters et à leurs voyous pour protéger un secret précieux. Malone passe par l'enfer pour la protection de l'information, mais il y va aussi de l'enfer....

title: Festin de requin 2 : Le récif se rebelle
resume: Trained in the skills of sea power, Pi the fish can fight a shark, sink a squid or batter any random predator that ever threatens his friends and neighbors on the reef. Unfortunately, being the only hero in town can take its toll, especially when a group of sharks declares that the end of the reef is soon at hand.

title: The returner
resume: A young woman from the future forces a local gunman to help her stop an impending alien invasion which will wipe out the human race.

title: Todd McFarlane's Spawn 2
resume: Spawn - having become plagued by nightmares - discovers that his former Special Forces partner, Chapel, was the one who murdered him. Their paths inevitably cross when Chapel attempts to steal military weapons for Jason Wynn.

title: Phra apai mani
resume: Two princes get banned from Rattana by their father, King Sudas. During their journey, one of the brothers, Apai Mani, gets kidnapped by a giant sea witch who fell in love with him. His brother Sri Suvan and a couple of warriors want to rescue him.

title: One Piece : La Malédiction de l'épée sacrée
resume: The Straw Hat Pirates learn about the Shichiseiken on Asuka Island. Zoro disappears and the marines attack the island. Luffy and his gang fight off the marines when they find happen to find Zoro in enemy lines.

title: Ator l'invincible
resume: Once upon a time a god gave a mighty sword to the king of Aquiles to bring justice to his people. Now he wants it back - but the king would rather give his life than the sword.

title: Tarzan s'évade
resume: An expedition seeking to bring Jane back to civilization, and Tarzan into captivity, gets more than it's bargained for.

title: Un cocktail explosif
