resume: In 1936, a Dutch physician who treats leprosy patients in the jungles of Indonesia has a dangerous run-in with a local witch-doctor who uses black magic to kill his enemies.

title: Davy Crockett et les pirates de la rivière
resume: Davy Crockett et son ami George Russell se rendent à La Nouvelle-Orléans pour vendre des fourrures d'animaux. En chemin, ils participeront à une course de bateaux, seront capturés par des Indiens et démasqueront les pirates de la rivière.

title: Le signe du cobra
resume: A beautiful woman is abducted from her peaceful South Seas home and taken to Cobra Island, where her grandmother Queen wants her to displace her evil twin sister and vengeance against her priest and corrupt advisor.

title: Hercule: La vengeance d'un Dieu
resume: La fiancée d'un jeune homme est kidnappée par un roi impitoyable, Hercule est appelé à l'aide. En exil depuis des années, le guerrier retrouve l'espoir à travers l'amour du garçon pour sa bien-aimée. Ensemble, ils vont combattre le tyran.

title: La Fille de d'Artagnan
resume: France, 1654: la fille de d'Artagnan grandit dans un couvent. Lorsque la mère supérieure est assassinée, Eloïse soupçonne un plan d'assassinat du roi et espère l'empêcher et venger le meurtre en retrouvant son père et les 3 mousquetaires.

title: Maciste contre le cyclope
resume: Strongman Maciste must battle the one-eyed Cyclops monster that is ravaging the land of Sadok, while at the same time fending off the advances of the evil Queen Capys, who wants to do a little ravaging of her own.

title: Kangourou Jack: Bonjour l'Amérique
resume: When poachers kidnap Jackie Legs from the Australian Outback, his friends leap into action! Their attempts to save him route them back to the U.S. into the glitz and glamour of Las Vegas.

title: Leprechaun: Le retour de l'elfe guerrier
resume: Ethel and Tommy Barrick are sent to Ireland to spend the summer with their new stepmother. Once there, they discover her to be an evil, power-seeking witch, with real magical powers and a hatred for all things green.

title: L'oasis des tempêtes
resume: Trois hommes et une femme s'écrasent dans un profond cratère de l'Antarctique, où ils découvrent un monde préhistorique.

title: Breaking In
resume: Professional thief Ernie takes Mike on as an apprentice, but while Mike clearly has "larceny in his heart", it will take him a long time to get as good as Ernie.

title: Le trésor de Whittmore
resume: Visiting the charming lake town of Culver, a boy genius and his sister race against bullies to find a treasure hidden by an eccentric philanthropist.

title: Spymate
resume: Minky, un chimpanzé super espion surentrainé, fait partenaire avec son ex partenaire Mike pour sauver la fille de Mike des intentions d'un scientifique diabolique.

title: Dharam Veer
resume: Movie revolves around two brothers who are separated during birth but meet as adults and form a deep friendship. Also about the challenges that test their friendship.

title: Détective Conan: Le Poing de saphir bleu
resume: After being recovered from a pirate ship sunk in the nineteenth century off the coast of Singapore.

title: Le roi des zombies
resume: On a spooky island, three stranded travelers find an evil doctor working with foreign spies and in control of zombies.

title: Wizard
resume: Matwetwe (Wizard) is a coming of age adventure following Lefa and Papi, best friends and recent high school graduates, on the hustle of their young lives. Over the course of one action packed New Years Eve in the iconic township of Atteridgeville, the boys try to score a huge deal, dodge a king pin gangster and his violent minions, get the girl and ultimately save their lives in this hilarious and sometimes very serious escapade.

title: The Climbers
resume: Les quatre membres du China Everest Climbing Commando affrontent l'ascension la plus difficile. Les quatre premiers échecs leur ont coûté trop de force physique jusqu'à ce que le vent et la neige réduisent l'écart.

title: Bloodfight
resume: Years after retiring from the world of free fighting martial arts, a man returns to the deadly world of fighting after his best student is killed in the tournament.

title: Plight
resume: In an alternate dystopian reality, a forsaken brotherhood of young men diagnosed with autism embarks on a treacherous journey to get life-saving medication for their caregiver.

title: CarGo
resume: A young car learns the importance of family when he embarks on a mission to rescue his father who's been sent to Clunker Island to be re-purposed as junk metal.

title: Les 13 tueurs
resume: A group of samurai plan to assassinate a sadistic feudal lord.

title: Kuroshitsuji
resume: After her supposed death, a young woman returns as the son of her noble family to precede the family's prestigious company, with a demon at her side to avenge her parent's murder.

title: Le Brigand Briquambroque
resume: When the robber Hotzenplotz steals a grandmother's coffee grinder, Kasperl and his friend Seppel set out to get it back from him.

title: Solver
resume: When Luke Williams arrives at his late grandfather's cabin, he discovers a mysterious puzzle leading to a dangerous secret.

title: Les Étrangleurs de Bombay
resume: In the 1830s, a captain in the East India Company lobbies to investigate the criminal Thugee Cult of Kali, an organized crime group of stranglers and thieves.

title: Le pays des rêves
resume: Two wannabe heroes and their friends must stop a madman from giving everyone nightmares.

title: Geng: Pengembaraan Bermula
resume: In his grandfather's village, a boy hears of a scary beast living deep in the woods. He and his friends embark on an adventure to find answers.

title: Kaal
resume: Un expert en tigres, sa femme, deux touristes et un chef de village s'engagent dans une bataille pour leur survie contre des bêtes surnaturelles dans le parc national de Jim Corbett.

title: Antarctica
resume: Deux scientifiques japonais, Ushioda et Ochi, développent un lien avec leurs chiens de traîneau lors d'une expédition. Ils se voient obligés de repartir à la recherche des chiens abandonnés par inadvertance en Antarctique.

title: La bataille de Marathon
resume: Un soldat Grec mène le combat face à l'invasion de l'armée Perse.

title: La belle espionne
resume: Un contrebandier tombe amoureux d'une mystérieuse espionne, chargée de découvrir les projets d'une invasion de l'Angleterre par Napoléon. Il tente de découvrir l'identité de la femme.

title: Las viboras cambian de piel
resume: A hired gun wants to complete his last big job--killing a sheriff who hides away inside an old monastery--so he can retire with a prostitute.

title: Partners in Crime
resume: Two exes cross paths once again, but when they get involved in a crime, the duo must find a way out of their dilemma together.

title: Star Wars: A Droid Story
resume: Série animée avec R2D2 et C3PO, le plus célèbre duo de droïdes de la galaxie.

title: Modrý tygr
resume: In a city ruled by the diabolical Mayor, it appears that only one thing can save the old botanical garden from being demolished for the construction of an entertainment center: the Blue Tiger. Now it is up to Johanka and Matyas to protect the tiger from the evil clutches of the Mayor and his henchmen and save the garden.

title: Aanandam
resume: A coming of age drama exploring love, life and friendship as a class of second year engineering students set out on their very first college tour to the exotic lands of Hampi and Goa.

title: Yezhu Kadal Yezhu Malai
resume: Caught between family duty and romantic love, a young man faces an impossible choice.

title: Le Paradis des mauvais garçons
resume: Nick Cochran, un américain en exil à Macao, peut sauver sa réputation s'il aide à capturer un seigneur du crime international. Infiltré, peut-il tromper les méchants et, en même temps, courtiser la belle chanteuse et petite escroc, Julie Benson ?

title: Hung cheuk wong ji
resume: Two magically powerful monks are sent on a quest to fight the King of Hell.

title: Wish Upon a Unicorn
resume: After 8-year-old Mia loses her mother, her family moves to Grandma's Montana ranch. In the woods, Mia discovers a unicorn colt: a magical creature that brings luck to anyone who believes in it.

title: Pokémon Ranger et le Temple des mers
resume: Our heroes must protect the Prince of the Sea, Manaphy, from the evil pirate Phantom, and return the young Pokémon to the Sea Temple with the help of the the People of the Water and Jackie the Pokémon Ranger.

title: Les mines du Roi Salomon
resume: White hunter Allan Quartermain and his enigmatic guide help a young Irish woman locate her missing father in unexplored Darkest Africa.

title: Delia's Gone
resume: Un condamné s'engage dans un voyage de violence et de rédemption pour découvrir la vérité sur la mort de sa sœur.

title: Max Reload and the Nether Blasters
resume: A small town video game store clerk must go from zero to hero after accidentally unleashing the forces of evil from a cursed Colecovision video game cartridge.

title: iNumber Number: L'or de Johannesbourg
resume: Lorsqu'un policier sous couverture est chargé d'enquêter sur un vol d'or historique à Johannesburg, il est contraint de choisir entre sa conscience et la loi.

title: Z
resume: The western frontier has re-emerged and, as in the past, a hero will answer the people's cry for justice.

title: Deadheads
resume: Two inexplicably coherent zombies awake amidst a zombie attack, and decide to take a road trip to find the one's lost love, unaware they are being chased by the agents of a ruthless company with its own agenda.

title: La flèche et le flambeau
resume: Dardo, un personnage semblable à Robin des Bois, et ses fidèles partisans utilisent une ruine romaine dans la Lombardie médiévale comme quartier général pour mener une insurrection contre leurs conquérants.

title: Deadpool Movie in Lego
resume: A shot-for-shot remake of the 2016 movie, Deadpool, created entirely out of Lego.

title: San cheng mou moon 1991
resume: Lau Ching, a Mainlander with an incredibly powerful right arm, arrives in Hong Kong to find his cousin.

title: Doraemon: Nobita to tsubasa no yûsha tachi
resume: Doraemon, Nobita and friends help the humanoid birds of Birdopia to stop Seagrid from awakening Phoenicia a Dragon like Monster Which can bring an End to Both Birdopia and Human World.

title: Les Guerriers de l'apocalypse
resume: Japanese soldiers time travel to feudal era. Their lieutenant allies with samurai lord to become Shogun. Both seek power through different eras' warfare.

title: Vuk le petit renard
resume: Famous, great hunters, better stay away, here comes Vuk! (They say he is cunning as a fox!)

title: Pokemon 15: Kyurem vs la Lame de la Justice
resume: An over zealous pokemon called Keldeo enrages a very powerful Kyurem. With the help of Ash and Pikachu, can Keldeo become a sword of justice and defeat the mighty Kyurem?

title: Yahsi Bati
resume: In 1881, two Ottoman Secret Agents travel to the USA, at the Sultan's request, to deliver a valuable diamond as a gift for the President.

title: Kabaneri of the Iron Fortress: Unato Decisive Battle
resume: The film chronicles the attempt of the team to take back Unato castle.

title: Le tour du monde en 80 jours
resume: Un ouistiti se lance dans une folle aventure pour faire le tour de la planète en 80 jours après avoir accepté le défi d'une grenouille gourmande.

title: Everest Dark
resume: A Nepalese mountaineer risks everything to retrieve a fallen climber's body and honor the mountain gods, offering a rare local perspective on Everest.

title: Ana y Bruno
resume: An animated adventure about a young girl who seeks out her father in order to help save her troubled mother.

title: Thursday
resume: Grey Malcolm is a talented young assassin who's ready to get his life back. But before he can leave, he has one final assignment: kill a bank robber who has the city's underground up in arms. As Malcolm tracks his target he learns that his rival is also on the trail - and will stop at nothing to get Malcolm out of the picture. As the trail goes cold, Malcolm realizes that those close to him are being used as the bait - and that this assignment will prove to be the most challenging job he's ever seen, and it could be the most deadly.

title: Calloway le trappeur
resume: A strong-willed family in a small New England town struggles against tremendous odds to realize their dream of establishing a sanctuary for the great flocks of wild geese that migrate overhead.

title: San Andreas Quake: Magnitude 10
resume: When a discredited L.A. seismologist warns of an impending 12.7 earthquake, no one takes her seriously. Now on her own, she races desperately to get her family to safety before the earthquake breaks Los Angeles apart from the mainland.

title: Les aventures de Quentin Durward
resume: A Scottish knight in France to facilitate a marriage between a rich and beautiful countess and his aging uncle becomes involved in court intrigue.

title: Games of Rome : Les jeux de l'Empire
resume: A slave dancer is freed from her Roman masters by an Amazon warrior and is trained as an Amazon warrior and seeks vengeance on the ambitious corrupt Roman general who attacked her village and slain her family.

title: Code Geass: Boukoku no Akito 1 - Yokuryuu wa Maiorita
resume: The story takes place in Europe in the year a.t.b. 2017. A Knightmare unit made of boys and girls from Area Eleven are thrown into a military operation with a 5%chance of survival. They must rescue an allied unit left behind on the European warfront.

title: Chelovek niotkuda
resume: In the 1960s, a Soviet spacecraft crashed, and the cosmonaut wakes up in Moscow in 2023.

title: Last Flight Out
resume: A clean family movie of action, humor, and love. Pilot Dan's mission: rescue a woman working a jungle clinic in midst of warfare. She and another are willing to sacrifice their lives for villagers. A daring rescue results in a changed life. Planes, helicopter, explosions, and Samaritan's Purse are elements.

title: Le hold-up du siècle
resume: A motley crew of treasure hunters plan to rob the cruise-liner RMS Queen Mary, using a recovered WW2 German submarine.

title: Inara, the Jungle Girl
resume: 'Inara, The Jungle Girl' launches viewers into the life of Inara a young girl in the military whose world comes crashing down when her father passes away after a failed mission to the island of N'iah. Inara curious of her father's death learns of a new opportunity to travel to the island and learns that the jungle and the women that inhabit it have more in common with her than she could ever know.

title: Le mystère du château noir
resume: Man investigates the disappearance of two of his friends who were the guests of a sinister Austrian count.

title: Détective Conan: Mémoire assassine
resume: Three Police officers get murdered. Then, Ran saw the murderer murder her best friend and she lost her memory. Now Conan and Inspector Megure are trying to find the murderer.

title: Whisper - Libres comme le vent
resume: Mika is sent to spend the summer at her strict grandmother's horse farm. She is hesitant at first, but when she meets the wild stallion Ostwind, Mika discovers her amazing horse whispering powers.

title: L'Amazone nue
resume: Exploitation documentary: A white girl is part of an expedition into the dark Amazon jungle. In addition to native nudity (sex) there are animal killings (violence).

title: Tango Charlie
resume: Tarun Chauhan, a rookie army officer undergoes ups and downs in his mission and learns the true meaning of 'war' to overcome his weaknesses.

title: Mirai shônen Konan Tokubetsu-hen: Kyodaiki Giganto no Fukkatsu
resume: In the future, some humans build a spaceship to abandon earth. The spaceship crashed in an island isolated from the rest of the world. The story takes place when there are only 2 survivors in the island: Conan a boy born in the island and his grandfather. Then the world discover them.

title: Nordfor sola
resume: Two young men decide to spend an archive circle Norwegian winter in the isolated and uninhabited bay of Norway. Their home is built from salvaged material washed up onshore. They surf every day with much time for self reflection.

title: Il était une fois en Chine : Le Tournoi du lion
resume: Maître Wong et ses disciples s'inscrivent à la "compétition du lion dansant" afin d'arrêter un complot d'assassinat et de combattre un adversaire arrogant et fourbe.

title: Urga
resume: A curious friendship develops between Gombo, a young Mongolian shepherd living with his wife and family in a hut, deep in the wilderness of the steppes, and Sergei, a Russian worker whose truck breaks down not far from Gombo's hut.

title: Jungle Jack
resume: Au cœur de la forêt tropicale, Jungle Jack vit insouciant avec ses amis Zik et Zak et Cobra le serpent. Mais Jungle Jack ne se doute pas du danger qui le guette. La méchante vedette de cinéma Isabella Scorpion veut le capturer à tout prix.

title: The Harry Hill Movie
resume: When he thinks his hamster Abu (Johnny Vegas) has just a week to live, Harry Hill (Harry Hill) and his Nan (Dame Julie Walters) take the hamster to Blackpool. However, Harry's twin Otto (Matt Lucas) wants to kidnap Abu, and sends Ed (Simon Bird) and Kisko (Guillaume Delauney) to pursue them.

title: Les aventures de Marco Polo
resume: Adventurer Marco Polo travels to China, where he finds the Emperor Kublai Khan, court intrigue, danger, and unexpected love.

title: Force 5
resume: A martial-arts expert leads a team of fellow martial artists to rescue a senator's daughter from an island ruled by the evil leader of a fanatical religious cult.

title: Les Révoltés du Vénus
resume: A new midshipman joins a frigate, encountering mutiny, pirates, mistaken identities, and shipwrecks while navigating Spanish waters with his captain, lover, and friend. Survival is uncertain in this swashbuckling adventure.

title: Joram
resume: Un père est en fuite avec sa petite fille pour échapper aux fantômes de son passé et aux forces qui veulent sa mort.

title: Le Texan chanceux
resume: Jerry Mason, a young Texan, and Jake Benson, an old rancher, become partners and strike it rich with a gold mine. They then find their lives complicated by bad guys and a woman.

title: The Legend of Johnny Lingo
resume: When a storm washes a canoe bearing an infant boy ashore upon a small South Pacific island, he is at first well-received as a gift from the heavens, even to the point of the tribal chief adopting him as a successor.

title: Yunnan chong gu
resume: Once again the legendary tomb explorer Hu Bayi is on a dangerous mission as he seeks out the Tomb of Emperor Xian, located on an island of monstrous creatures in this mystical action-adventure.

title: BoBoiBoy: The Movie
resume: A group of alien treasure hunters named The Tengkotak has arrived on earth and kidnapped Ochobot in order to use him to locate an ancient and powerful Power Sphere hiding on earth. BoBoiBoy and his super friends must now race against time to save Ochobot and uncover the secrets behind the Sfera Kuasa. Their journey will take them on an adventure filled with action, comedy, and beautiful locales.

title: Jake Speed
resume: In a world where, unbeknownst to the public, all famous pulp fiction heroes are real, one of them, Jake Speed, agrees to help desperate Margaret Winston save her sister from sadistic white slaver Sid, who's operating in Africa.

title: La possédée du vice
resume: A beautiful Italian woman, Paola (Nadia Cassini) is told by her black friend (Evaristo Márquez) about the Caribbean love god Jambaya who appears in the form of the snake. By the end of the movie, Paola decides to give herself to Jambaya while a local woman named Stella (Beryl Cunningham) departs with her white friend's ex-lover, establishing a neat symmetry between their respective fantasies of exoticism.

title: La fille du bois maudit
resume: A railroad man from the city befriends a mountain girl in a Kentucky family feud.

title: Quels seront les cinq?
resume: A plane has engine trouble while flying over a jungle inhabited by cannibals.

title: Les Trois Lanciers du Bengale
resume: Three British soldiers on the Northwest Frontier of India struggle against the enemy - and themselves.

title: Sur la piste du Marsupilami
resume: Dan Geraldo, reporter en quête de scoop, arrive en Palombie. Avec un guide local, ils vont se lancer dans une aventure et révéler une nouvelle extraordinaire : le Marsupilami, animal mythique et facétieux, existe vraiment !

title: La véritable histoire du Chat Botté
resume: An adaptation of Charles Perrault's famous Puss'n Boots, "The True Story of Puss'n Boots" is a story for young and old for the first time on cinema screens.

title: Dark Mission (Les fleurs du mal)
resume: An undercover C.I.A. Agent goes to South America to stop a drug syndicate.

title: Natural Selection
resume: Having discovered that her dying husband has an illegitimate child living in Florida, a devout Christian housewife leaves her sheltered world on a mission to reunite father and son.

title: Eva: Pendakian Terakhir
resume: Eva is a girl who is trying to recover from deep sadness after losing her mother.

title: Pinocchio et Gepetto
resume: Puppeteer Geppetto becomes a puppet himself after drinking an elixir that Pinocchio bought from a traveling carnival.

title: La captive aux yeux clairs
resume: La réussite du voyage est liée à la survie de la jeune fille indienne ainsi que sur leur capacité à mener à bien des échanges commerciaux avec les Pieds-Noirs.

title: Objectif Lune
resume: Objectif Lune est une aventure familiale qui suit Mike Goldwing, un surfeur de 12 ans, qui, avec l'aide de ses amis, de son grand-père ex-astronaute et d'un lézard de compagnie fou nommé Igor, s'envole pour la lune afin de sauver le monde.

title: Odela2
resume: In a remote village, steeped in rich cultural heritage and age-old traditions, its true saviour Odela Mallanna Swamy always protects his village from evil forces.

title: Si Juki the Movie: Harta Pulau Monyet
resume: Juki again experienced a problem that most people often experience. In the midst of the family's difficult financial conditions, Si Juki finds a treasure map left by his ancestors.

title: Le tour du monde sous les mers
resume: The crew of a five-man submarine travels the world oceans, planting sensors on the ocean floor to warn scientists of any impending earthquakes.

title: Maîtresse des singes
resume: The wife of a famous anthropologist is rushed to hospital in labor. At the same time, druggies raid the hospital looking for drugs, causing the baby to be stillborn. While recovering from the trauma, she learns that her husband has disappeared in Africa. She launches an expedition to find him, and discovers a bizarre world of sexy jungle women!

title: Avane Srimannarayana
resume: In the pursuit of solving an ancient mystery of Amaravati, Narayana, a corrupt cop must battle the dangerous clan of dacoits and it's fierce leader.

title: Chicago Overcoat
resume: The fates of an aging hitman and a washed up detective become entwined when one last job leads to one last chance to settle an old score.

title: Ulysses : Voyage au coeur des ténèbres
resume: ODYSSEUS, The Warrior King, has been away from Ithaca for twenty years. The first ten he spent fighting the Trojan War; the last ten he spent fighting to get home. Among his adventures is the tale Homer felt was too horrific to tell; the missing book of The Odyssey known as... THE ISLE OF THE MISTS.

title: La sueur sur la peau
resume: After escaping from a juvenile correctional institution, nine women find refuge in a deserted island, where seven men, led by an ex-Nazi, are searching for a buried treasure. Can they survive when there's nowhere to hide?

title: Mugamoodi
resume: A hopeless young man uses his "Kung-fu" skills and mask to tackle a bank robbery group without revealing his identity.

title: Maya, donne-moi un titre
resume: A father and daughter maintain their bond despite living in different countries through an imaginative nightly ritual where she suggests a title and he creates short animated films starring her as the hero.

title: Hollywood Adventures
resume: A young man goes from China to Hollywood on short notice to find his girlfriend. He ends up connected with two others in his quest, which gets much more complicated than he envisioned.

title: 31 Minutos: La Película
resume: The rag-tag crew of world famous TV news show 31 Minutos goes into the sea to a mistery island to rescue their beloved producer Juanin Juan Harry.

title: Hex
resume: Après une mystérieuse disparition lors d'un saut, un groupe de parachutistes est confronté à des phénomènes paranormaux qui les obligent à lutter pour leur vie.

title: Sangraal
resume: A swordsman's wife is murdered by followers of the evil Goddess Rani. He vows vengeance upon the cult and journeys to the Ark of the Templars to get a magic crossbow that will help him accomplish his mission.

title: Simon au pays des globules
resume: A little kid shrinks himself so that he can travel into the body of his grandfather. Here he has to kill the kidney-stone his grandfather is suffering from.

title: Rudolph, le petit renne au nez rouge: Le film
resume: It's up to Santa's most famous reindeer to save the day when an evil queen conjures up a storm on Christmas.

title: L'empreinte du dragon rouge
resume: In 1910, Hong Kong members of a secret Tong crime syndicate protect their identities by murdering the daughter of a British sea captain who vows revenge.

title: Angélique, marquise des anges
resume: Dans le premier volet de la série Angélique, notre jeune et belle héroïne fougueuse se retrouve impliquée dans un complot d'assassinat politique et est fiancée à un inconnu de douze ans son aîné, qu'on prétend sorcier.

title: Under the Crystal Sky
resume: An Indigenous family encounters a life changing celestial phenomenon while struggling for survival in the 1800s Southwest.

title: Joseph Andrews
resume: Angleterre, XVIIIème siècle. Joseph Andrews est abandonné dès son plus jeune âge chez la sulfureuse Lady Booby. Bientôt séduite par ses charmes, la maîtresse dévergondée tente de l'initier aux délices de l'amour..

title: Le territoire des loups
resume: A two-week trek through the Cascade Mountains tries the survival instincts of five adventurous teenagers. At first, it's all a good time. Shooting the rapids, exploring caves and making new friends. But when an accident occurs, Mother Nature raises the stakes and challenges the hikers to the greatest test of their young lives.

title: The War of the Worlds: The Musical Drama
resume: An Audible Original Production in which H.G. Wells' classic, War of the Worlds, is revisited

title: Gun City
resume: En 1921, alors qu'anarchistes et policiers s'affrontent à Barcelone, un agent joue sur les deux fronts pour découvrir qui a volé des armes et éviter une guerre civile.

title: Sherni
resume: Un agent forestier intègre qui s'efforce de trouver un équilibre dans un monde de conflits entre l'homme et l'animal, continue de chercher sa véritable vocation dans un environnement hostile.

title: Le fils du Cheik
resume: The son of the sheik and a dancing girl fall in love, but when he is made to believe she has betrayed him he seeks revenge.

title: Le roman de Renard
resume: Lorsque les farces espiègles de Renard vont trop loin, le Roi Lion est obligé de traduire l'escroc en justice.

title: Death Zone: Cleaning Mount Everest
resume: The dramatic self-documented story of 20 elite Nepali climbers who venture into the "Death Zone" of Mount Everest to restore their sacred mountain and the contaminated water source of 1.3 billion people.

title: At Her Feet
resume: Archeology students and their Hawaiian guide encounter unseen allies and a misguided protector as they risk their lives saving artifacts in the path of an erupting volcano in Hawaii Volcanoes National Park.

title: Jak rozpetalem druga wojne swiatowa
resume: The adventures of unlucky Polish soldier Franek Dolas during world war II. In September he escapes from Stalag and goes to France. After that he fights in Africa and Europe.

title: Kim
resume: Pendant le Raj britannique, l'orphelin d'un soldat britannique se fait passer pour un hindou et est déchiré entre sa loyauté envers un mystique bouddhiste et son aide aux services secrets anglais.

title: On m'appelle Zapper
resume: A female private detective, Harriet Zapper, is hired by a rich old man to find his missing children, and becomes involved in counterfeiting and murder

title: Die Schule der magischen Tiere 2
resume: The students of the school of magical animals want to perform a musical for the school's anniversary. Will the rehearsals end in chaos or will the class pull together? And what's up with the strange holes on the school grounds?

title: Oculus
resume: Zia Lainey, shattered by the loss of her son, awakens inside the afterlife of the Oculus, transforming her into Zylah, Leader of the Suits. As she navigates this enigmatic realm, Zylah grapples with her new-found identity and revenge to hold those who are responsible. All while seeking solace and understanding for her own grief.

title: An Egypt Affair
resume: Un mari rejeté. Une belle étrangère. Une liaison dangereuse. Pour deux couples qui profitent d'une spectaculaire aventure égyptienne, la trahison et la tromperie naviguent sur le Nil en même temps qu'eux.

title: Liane fille sauvage
resume: A scientist and his nephew are hosts of Lana, queen of the Amazons. Meanwhile, other white men penetrate the Brazilian jungle, wishing to find and take the legendary Amazons' treasure.

title: Iyobinte Pusthakam
resume: Set in the pre-independent India, Aloshi returns from the war to his estranged family and childhood love, only to find his elder brothers taking the side of a ruthless business man to overthrow their father.

title: La princesse et le pirate
resume: A cowardly actor and a runaway princess are voyaging on a ship that is captured by a notorious pirate who recently buried his treasure on a secretly mapped island.

title: The Roblox Movie
resume: In the world of Roblox, three friends must save their world from an evil entity set on taking over their homeworld.

title: Xun Long Jue · Mi Zong
resume: The story follows the team as they try to raid a tomb made by master tomb raiders. It is set partially in Russia and will involve scenes at Catherine Palace in St. Petersburg.

title: Iguana
resume: In the 19th century, a bullied, disfigured man dubbed Iguana flees from abusive locals, finds his own island and declares himself tyrant of his new domain. A man and a woman get stranded there and become victims of his new sadistic nature.

title: Échec à Borgia
resume: An unscrupulous agent for the Borgias suffers a change of heart when asked to betray a noble count and his much younger, very beautiful wife.

title: Zak & Wowo, la légende de Lendarys
resume: Zak part à la recherche de son jumeau Kyle, qui a mystérieusement disparu. Muni d'une pierre de jade magique, il est accompagné de sa grand-mère NaïNaï, une belle hors-la-loi capable de communiquer avec les créatures fantastiques.

title: Doraemon: Nobita to robotto kingudamu
resume: A robot empress schemes to strip emotions from all robots in a parallel world. Doraemon and companions must prevent her sinister plan after arriving through their time machine.

title: Yolki 11
resume: Uncle Yura, serves as a security guard in an elite village, raises a mini-pig Kostya and does not like New Year at all.

title: Running Man: Revengers
resume: On the eve of the annual Running Man competition, the players race against one another through a series of challenges to obtain the 'Super Belt,' a legendary item which make its wearer absolute ruler of the world.

title: Lena and Snowball
resume: Brimée à l'école et seule à la maison, Lena continue d'espérer qu'elle aura un jour un véritable ami. Un après-midi, ses rêves deviennent réalité, sous la forme d'un lionceau blanc câlin.

title: Le serment du chevalier noir
resume: During King Arthur's time, a sword maker wishes to win Lady Linet's heart but first he must become a noble knight.

title: Gamera contre Barugon
resume: A giant monster that emits a destructive ray from its back attacks Japan and takes on Gamera.

title: Eiga Kureyon Shinchan: Bakauma! B-kyu gurume sabaibaru!!
resume: In the story, Shin-chan and the Kasukabe Defence Group members were supposed to go to the B-class Gourmet Carnival. But, just then, a mysterious person asked Shin-chan to deliver a sauce to the carnival.

title: Les aventuriers
resume: After WW1, Zeb and Thor start a cannery business in Alaska but eventually they drift apart with Zeb becoming unscrupulous and Thor becoming involved in Alaskan politics.

title: Mon Ninja et moi 2
resume: Alex et le Checkered Ninja se lancent dans une chasse effrénée au méchant Phillip Eppermint, qui a échappé à une peine de prison en Thaïlande.

title: Simbad et le calife de Bagdad
resume: The sailor Sinbad is dragged by two cheaters on board a ship on which the beautiful Sherazade travels, promised to the Caliph of Baghdad.

title: Oups! J'ai encore raté l'arche...
resume: À la dérive après une inondation, deux naufragés tentent de réunir une famille peu conventionnelle, de franchir un volcan et de négocier un accord de paix.

title: Return to the Lost World
resume: When Belgian scientist Bertram Hammonds arrives in the Lost World to drill for crude oil, Professors Challenger and Summerlee return to the Lost World plateau.

title: Salons de massage
resume: France, a reporter working from an international news agency, manages to be paid to visit all of Munich's massage parlors. He wants to find the whereabouts of Sonia, a personal masseuse with whom he experienced perfect bliss.

title: Behind That Curtain
resume: Eve Mannering realizes too late that her abusive husband is a philanderer and murderer and seeks protection with her true love, explorer John Beetham.

title: Le Club des 5 - le film
resume: Five kids and a dog investigate the disappearance of a professor, uncovering a conspiracy involving criminals related to his alternative energy project; they attempt to rescue him from kidnappers.

title: La vengeance de Siegfried
resume: Terminant son initiation chez le nain Mime, Siegfried se forge une épée et va tuer le dragon Fafnir se baignant dans son sang pour acquérir l'invincibilité. Mais une feuille de frêne se colle sur son dos, lui laissant une partie vulnérable

title: Pilgrim's Progress
resume: An allegory of the life of a believer on a journey from the City of Destruction to the Celestial City.

title: Adiós
resume: Un escroc à la liberté surveillée se lance sur un sanglant chemin de vengeance lorsque sa jeune fille meurt dans un accident de voiture après la fête de sa première communion.

title: Le monde des maudits
resume: Earth has been ravaged by a nuclear war, and a feminist warrior is forced to join up with a soldier of fortune in her journey to find a rumored "paradise" as they battle gangs of rampaging bandits.

title: Alien Predator War
resume: When a band of ruthless alien predators invade Earth, a team of soldiers must team up with a group of alien refugees to fight back and save humanity.

title: One Piece: Le Royaume de Chopper - L'Étrange Île des animaux
resume: As the Straw Hat Pirates sail through the Grand Line. Chopper has been teased by Usopp about him not being brave enough to face dangers like a real pirate. They spot an upcoming island, and according to Nami's map reading. The island is called Crown Island, which is said to hold a crown treasure. A line of geysers erupted from under the Going Merry. And the whole crew find themselves flying over the island. Unfortunatly, Chopper fell off the ship and was separated from his friends. Luffy and the others landed on the other side of the island and were greeted by an elderly parrot, who tells them that Crown Island is home to many bizarre talking animals. Chopper meanwhile finds himself being worshiped as the island's new king by the animals. According to Momambi(a jungle boy) a new king appears from the heavens when the old one pasts away. Momambi was over joy to have someone like Chopper to be their new king. But Chopper doesn't want to hold that title and tries to reason that he's really a pirate. Momambi, refused for Chopper to take the path of being a pirate. And insists that he'll be much happier as Crown Island's ruler. To make matters worse, a trio of human "horn" hunters are on the island. The leader, Count Butler is a violin playing/horn eating human who wants to eat the island's treasure to inherit immense power. Will Luffy & the rest be able to prevent the count from terrorizing the island? And will they be able to convince Momambi that not all pirates are bad?

title: Doraemon: Nobita no kyôryû
resume: After bringing a fossilized egg back to life with the Time Cloth, Nobita finds himself the owner of a baby dinosaur. Everything is fine until it grows up. Nobita and friends use Doraemon's time machine to return it back to its own time.

title: Thomas & Friends: Big World! Big Adventures!
resume: Thomas leaves Sodor to fulfil his dream of seeing the world. This heroic quest takes Thomas across deserts, through jungles and over dangerous mountains as he travels across five continents seeing sights he has never seen before.

title: Eiga Crayon Shin-chan gekitotsu! Rakuga kingudamu to hobo yonin no yûsha
resume: The Scribble Kingdom in the sky which charges it's life energy with scribbling is endangered when the people in the world lessen their scribbling. The military is send in to enforce more scribbling.

title: The River Rat
resume: After serving time for a murder he didn't commit, all Billy wants to do is to reconnect with his daughter. However, some loose ends, like the whereabouts of the stolen loot, just won't let him go.

title: La jeunesse des trois mousquetaires
resume: Young Blades follows D'artagnan (Hugh Dancy), a young arrogant swordsman; Radegonde (Sarah-Jane Potts), a clever girl he meets in the woods; and a trio of Musketeers as they attempt to thwart a plot to send France and Spain into war.

title: Chhota Bheem Paanch Ajoobe
resume: Dhuni Baba wakes up with a start and pulls out an old staff. He grows nostalgic and remembers his master holding the same staff and teaching five other students. They all learnt yoga and martial arts from this master. Seven guys learn different martial arts while Dhuni Baba has an understanding of all. He abruptly and exclaims, 'They martial warriors are coming!'

title: La fièvre du pétrole
resume: Two buddies who rise from fly-by-night wildcatters to oil tycoons over a ten-year period, are in love with the same woman.

title: Bon Voyage!
resume: A family takes a long delayed trip to Europe and finds an unending series of comedy adventures.

title: Don't Lose Your Head
resume: During French Revolution, English nobles Sir Rodney and Lord Darcy aid French aristocracy against Robespierre. Disguised as "Black Fingernail", Sir Rodney battles Camembert and Bidet, French secret police leaders.

title: Virgo and the Sparklings
resume: Riani, a teenager who is forced to reveal her hidden powers when several mysterious cases occur and turn the city into chaos.

title: El Coyote y la Bronca
resume: El ranchero Juan 'El Coyote' y Trinidad tienen una familia ejemplar de cual son muy orgullosos. Un dia, los hijos de Juan se meten en grandes problemas provocando un terrible acontecimiento en el pueblo y dañando el nombre de la familia.

title: Gawain et le chevalier vert
resume: The medieval legend of a supernatural knight who challenges the king's men to kill him.

title: Kong, le roi des singes
resume: Boosting this family-friendly take on the 1933 film are the acting talents of Jodi Benson and Dudley Moore.

title: Le pays sauvage
resume: A family leaves city life to take possession of a Wyoming ranch.

title: La Légende du dragon rouge
resume: En Chine, Hung Xi Guan, un moine Shaolin désespéré par la mort de sa famille, se révolte contre l'autorité impériale. Avec son jeune fils, qu'il initie aux arts martiaux, il se lance à la recherche des meurtriers

title: Karthikeya 2
resume: Une suite du thriller Karthikeya, qui traite des problèmes personnels de Karthik et de la façon dont il s'en sort. Sa quête de la vérité l'amène à découvrir le pouvoir de l'ancien système indien et du Tatva du Seigneur Sri Krishna.

title: Compagnon d'aventure
resume: A wealthy sportsman's decision to hire a backwoods orphan to exercise a champion Irish Setter has unexpected consequences.

title: Beneath Loch Ness
resume: The legendary Loch Ness Monster, terrorizes a lake in Scotland and Patrick Bergin comes out to kill it.

title: Magic Boys
resume: After witnessing a murder, a hapless pair of misfits escape their own near death experience by posing as male strippers - only to find themselves neck deep in even bigger trouble.

title: Les turbans rouges
resume: To protest against British oppression and tyranny a tribal leader becomes a bandit.

title: Le boulet
resume: Les aventures loufoques de Moltès, caïd en prison et Reggio, un garde. Après remporté gros au loto, ils participent à un rallye en Afrique pour retrouver le bulletin gagnant et sont pourchassés par le Turc, un ennemi juré de Moltès.

title: Les douze heures
resume: Un ancien aristocrate russe miséreux à l'aube de l'ère de l'Union soviétique part à la recherche d'un trésor en diamants caché dans une des douze chaise du salon de sa belle mère, mobilier confisqué et dispersé dans tout le pays.

title: Kuntilanak 3
resume: Dinda, who is considered strange by the village children because of her strength, accidentally injures Panji and Ambar. She regrets and asks Aunt Donna to register her at the Mata Hati School, so that she can learn to control her power.

title: Deiji
resume: About a tragic love triangle story involving young painter Hye-young, Interpol detective Jeong Woo, and professional hitman Park Yi.

title: Canoa
resume: A group of university employees arrive in a small village during a hiking expedition. Once there, the local priest accuses them of being university students who're attempting to spread communism and mobilizes the townspeople to lynch them.

title: L'enquête sacrée
resume: En l'an 35, un tribun romain est envoyé en Palestine pour enquêter sur la mort et l'éventuelle résurrection de notre Seigneur Jésus de Nazareth.

title: La revanche des gueux
resume: Le roi d'Angleterre cherche à faire périr le fils de Robin des Bois, pour se venger du père, qui l'a autrefois vaincu. Le jeune Robin regroupe les anciens compagnons de son père et entre en lutte contre le despote.

title: Les musiciens de Brême
resume: The popular children's tale about a donkey, a dog, a cat, and a rooster who are on their way to the slaughterhouse when they get a lucky break and escape.

title: Impact final
resume: Après l'impact d'une météorite qui déclenche une nouvelle ère glaciaire, un groupe de survivants tente de trouver un appareil qui pourrait redonner espoir à l'humanité

title: Le sauvage
resume: À la veille de son mariage avec un homme de la haute société, Nelly change d'avis et prend la fuite. Alors qu'il la poursuit, elle fait irruption dans la vie de Martin, un homme solitaire qui occupe la chambre voisine de son hôtel.

title: Nocturna, la nuit magique
resume: Tim, un garçon orphelin, a peur du noir. Toutefois, lorsque les étoiles s'éteignent dans le ciel, il se retrouve à explorer le monde de la nuit avec son nouvel ami, le Berger de Chats, pour découvrir pourquoi.

title: La Bataille de la montagne du Tigre
resume: Une histoire qui raconte le conflit entre une escouade de l'Armée populaire de libération et une troupe de bandits dans le nord-est de la Chine pendant la révolution chinoise.

title: For Y'ur Height Only
resume: The diminutive Agent 00 must rescue a kidnapped scientist and stop a mysterious warlord from taking over the world.

title: Le Monde du silence
resume: A documentary about the undersea explorers and how they penetrate into the underwater world.

title: Kina & Yuk: renards de la banquise
resume: Kina et Yuk, deux renards polaires prêts à fonder une famille, vivent sur la banquise, mais la température trop douce perturbe la nature et les sépare. Ils vont braver tous les dangers pour se retrouver avant la naissance de leurs petits.

title: Les maraudeurs attaquent
resume: Pendant la Seconde Guerre mondiale, une unité américaine de 3000 hommes, connue sous le nom de Merrill's Marauders, combat les forces japonaises en Birmanie.

title: Torna 2
resume: In this Iranian sci-fi, a professor builds a restaurant; that restaurant then turns into a spaceship. Then enter four troublesome teenagers who will go with the professor on the ship that takes them on a journey to an unknown land.

title: Baby Shark's Big Movie!
resume: Suivez Baby Shark et sa famille alors qu'ils quittent Chomp City, la grande ville des requins.

title: Nôgêmu nôraifu: Zero
resume: Adaption of the sixth Light Novel of series, it follows the story of two new characters, Riku and Schwi, during the events of the Great War prior to the Ten Covenants.

title: La Leyenda de la Llorona
resume: A group of kids must stop a ghost who abduct kids after the drowning of her own children.

title: Road Wars: Max Fury
resume: Dans un terrain vague post-apocalyptique, deux sœurs quittent leur forteresse pour sauver leur mère blessée.

title: Le Saint: les créateurs de fictions
resume: Amos Klein, auteur renommé de romans policiers, vit sa célébrité dans le plus grand anonymat. Un jour, l'écrivain reçoit une lettre bien étrange, signée du nom de l'un de ses personnages de fiction, lui demandant sa coopération.

title: Nintama Rantaro Dokutake Ninja-tai Saikyou no Gunshi
Doraemon: Nobita no Uchû Eiyûki
resume: Nobita wishes to be a real hero. Doraemon uses his gadget, the Burger Director to make them a real movie superhero. Aron saw the five powers and abilities and asks them to help him save his planet, the planet Pokkuru. After their journey to the planet, the gang thought it was only Burger's doing but realizing that it is not a movie and they are actually fighting bad guys.

title: Peur bleue
resume: When a group of friends fail to lower the ladder of their boat, they find themselves stranded in the surrounding waters and struggle to survive.

title: Bigger
resume: Lee, a troubled young woman, travels with Chet, a giant who helps her discover her inner strength as she struggles to survive the adventure of a lifetime.

title: Les Gladiateurs de Rome
resume: Avant de rencontrer Lucilla, Timo, un élève de l'Académie des gladiateurs, n'avait aucune envie de combattre dans l'arène. Maintenant, il souhaite devenir le combattant dont rêve sa belle.

title: Strangers in Good Company
resume: A busload of women become stranded in an isolated part of the Canadian countryside. As they await rescue, they reflect on their lives.

title: Ewa chce spac
resume: A young female student arrives in a new city, and finds herself in a confusing situation: there is no place for her for sleeping. An incredible odyssey through the endless maze of night streets is ahead.

title: Le signe de Zorro
resume: A seemingly idiotic fop is really the courageous vigilante Zorro, who seeks to protect the oppressed.

title: Sand Land
resume: Le monde est devenu un désert désolé appelé SandLand, habité par des humains et des démons.

title: Samouraï
resume: When a samurai clan attempting to assassinate a feudal lord begin to suspect a traitor, they start an investigation on a ronin who is helping their cause.

title: Le capitaine Kidd
resume: The unhistorical adventures of pirate Captain Kidd revolve around treasure and treachery.

title: Shogun Samourai
resume: Après la mort par empoisonnement du shogun Tokugawa, ses fils Iemitsu et Tadanaga se disputent le shogunat, divisant le pays en factions belligérantes. Le mentor d'Iemitsu trahit tout le monde pour assurer le pouvoir d'Iemitsu.

title: Werewolves of the Third Reich
resume: Allemagne, aux moments forts de la Seconde Guerre mondiale, un groupe disparate de soldats américains découvre le plan diabolique du docteur Mengele visant à créer une armée imparable de loups-garous Nazis.

title: Anno zero - Guerra nello spazio
resume: Captain Alex Hamilton investigates a strange signal on Earth and a UFO above Antarctica, discovering a giant robot enslaving humanoids and observing Earth from an unknown planet.

title: Lu Xing Sha
resume: Qian Cheng, le patron de l'entreprise pharmaceutique, a investi dans un laboratoire de recherche bio-pharmaceutique situé au fin fond de la jungle. En modifiant le gène du requin pour développer un nouveau type de médicament anticancéreux.

title: Wiro Sableng 212
resume: Indonesia, the 16th century, Wiro Sableng, a disciple from a mysterious Warrior named Sinto Gendeng, got a mission from his Master to take down Mahesa Birawa, her former disciple who betrayed her.

title: Kin no tori
resume: A golden apple is stolen from the King's garden. The King orders his three sons to guard the apples in turn and to find out who is the thief. When the youngest son, Hansu, presents a feather that he got from the golden bird that stole the apple the king sends his three sons to bring this bird to him and so Hansu journey begins.

title: Cody le Robosapien
resume: A robot boy and a human boy team up to save their respective parents, who are being held captive by the organization that funded the robot's creator.

title: Qing gong qi shi lu
resume: With the impending death of the Emperor Ching one candidate for the throne hires the lady assassin to get rid of another strong contender.

title: Cinq semaines en ballon
resume: In 1862, the British commission inventor Fergusson to claim uncharted land in West Africa for Britain by flying his giant hot air balloon there.

title: Gidget à Rome
resume: Gidget, in Rome for a holiday, misinterprets attention she receives from a famous journalist. Discovering he is "chaperoning" her at Dad's request she resumes interest in her boyfriend. Based upon characters created by Frederick Kohner.

title: CIA: Comrade in America
resume: Un jeune homme du Kerala a deux semaines pour empêcher le mariage arrangé aux États-Unis de la femme qu'il aime, mais il n'a pas les papiers pour y arriver.

title: Apocalypse Pompei
resume: Mount Vesuvius erupts when a family visits Pompeii. The daughter uses her skill and her father his ability, in order to escape the disaster.

title: L'Enlèvement des Sabines
resume: The classic story from the early days of Rome where there are no women. Romulus, the founder of Rome, finds women to be wives from Sabina where there are a lot of women. The Sabine men, of course, attack Rome to get their wives and daughters back.

title: L'Aigle rouge de Bagdad
resume: Using a magic flying carpet and a handful of friends, the son of a murdered Caliph must fight the usurper in order to win the throne of the Caliphate.

title: Arrowhead
resume: A tech is sprung from prison by a revolutionary leader who promises him an opportunity to save his father from a scheduled execution if he completes a data-stealing mission. But it goes awry, stranding him on a strange alien moon.

title: Genius Party
resume: Several directors take part in an anthology dedicated to short anime films.

title: L'île mystérieuse
resume: A group of escaped prisoners, traveling in a hot air balloon, have to land on a remote islands and must try to survive there. They encounter a castaway, pirates, and captain Nemo with his array of scientific gadgets to keep strangers off his island.

title: Djam
resume: A Greek girl meets a French woman in Constantinople.

title: Thabo and the Rhino Case
resume: Thabo (11) wants to become a private detective. If only his home, the small African village, was not the most peaceful Savannah paradise. But things take a sudden turn when a rhino is murdered in the safari park for its horn.

title: Péril de glace
resume: An Antarctic drilling station is under attack by a mysterious killer. Will anyone survive?

title: Tarzan et la Diablesse
resume: Des braconniers d'ivoire, dirigés par Lyra la diablesse, Vargo et Fidel, capturent une tribu indigène pour transporter leur butin. Tarzan intervient, mais il est capturé.

title: Shakespeare's Mummy
resume: After a mummy hand appears in a frat party pizza, four kids must chase it down, escape the mob and an ancient sect but most of all learn to forgive each other if they're going to stop an Egyptian zombie apocalypse . . . then deliver pizza.

title: La dernière reine
resume: D'après la légende, le roi d'Alger avait une femme nommée Zaphira. À la mort du suzerain, probablement assassiné par son allié Barberousse, venu libérer la ville des espagnols, celle-ci monte sur le trône en tenant tête à ses opposants.

title: La Folie des grandeurs
resume: Au 17ème siècle en Espagne, le ministre des Finances tente de déshonorer la reine. Mais son plan est trop complexe.

title: Tri kota. Zimnie kanikuly
resume: Korzhik, Caramel and Kompot dream of a bright and unusual New Year celebration, this is their main goal. But when the kitten Lollipop appears, they turn their attention to him and are forced to save Lollipop and his parents. And suddenly the New Year turns out even better than they expected.

title: Hidden Dragon
resume: In a magical undersea world where dragons rule and humans are feared, a naive young dragon forms an uneasy alliance with the sea's greatest enemy - a human girl.

title: Safari cannibal
resume: Des soldats japonais de la Seconde Guerre mondiale cachent un trésor dans une grotte de la forêt des Philippines après avoir été attaqués par une tribu indigène. Des décennies plus tard, une équipe hétéroclite souhaite récupérer l'or.

title: Koati
resume: Trois héros improbables : Nachi, Xochi et Pako, se lancent dans une aventure pour empêcher le méchant serpent corail Zaina de détruire leur forêt tropicale.

title: Extremedays
resume: During a lifelong expedition planned by four lifelong friends - Will, Brian, Matt, and Corey - Corey's beloved grandfather suddenly passed away.

title: Les racines du ciel
resume: En Afrique-Équatoriale française, un écologiste idéaliste lance une campagne de sensibilisation publique pour permettre de sauver les éléphants africains de l'extinction.

title: Turneja
resume: Year 1993, the bleakest time of war in Bosnia and Herzegovina. A group of actors from Belgrade, utterly unaware of what they're setting themselves up for, embark on a search for quick earnings - on a "tour" around the Serbian Krajina. However, there they are thrust into the heart of war and begin to wander from war front to war front, from one army to the next.

title: Call of Silence
resume: The world has been ravaged by a pandemic. Alone and outside the safety of the forest, Marko faces a shattered world shrouded in silence and danger.

title: Blue
resume: Un groupe de personnes, confronté à de nombreux défis, décide de traquer un trésor perdu en route vers l'Inde.

title: Doraemon: Nobita to mugen sankenshi
resume: Nobita comes into his dream with Doraemon's tools. He is a hero there.

title: Özgür Dünya
resume: The story of a game managed by artificial intelligence, which will fall as a bomb to the sector, actually has a different meaning for Asli and her father. This work, designed with a thousand difficulties, will be the first in the world.

title: Eiga Kureyon Shinchan: Ora no hikkoshi monogatari - Saboten daishuugeki
resume: This is the story of the transfer of shinchan's family to mexico where they unintentionaly unravel the secret of some mysterious cactus

title: Le jardin d'Allah
resume: The star-crossed desert romance of a cloistered woman and a renegade monk.

title: Les Cinq Gosses d'oncle Johnny
resume: William Holden plays a drifter who comes to a small town and discovers a cabin in the forest where five kids--January, February, March, April, and May--are living on their own. Their parents died a while ago, and they want to keep that a secret from the townspeople, especially the young schoolteacher (Coleen Gray), because they don't want to end up in a children's home and then eventually separated. Holden's character moves in with the kids and poses as their uncle to take care of them while romancing the teacher. However, in order to keep the children, he must get married.

title: Cloudburst
resume: A lesbian couple escape from their nursing home and head up to Canada to get married. Along the way, they pick up a young, male hitchhiker.

title: Le prince oublié
resume: Djibi raconte chaque soir à sa fille Sofia des histoires qui l'emmène dans Storyland, où il est le héros dans leurs aventures de contes de fées. Cinq ans plus tard, Djibi doit trouver un moyen de rester éternellement le héros de sa fille.

title: Missile X
resume: An American intelligence agent travels to pre-Islamic Revolution Iran to try to thwart a power-mad European baron from using a stolen cruise missile to destroy an unspecific target in that country.

title: One Glorious Day
resume: "One Glorious Day" tells the tale of when Ek, who is a disembodied spirit, required to wait his turn in the boring cosmos until he is allowed to inhabit an earthly body. Impatient, he sneaks off to earth to find a body.

title: This Game's Called Murder
resume: Un conte moderne à l'humour noir sur la cupidité, la romance et l'innocence perdue dans une société aliénée et folle de consommation qui fonctionne comme une critique sévère de la société d'aujourd'hui sans se prendre trop au sérieux.

title: Duel à Ichijoji
resume: Musashi, qui essaye de défier en duel le maître d'une école de samouraï, en est empêché par ses disciples. Otsu, qui attend toujours son retour, rencontre Akemi qui se languit aussi de lui. Aucune des deux ne sait qui serait la promise.

title: Sakura hime
resume: The mad journey of a rebellious princess who ventures to work at a brothel to find the tattooed intruder she met on a fateful night.

title: Sleeping Beauty
resume: The beautiful Aurora is cursed into everlasting sleep by an evil witch for a crime she didn't commit. The brave Commander of the Guard, William, embarks on a quest inspired by both love and loyalty to free the doomed princess.

title: Échec au roi
resume: The wartime adventures of Scotish highland leader Rob Roy MacGregor during the reign of King George I in the 18th century.

title: Between Waves
resume: When a best-selling author has a midlife crisis, he returns to his coastal hometown and embarks on a wild adventure in a desperate attempt to reclaim his youth.

title: Fungi
resume: In a post-apocalyptic Sweden, scientists seek a cure for a deadly mushroom infection. They face a gang using drugs to stave off the effects as they race to a research bunker for survival.

title: Made in U.S.A.
resume: Two misfit best friends, Dar and Tuck, leave their dying coal-mining town with only one goal in mind - to reach sunny California and hook up with some beach babes. On the road, they meet gun-crazy outlaw Annie, and she takes over.

title: Descente mortelle
resume: A group of former military elites set out to explore an uncharted abyss, not knowing their worst nightmare is waiting for them deep beneath the ground.

title: Duncan
resume: Une satire inspirée de la théorie du complot connue sous le nom de Pizzagate. Un journaliste et un milicien d'extrême droite s'associent pour révéler la vérité derrière des sectes sexuelles, une pizzeria et le peuple des lézards.

title: Phantom Soldier
resume: An M.I.A. US soldier nicknamed White Ghost lives in hiding in the jungles of communist Vietnam. The US army finds out about him and sends a black ops team to rescue him. However, the team is led by a man who wants White Ghost dead.

title: Pilote du diable
resume: Former World War II flying ace Matt Brennan takes a position as a test pilot for a commercial aircraft corporation and bumps into his old girlfriend, Jo Holloway, who now works as a receptionist for the company.

title: Renard et Lapine sauvent la forêt
resume: It centers on the adventures of Fox and Hare, best friends who are surrounded by a bunch who have become like family. One day, they find out that Owl has gone missing, and they embark on a journey to find him.

title: Fairy Tail, le film : Dragon Cry
resume: In the new film, based on the Hiro Mashima's manga, Natsu Dragneel and his friends travel to the island Kingdom of Stella, where they will reveal dark secrets, fight the new enemies and once again save the world from destruction.

title: Atlantic Rim : Résurrection
resume: The east coast is under attack by monsters. The mechs attempting to fight them off are better armed than their precursors, but so are the creatures.

title: Tai Chi Hero
resume: Yang Luchan marries the Chen style kung fu grand master's daughter in Chen village in 1800s China, so he can learn Chen style kung fu/tai chi. The deputy governor wants the village.

title: Age of the Dragons
resume: Herman Melville's classic novel Moby Dick, is recreated in a world where Captain Ahab and his crew search for a Great White Dragon.

title: Daye: Seret ahl el Daye
resume: Daye, an 14-year-old Nubian albino with a golden voice, faces adversity due to his unique appearance. Abandoned by his father and bullied by peers, he dreams of following his idol, Mohamed Mounir.

title: Villmark
resume: 5 Norwegians head for a cabin in the wilderness for a few days of team building. But strange things start happening--especially down by the water where they find an abandoned tent. Is someone else around?

title: Guyana : La Secte de l'enfer
resume: Reverend Jim Jones, the priest of an independent church in the South American country Guyana, orders his followers to commit suicide. But not all of them follow him blindly and begin to think on their own.

title: Zoombies 2
resume: A game ranger and a team of poachers end up surrounded by zombie animals and they forge an alliance to stop the beasts before the super-zombie virus spreads to the entire world.

title: Au secours ! J'ai rétréci mes amis
resume: To protect his magic objects Otto Leonhard has taught Felix the secret art of shrinking. When Felix's friends almost mess up his date with Melanie, he shrinks them spontaneously to a tenth of their size.

title: Le Cerveau
resume: Lorsque l'OTAN transfère une partie de ses fonds de Paris à Bruxelles par train, un cerveau criminel se faisant passer pour un colonel britannique envisage de les voler, mais deux voleurs français de moindre envergure ont la même idée.

title: Captain Miller
resume: L'histoire se déroule dans les années 1930-1940 en Inde britannique et suit un hors-la-loi appelé Miller qui se livre à des pillages, des vols et des agressions sanglantes.

title: Mayor Grom. Igra
resume: Un an s'est écoulé depuis la défaite du docteur de la peste, et Igor Grom est devenu un héros pour toute la ville. Mais il attend maintenant de se battre contre un nouveau super-vilain.

title: Mika & Sebastian: l'aventure de la poire géante
resume: Life in Solby is nice and peaceful until one day Mitcho and Sebastian find a message in a bottle by the harbour. The bottle is from the missing mayor of Solby with a message that he is on a mysterious island and has made a great discovery. Now they must embark on a perilous journey to help save the mayor and bring him home, and in the process they uncover something that will bring great pleasure to the city of Solby - a giant pear.

title: Pororo 3: Cyber Space Adventure
resume: In this Pororo the Little Penguin adventure, Pororo must tap into his video game abilities to save a princess. Together with his group of friends, Pororo enters a magical world to save the day!

title: The Warrior
resume: In feudal India, a warrior (Khan) who renounces his role as the long time enforcer to a local lord becomes the prey in a murderous hunt through the Himalayan mountains.

title: Tracker
resume: Tracker is an adventure thriller centered on the growing hobby called geocaching (following GPS coordinates to find hidden items), that takes the characters on a complex hunt as they race against time to save the life of a loved one.

title: La malle de Singapour
resume: A bord de son bateau reliant Hong Kong à Singapour, le capitaine Gaskell est partagé entre une jeune femme raffinée et une ancienne petite amie, aux manières beaucoup plus directes. Le navire est alors attaqué par des pirates.

title: Manborg
resume: A soldier, brought back to life as a cyborg, fights alongside a band of adventurers against demon hordes in a dystopian future.

title: The Last Boy on Earth
resume: In a distant future, an enigmatic boy becomes the central figure in the search for a new hope. Who is this kid? Why is everyone looking for him? Sometimes it is better not to know certain answers.

title: Quantum Supremacy
resume: In a future threatened by rogue robots and an all-powerful AI, Captain Monroe and his crew race to prevent humanity's downfall in Quantum Supremacy.

title: American Dream
resume: Les entrepreneurs Scott et Nicky ont désespérément besoin d'argent pour terminer leur projet de construction. Ils se tournent vers le gangster russe Yuri, mais après avoir refusé, Yuri se venge en essayant de reprendre leur projet.

title: Zone Troopers
resume: In Italy, during World War II some American soldiers find an alien UFO.

title: Noviembre
resume: Impelled by a spirit which still preserves a patina of idealism, Alfredo arrives in Madrid intent on creating "a performance which is freer.

title: Atlantic Convoy
resume: German agents infiltrate an Iceland port used by the US Navy for anti-sub patrols protecting convoys. Their goal is to block the harbor and trap the patrols. The officers in charge must stop the plot before the subs are left unchecked.

title: Le règne par le sabre
resume: So-ha, a deadly female warrior, is sent to find a exiled prince after the Killer Blade Army killed the royal family.

title: Le gardien de la cité perdue
resume: Briar and Bramble lose their mother at a very young age due to mysterious circumstances. Many years later, when an older female bear shows up on the scene, the Bear Brothers are determined to find out the truth once and for all.

title: Pulau
resume: The vacation of a group of youngsters turns into an endless horrifying nightmare after a losing bet forces them to spend a night at a deserted island. As they stumble upon a mysterious abandoned village there, they accidentally break an old spell that was placed to restraint an antagonizing spirit trapped in the island. One by one, they are made to suffer the gripping and gruesome consequences of their mistakes, infuriating an evil creature that needs human blood to stay alive. The only way out is in the hands of a girl who desperately needs to use her supernatural gift to untangle an unsettling history connected to a tainted cross-cultural love story.

title: Zodi et Téhu, frères du désert
resume: Il raconte l'histoire d'un garçon berbère qui se lie à un chameau alors qu'ils traversent le désert du Sahara.

title: Les As de la jungle
resume: The Jungle Bunch's tiger striped Kung Fu penguin leader Maurice and his comrades, a goldfish, a tarsier and a gorilla, fight to protect the jungle from a gang of silly baboons lead by Igor the evil koala.

title: Afterwards
resume: AFTERWARDS is a dark yet spiritual drama that follows the journey of a man who's been abandoned in the frozen north for thirty years after his death.

title: Pavillon noir
resume: After being wronged by the Caribbean authorities, a Dutch captain turns pirate to wage war.

title: Will
resume: An orphan journeys across Europe to the 2005 Champions League Final in Istanbul.

title: Vlci bouda
resume: A group of teenagers are mysteriously invited to a skiing workshop in the mountains. There are eleven of them, but the camp supervisors insist that there should be only ten, and that one of them is an intruder.

title: Tchin-Tchin
resume: A young girl lost in Shanghai is taken in by an American playboy and his girlfriend.

title: Le pays du dauphin vert
resume: A young man loved by two sisters becomes a naval officer and sails to New Zealand, where he drunkenly writes a marriage proposal to the wrong sister, profoundly affecting the life of the other.

title: The pirates
resume: Une bande de pirates et un groupe de bandits se battent pour attraper une baleine grise qui a avalé un sceau royal.

title: Les guerriers de la jungle
resume: A group of models fly into the jungle of some South American country to look for a photo location. Their plane is shot down and they are captured by a drug baron's private army. At the same time, the Mafia's representative arrive to negotiate future collaboration.

title: Chasseur de monstres 2: Le destin du royaume
resume: L'histoire se poursuit avec Wuba suite à sa séparation avec ses parents humains (Tian et Lan) pour son propre voyage. La paix n'a pas été restaurée dans le monde des monstres après la mort du roi monstre démoniaque.

title: Zu, les guerriers de la montagne magique
resume: A Chinese soldier in an ancient civil war flees the battlefield and gets caught up in a fantastical quest to save the world from evil.

title: L'Agent Pierrafeu 007
resume: While preparing for a camping trip, Fred Flintstone is enlisted by the Bedrock Secret Service to capture a criminal mastermind after a spy who looks like him is injured on the job.

title: Okko et les Fantômes
resume: Suite à un terrible accident de voiture ayant coûté la vie à ses parents, Okko se retrouve envoyée chez sa grand-mère qui tient une auberge à la campagne. Là, un gentil fantôme la pousse à aider sa mamie dans la gestion de l'établissement.

title: Second Time Lucky
resume: There's a new wager between Heaven and Hell. Devil bets God that if God were to pick two young people to be the new Adam and Eve, they'd sin again. God accepts and sends a college couple to various eras, starting with the Garden of Eden.

title: Mosley
resume: A species of creatures known as "thoriphants" rebel against their life of servitude and embark on a treacherous journey to find the fabled city of Uprights.

title: Samson contre Hercule
resume: While traveling through the kingdom of Sulom, Samson is arrested and finds that the queen no longer reigns and that a power-mad warlord and his army of mercenaries now controls the kingdom. Samson teams up with some of his one-time adversaries to battle the usurper and restore the rightful queen to power.

title: Load Wedding
resume: Un jeune homme se marie avant sa soeur aînée, la rendant amère, jalouse et sans dot.

title: Le comte de Monte-Cristo: La trahison
resume: Edmond Dantès est faussement accusé par les envieux de sa bonne fortune et condamné à passer le reste de sa vie dans la tristement célèbre prison insulaire du Château d'If.

title: En route vers Rio
resume: Two inept vaudevillians stow away on a Brazilian-bound ocean liner and foil a plot by a sinister hypnotist to marry off her niece to a greedy fortune hunter.

title: Passeport pour l'oubli
resume: A local doctor is recruited as a cold war spy to fulfill a very important secret mission in the Middle East, only to experience that his mission is complicated by a sexy female double agent.

title: Bibi & Tina voll verhext!
resume: When robbers hit Frankenstein's castle, teen pals Bibi and Tina hunt for the crooks, then devise a plan to save the neighbors' failing ranch.

title: River Queen
resume: An intimate story set during the 1860s in which a young Irish woman Sarah and her family find themselves on both sides of the turbulent wars between British and Maori during the British colonization of New Zealand.

title: Galactica - Les Cylons attaquent
resume: Running low on fuel, the Battlestar Galactica receives the help of the supposedly lost Battlestar Pegasus which is taking the offensive with the Cylons.

title: Old Gringo
resume: Looking for change late in life, Harriet travels for a job as teacher in Mexico. The revolutionaries use her to gain access to a fortified estate. There she meets General Arroyo and befriends Old Gringo, a writer.

title: Maidentrip
resume: 14-year-old Laura Dekker sets out on a two-year voyage in pursuit of her dream to become the youngest person ever to sail around the world alone.

title: Détective Conan: Le Pire Cauchemar
resume: A spy infiltrated the Japanese National Police Agency, retrieving secret files of Britain's MI6, Germany's BND and America's CIA and FBI. Rei Furuya and a group of Tokyo Police PSB intercepted the spy during the getaway, and just before the major car accident, FBI Agent Shuichi Akai sniped and crashed the spy's vehicle. The next day, at the aquarium in Tokyo with the Ferris wheel, Conan and the Detective Boys found a woman with heterochromia iris who suffered memory loss and had a broken cell phone. Having decided to stay and help the woman regain her memory, Conan and the Detective Boys are under the watchful eye of Vermouth.

title: Kak menya zovut
resume: Two Moscow teens visit Olya's estranged father in Crimea and decide to switch identities as a prank. Their seemingly innocent deception leads to life-altering consequences.

title: Survivor
resume: Au cours de leur recherche d'une planète habitable, les derniers humains vivants s'écrasent sur un monde stérile, habité par des extraterrestres sanguinaires et de mystérieux guerriers post-apocalyptiques.

title: Mohenjo Daro
resume: In 2016 BC, a kind farmer leads an uprising in the city of Mohenjo Daro.

title: Need for Speed 2
resume: A follow-up to the 2014 action movie 'Need for Speed'.

title: To aru hikuushi e no tsuioku
resume: A pilot, despite being advised not to, bonds with a princess when he is tasked with escorting the royal subject overseas and across enemy territory to reunite her with her future husband.

title: Return of Hanuman
resume: A young boy, Minku, ridiculed by his friends, begs the gods to send him down to Earth, and his wish is granted.

title: Dead Dead Demon's Dededede Destruction Kôhen
resume: A huge spaceship materializing over Tokyo initiates a contentious war with seemingly harmless aliens. However, high school students Koyama and Nakagawa act unaffected, prioritizing their daily routines.

title: Le Roi Arthur: le pouvoir d'Excalibur
resume: Lorsque le roi Arthur livre son dernier combat au cœur de la bataille de Camlann, le royaume sombre dans le chaos. Avant de mourir le roi charge l’un de ses plus fidèle chevalier de confier Excalibur, son épée légendaire à la Dame du Lac.

title: The Black Knight Returns
resume: When an evil corporation threatens to unleash the black plague, Evan Grail, is recruited by his grandfather,Max, into the order of the Black Knights - a secret band of warriors who have been called upon in the past to fight evil

title: The Twilight People
resume: A kidnapped diver is taken to an island inhabited by a mad scientist and his half-animal, half-human creations.

title: Les amours d'Hercule
resume: Hercule doit sauver son amour d'une reine maléfique.

title: Neelakasham Pachakadal Chuvanna Bhoomi
resume: Kasi and Suni go for the ride from Kerala to Nagaland in search of Kasi's girlfriend. En route, they encounter different people who change their lives forever.

title: Sauvetage au sommet
resume: Un père et son fils tentent de sauver une petite ville et son tunnel nouvellement construit qui est menacé par des catastrophes naturelles.

title: Chasse sanglante
resume: Five city boys head out into the countryside for a relaxing hunt. However, local psychopaths turn the hunters into the hunted, and they need all the ammo and wits they have to get out of the woods alive.

title: King
resume: King, un lionceau victime de la traite, s'échappe de l'aéroport en plein transit et trouve refuge chez Inès et Alex, qui élaborent un plan fou: ramener King en Afrique. Cependant, les douaniers ne facilitent pas leur mission.

title: Doraemon: Nobita to Animaru puranetto
resume: What comes to the end of war, unlimited development and environmental destruction.

title: La Guerre des boutons
resume: Deux groupes de garçons des villages ruraux de Longeverne et Velran sont en guerre constante l'un contre l'autre. Leur guerre est une tradition qui se transmet de père en fils et sans motif.

title: Lili à la découverte du monde sauvage
resume: Leafie is a hen who manages to escape the horrible conditions of an egg production line. After surviving a harrowing encounter with a one-eyed weasel and being rejected by the barnyard animals where she grew up, a chance encounter sees her becoming the guardian of a duckling. Despite the child being a duck, Leafie is willing to learn and make the sacrifices she needs in order to ensure the happiness of her son.

title: Intervention Delta
resume: Lorsque la femme et les enfants d'un industriel sont enlevés par des terroristes en Grèce, l'ex-mari de la femme vient à la rescousse avec un plan impliquant des deltaplanes.

title: The Edge - L'affrontement
resume: In 1945, Soviet war hero Ignat is sent to work as a locomotive mechanic in a Siberian labor camp where he meets an assortment of Germans and Russians.

title: Le vilain petit canard et moi
resume: This modern version of Hans Christian Andersen's fairytale is charming. Ratso is a streetwise chancer of a rat whose theatre show is struggling. Then he finds an egg that hatches a mutant swan. Ratso soon sees the potential of showing Ugly as a freak. But things go awry when rodent heavies appear...

title: Welp
resume: Sam, 12 ans, trop imaginatif, part dans les bois pour un camp de scoutisme d'été avec sa bande, convaincu qu'il rencontrera un monstre. C'est effectivement ce qui arrive.

title: Richard Coeur de Lion
resume: While leading the Third Crusade, King Richard the Lionheart (George Sanders) battles treachery in his own camp as well as the Saracens and their charismatic leader Emir Hderim Sultan Saladin (Sir Rex Harrison).

title: Mission: Killfast
resume: From Astro-Zombies director Ted V. Mikels comes this adrenalized tale of a high-kicking CIA agent, vengeful Las Vegas gangsters, unhinged arms dealers, terrorists with nuclear weapons, explosions and bikini clad beauties.

title: I Heart Robots
resume: Des années après l'apocalypse des robots, Terra s'aventure hors de son enceinte isolée pour emmener son adorable compagnon robot West et sauver ce qu'il reste d'un monde en voie de disparition.

title: Chhota Bheem Aur Mayavi Gorgan
resume: Dholakpur's court learns that Gorgan's prince seeks King Indravarma's help due to nightly goblins destroying their city. Bheem and friends embark to battle the goblins responsible for the curse.

title: Violence et sexe aux temps préhistoriques
resume: In prehistoric times, two brothers fight each other for the leadership of their tribe.

title: A Christmas Carol
resume: An old and evil businessman who doesn't believe in Christmas is haunted by three ghosts that shows him the joy of Christmas.

title: Black Beauty
resume: A father allows his daughter to spend the summer with her grandfather rehabilitating an injured horse, and they learn that love and trust can heal anything.

title: Dragon Ball : L'Aventure mystique
resume: Goku and Krillin are invited to participate in a martial arts tournament taking place in the country of Mifan, where a desperate emperor needs help.

title: Kyo kara ore wa!
resume: Three years after the event of the series, Takashi Mitsuhashi and Shinji Ito face the new enemies.

title: Big Shots
resume: Ivan Reitman brings you Big Shots, a slam-bang comedy-adventure with a heart as big as Chicago.

title: Reign of Fire
